NK033(gi)008:1: // rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba snying thig ma bu'i
NK033(gi)008:2: bka' srol chu bo gnyis 'dus kyi khrid yig dri
NK033(gi)008:3: med zhal lung zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)008:4: na mo gu ru badz+ra sa man+ta b+ha d+r+aa ya /
NK033(gi)008:5: rang byung ye shes kun khyab gdod ma'i mgon //
NK033(gi)008:6: khyad par bdun ldan dbyings snang longs spyod rdzogs //
NK033(gi)008:7: rang bzhin 'gro 'dul sna tshogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)008:8: khyab bdag bla ma'i zhabs la phyag bagyi'o //
NK033(gi)008:9: zab cing brtag dka' nam mkha' lta bu'i gnas //
NK033(gi)008:10: spang bya gnyen po gnyis ka'i mtha' las grol //
NK033(gi)008:11: su 'phrad 'byung bzhi 'od du dengs byed pa //
NK033(gi)008:12: bstan pa 'od gsal rdo rje rtse mor 'dud //
NK033(gi)008:13: dga' rab la sogs rgya bod rig pa 'dzin //
NK033(gi)008:14: khyad par dri med bshes gnyen mkhas pa'i rje //
NK033(gi)008:15: klong chen rab 'byams ye shes sgyu ma'i 'phrul //
NK033(gi)008:16: rdo rje gzi brjid byang chub bar du bsnyen //
NK033(gi)008:17: bcu bdun rgyud kyi gnyen 'dzin 'khor 'das kyi //
NK033(gi)008:18: dbyings phyug sngags kyi bdag mo ral gcig mas //
NK033(gi)008:19: gnang ba'i skabs stsol 'chad dang nyams len la //
NK033(gi)008:20: bar chad med cing grub pa mthar phyin mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:21: gdod ma'i dbyings su 'khor ba dong sprugs chos //
NK033(gi)008:22: rtog ges ma bslad byin rlabs gzi ma nyams //
NK033(gi)008:23: dri med bshes gnyen thugs kyi thig le ni //
NK033(gi)008:24: kun mkhyen chos rjes bcud du dril ba gang //
NK033(gi)008:25: gter chen yab sras zhal lung bum bzang las //
NK033(gi)008:26: khyab bdag bla ma'i drin gyis legs thob pa //
NK033(gi)008:27: rang bzos ma bslad gzhan la phan 'dod blos //
NK033(gi)008:28: 'dus gsal lag khrid rim pa bshad par bya //
NK033(gi)008:29: 'dir phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba ma lus pa'i bstan pa thams cad kyi rtse mo /
NK033(gi)008:30: chos kyi 'khor lo mtha' dag gi yang bcud /
NK033(gi)008:31: rdo rje theg pa'i nyams len thams cad kyi mthar thug /
NK033(gi)008:32: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i snying po /
NK033(gi)008:33: yang gsang man ngag gi sde slob dpon chen po
NK033(gi)008:34: bi ma la mi tra'i snying thig ma bu'i bka'
NK033(gi)008:35: srol chu bo gcig 'dres kyi zab khrid 'chad par
NK033(gi)008:37: mthun rkyen tshogs pas gdams ngag gi sgrom du gzhug pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:38: 'chad bya khrid tshul gdams ngag dngos bshad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:40: khrid 'chad pa po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid /
NK033(gi)008:43: mthun rkyen gyi gzhi bzung ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:45: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK033(gi)008:46: mkhas shing bya ba bral ba dang //
NK033(gi)008:47: chos nyid don la tshad phebs dang //
NK033(gi)008:48: 'dod pa'i don la rmongs pa med //
NK033(gi)008:49: gsang sngags bla ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK033(gi)008:51: spyir gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag gi don la mkhas shing grub mtha'i dbye ba phyed pa /
NK033(gi)008:52: bye brag lam 'di nyid kyi nyams myong drod tshad dang ldan pa /
NK033(gi)008:53: man ngag gi don ston pa la mkhas shing chags
NK033(gi)008:54: sdang sogs tshe 'di'i 'du 'dzi'i g.yeng ba dang bral
NK033(gi)008:55: ba / rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i
NK033(gi)008:56: rim gnyis kyi nyams len mthar phyin pas ye shes
NK033(gi)008:57: kyi dkyil 'khor chos nyid mngon sum gyi don tshad
NK033(gi)008:58: ba / la phebs pa / dgongs pas rang rgyud grol cing thugs rjes gzhan rgyud smin nus pa /
NK033(gi)008:59: gnas lugs kyi don la shes rab zab mos sgro
NK033(gi)008:60: 'dogs chod pa'i ye shes kyis slob mas dris pa'i
NK033(gi)008:61: lan la ma rmongs pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:62: mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan pa ni bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:63: de las ldog pa'i skyon can bsten du mi rung ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:65: mi shes nga rgyal chen po dang //
NK033(gi)008:66: blo rmongs tshig phyir 'breng ba dang //
NK033(gi)008:67: gsang sngags don la mi dgongs dang //
NK033(gi)008:68: gzhan gyi zhe gcod khengs tshig dang //
NK033(gi)008:69: log pa'i lam du zhugs pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:70: dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhal ma mthong //
NK033(gi)008:71: dam tshig 'chal bar gyur pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:72: dris pa dag la lan mi 'debs //
NK033(gi)008:73: thos chung nga rgyal che ba ste //
NK033(gi)008:74: slob dpon ma brtags slob ma'i bdud //
NK033(gi)008:75: ces pas skyon de dag dang ldan pa ni thog ma nas bsten par mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:76: gnyis pa slob ma'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK033(gi)008:78: dad pa'i stobs dang brtson 'grus che //
NK033(gi)008:79: shes rab che zhing 'dzin chags med //
NK033(gi)008:80: phu dud che zhing gsang sngags spyod //
NK033(gi)008:81: rtog med sems la g.yeng pa med //
NK033(gi)008:82: dam tshig ldan zhig sgrub la brtson //
NK033(gi)008:83: slob dpon ji skad gsung bzhin byed //
NK033(gi)008:85: bla ma dang gdams ngag la yid rab tu spro zhing don du gnyen ba dang ba'i dad pa /
NK033(gi)008:86: bsgrub bya'i 'bras bu la ched du gdung ba 'dod pa'i dad pa /
NK033(gi)008:87: the tshom mi byed pa yid ches kyi dad pa /
NK033(gi)008:88: nyi tshe ba'i rkyen gyis mi 'phrog pa mthar thug
NK033(gi)008:89: gi dad pa ste byin rlabs 'jug pa'i rgyu tshang
NK033(gi)008:90: ba / bla na med pa'i byang chub sgrub pa
NK033(gi)008:91: la phyi bshol dang thang lhod med pa'i snying stobs
NK033(gi)008:93: gnas lugs zab mo'i don la dpyod pa'i shes rab gsal bas nyams rtogs skye sla ba /
NK033(gi)008:94: zas gos sogs srid pa'i bde 'byor la 'dzin chags chung ba /
NK033(gi)008:95: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha la phu dud che bas byin rlabs 'jug pa'i sgo tshang ba /
NK033(gi)008:96: gsang sngags kyi lam la the tshom gyi sgro 'dogs
NK033(gi)008:97: chod pas zab mo'i spyod pa la 'jug nus pa
NK033(gi)008:98: / chags sdang rmongs gsum sogs tha mal gyi rnam
NK033(gi)008:99: rtog la sems mi 'jug pas g.yeng ba dang bral
NK033(gi)008:100: / ba / rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK033(gi)008:101: tshig gnyer du blangs pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam
NK033(gi)008:102: / ba / bca' brtan pa / zab mo'i lam sgom pa la skyo ngal med cing /
NK033(gi)008:103: bla mas ji ltar gsungs pa las mi 'da' ba ste /
NK033(gi)008:104: mtshan nyid de ldan gyi slob ma nyid 'chad yul du bzung bar bya dgos shing /
NK033(gi)008:105: de las ldog pa'i snod skyon can ni /
NK033(gi)008:107: bkur bsti phu dud mi byed cing //
NK033(gi)008:108: gsang sngags 'chal bar spyod pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:109: rigs rgyud med cing ngang rgyud med //
NK033(gi)008:110: shes rab chung bar gyur pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:111: bka' drin khyad du gsod pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:112: don med 'chal bar gyur pa ste //
NK033(gi)008:113: slob ma ma brtags slob dpon dgra //
NK033(gi)008:114: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i snod min la zab mo'i
NK033(gi)008:115: chos bstan na d+aa ki dam can gyis bka' chad
NK033(gi)008:116: 'bebs shing dngos grub mi thob pa dang sgro skur
NK033(gi)008:118: gsum pa bsten pa'i tshul ni /
NK033(gi)008:119: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i slob ma des kyang nad pas sman pa bsten pa ltar /
NK033(gi)008:120: 'khor ba'i nad las thar ba'i don du /
NK033(gi)008:121: lus ngag yid gsum gus pas g.yo zol med par sri zhu dang phu dud bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:122: gru 'dod pas mnyan pa bsten pa ltar 'khor bas 'jigs nas rtag tu ci gsung nyan pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:123: tshong pas ded dpon bsten pa ltar thar pa 'dod pa'i rim gro cher bya /
NK033(gi)008:124: khyad par du rab sgrub pa'i zhabs tog gis sgrub brgyud kyi bstan pa zin pa /
NK033(gi)008:125: 'bring lus ngag gi zhabs tog gis sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyong ba /
NK033(gi)008:126: tha ma zang zing gi yo byad kyis tshogs gnyis
NK033(gi)008:127: kyi bre kha khengs pa gang rung gis cis kyang
NK033(gi)008:128: mnyes pa bsgrub par bya ste /
NK033(gi)008:130: de ltar man ngag slob dpon la //
NK033(gi)008:131: rang lus dang ni rin chen rdzas //
NK033(gi)008:132: shin tu dkon pa dag gis bsten //
NK033(gi)008:133: zhes gsungs shing de'i yon tan kyang /
NK033(gi)008:135: nam mkha' gang ba'i sangs rgyas la //
NK033(gi)008:136: sna tshogs rin chen spras pa yi //
NK033(gi)008:137: stong gsum gang ba phul bas kyang //
NK033(gi)008:138: bla ma'i ba spu nyag gcig la //
NK033(gi)008:139: mar gyi thig pa gcig byugs na //
NK033(gi)008:140: bsod nams brgya phrag char mi phod //
NK033(gi)008:142: gzhan yang sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa 'dag cing kun gyis mthong na dga' ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:143: bsod nams dang 'byor pa 'phel zhing mkha' 'gros stong grogs byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:144: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad dka' ba med par thob pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:145: dam tshig mchog gi rgyud las /
NK033(gi)008:146: dngos grub 'dod pa'i dad pa can //
NK033(gi)008:147: dngos grub bla ma mnyes las 'byung //
NK033(gi)008:149: bzhi pa mthun rkyen gyi gzhi bzung ba la bzhi //
NK033(gi)008:156: lung stong gangs khrod ri rtse dur khrod dam //
NK033(gi)008:157: shin tu dben zhing dwangs mtho bsil ba'i sar //
NK033(gi)008:158: skal ldan skyes bu'i nyams len byed pa'i gnas //
NK033(gi)008:159: bsam gtan 'phel zhing brtan pa myur du thob //
NK033(gi)008:160: ces pas sgrub pa'i gnas spyir yid dang mthun pa /
NK033(gi)008:161: dgra rkun sogs kyi 'tshe ba med cing skye bo'i
NK033(gi)008:162: rgyu 'grul dang ca co sogs kyi rnam g.yeng chung
NK033(gi)008:163: ba / sa phyogs bkra shis shing gzhi bdag chos la dkar ba /
NK033(gi)008:164: bla ma dang mkha' 'gro dang grub thob gong mas byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas /
NK033(gi)008:165: gangs ri nags khrod brag ri la sogs pa rang
NK033(gi)008:166: bzhin gyis rig pa dwangs shing sa phyogs mtho ba
NK033(gi)008:167: / shar gyi mdangs 'phrogs shing nub kyi zer sdud
NK033(gi)008:168: pa zhes nyi ma snga mo 'char zhing phyi mor
NK033(gi)008:169: nub pas nyi tshe ring ba /
NK033(gi)008:171: mthun rkyen thams cad rnyed par sla ba'i gnas su bsgrub par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:173: dus dang tshes grangs gza' skar sogs bzang ba la 'jug dgos shing /
NK033(gi)008:174: khyad par thod rgal bsgom pa'i dus ni /
NK033(gi)008:175: dbyar ma ston dang dgun chung dpyid kyi dus //
NK033(gi)008:176: zer gnyis dus ni mchog tu bshad pa yin //
NK033(gi)008:178: dus der bsil drod snyoms pa'i dbang gi byings rmugs kyi rkyen nyung zhing /
NK033(gi)008:179: bye brag 'char nub kyi zer gnyis te ye shes
NK033(gi)008:180: 'char ba'i rkyen du 'gyur bas ngo sprod kyi dus
NK033(gi)008:181: su bshad pa'i phyir de dang bstun par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:183: 'tsho ba'i yo byad zas skom dang gos stan /
NK033(gi)008:184: bsten pa'i yo byad dam rdzas /
NK033(gi)008:185: mkho ba'i yo byad rdo rje dril bu sogs /
NK033(gi)008:186: mthun pa'i yo byad sman dang rten 'brel gyi rdzas /
NK033(gi)008:187: khyad par gyi yo byad dbang yon dang gtor tshogs
NK033(gi)008:188: kyi rgyu la sogs pa mdor na gang gi phyir
NK033(gi)008:189: yang gnas skabs de dag tu brel mi dgos par
NK033(gi)008:191: phyag rten me tog dbang yon gtor tshogs rgyu //
NK033(gi)008:192: nyams len dus su khams kyi rten so btsal //
NK033(gi)008:193: mthun pa'i yo byad kun dang ldan par bya //
NK033(gi)008:196: zab lam sgom pa'i nyams myong can nam /
NK033(gi)008:197: min kyang rgyud zhi dul dang ldan cing dam tshig gtsang ba /
NK033(gi)008:198: dag snang 'byongs shing nyon mongs shas chung ba /
NK033(gi)008:199: brtse sems che bas mthun rkyen sbyor ba la skyo
NK033(gi)008:200: ngal med pa nyid bsten par bya ba klong gsal
NK033(gi)008:201: las gsungs so // gnyis pa khrid tshul gdams ngag dngos rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK033(gi)008:202: nges shes skyed pa lo rgyus /
NK033(gi)008:205: bsgoms pa las byung ba'i 'bras bu /
NK033(gi)008:206: zhar byung lag len gyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:209: skal ldan nges shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)008:210: brgyud pa'i lo rgyus bshad par bya //
NK033(gi)008:216: gdod ma'i dbyings su chos thams cad kyi chos nyid
NK033(gi)008:217: ka dag gi spros pa'i mtha' thams cad bral ba'i
NK033(gi)008:218: klong nas / bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang
NK033(gi)008:219: po yab yum gnyis lhun grub ye shes kyi skur
NK033(gi)008:220: bzhengs nas rang snang gi 'khor rgyal tshab rigs lnga
NK033(gi)008:221: klong nas / dang / rgyal sras sems dpa' sogs
NK033(gi)008:222: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i tshogs la rdzogs pa chen
NK033(gi)008:223: po sgra tshig bya rtsol las 'das pa dus kun
NK033(gi)008:224: mnyam pa nyid du brjod med kyi sgo nas gsungs
NK033(gi)008:225: klong nas / dang / so // gnyis pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:226: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes dur khrod
NK033(gi)008:227: me ri 'bar ba'i gnas su sprul sku mchog dga'
NK033(gi)008:228: rab rdo rje la chos nyid don gyi gnas lugs
NK033(gi)008:229: nyid chos can bya rtsol las 'das pa tshig sdeb
NK033(gi)008:230: sbyor legs pa'i sgo nas bshad /
NK033(gi)008:231: des dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal du slob
NK033(gi)008:232: dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la chos nyid bya rtsol
NK033(gi)008:234: des so sa gling gi dur khrod du rig 'dzin
NK033(gi)008:235: sh+r+ai sim ha la mngon sum rang thog tu phab
NK033(gi)008:236: nas gsungs / des dur khrod chen po bsil sbyin
NK033(gi)008:237: du slob dpon dz+ny+aa na s+au tra la mngon sum
NK033(gi)008:239: des dur khrod chen po b+ha sing du pan chen
NK033(gi)008:240: bi ma la mi tra la gnas lugs go rtogs
NK033(gi)008:241: dang bral bar ye shes gong 'pho'i tshul du brda'
NK033(gi)008:242: dang brda'i sgo nas gsungs pa ni rig 'dzin brda
NK033(gi)008:244: pan chen bi ma la nyid kyis mnga' bdag rgyal po dang /
NK033(gi)008:245: myang ban ting 'dzin bzang po sogs la gsang ba
NK033(gi)008:246: bla na med pa'i gdams pa rnams mnog chos su
NK033(gi)008:247: gnang zhing / myang ban nyid kyis brgyud pa'i bka'
NK033(gi)008:248: srol mi nyams pa'i ched du snyan brgyud rnams 'bro
NK033(gi)008:249: rin chen 'bar dang spas blo gros dbang phyug gnyis
NK033(gi)008:250: gnang zhing / la gtad / dpe brgyud rnams ma
NK033(gi)008:251: 'ongs pa'i gdul byar dgongs te dbu ru zhwa'i lha
NK033(gi)008:252: khang du spas pa phyis gnas brtan ldang ma lhun
NK033(gi)008:254: snyan brgyud kyang btsal nas gsan pas bka' gter chu bo gcig 'dres su gyur /
NK033(gi)008:255: des lce btsun seng ge dbang phyug la gnang /
NK033(gi)008:256: lce btsun chen pos kyang zab pa pod bzhi sogs
NK033(gi)008:257: gter nas bzhes shing khyad par byar gyi phu brag
NK033(gi)008:258: dkar them pa 'dra bar pan chen bi la mi
NK033(gi)008:259: tras gdams ngag rnams rdzogs par zla ba bdun du
NK033(gi)008:260: stsal / 'o yug phyi gong rdzas ra bar 'od kyi skur gshegs /
NK033(gi)008:261: des zhang ston bkra shis rdo rje /
NK033(gi)008:262: des lce btsun gyi sras mkhas pa nyi ma 'bum /
NK033(gi)008:263: des chos bdag gu ru jo 'ber /
NK033(gi)008:264: der 'khrul zhig seng ge rgyab ba /
NK033(gi)008:265: des grub thob zla ba mun sel /
NK033(gi)008:266: des rig 'dzin chen po ku m+aa r+aa dza /
NK033(gi)008:267: des mkhas grub kun gyi gtsug rgyan chen po 'gran
NK033(gi)008:268: zla thams cad dang bral ba kun mkhyen chos kyi
NK033(gi)008:269: rgyal po la gdams pa rdzogs par gnang ba yin
NK033(gi)008:271: sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud las lung bstan pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:273: de nas blo gros mchog gis 'dzin //
NK033(gi)008:274: ces mtshan gyi rnam grangs tshul khrims blo gros zhes mtshan gyi 'brel dang /
NK033(gi)008:275: shes bya la chags thogs med pa'i mkhyen rab kyi rtsal kha rgyas pas don du 'brel gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:278: zhes par yang ngos 'dzin cing spyir rnam par thar pa bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK033(gi)008:279: khyad par 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i chos 'khor
NK033(gi)008:280: gzhan dring mi 'jog par bskor ba kun tu bzang
NK033(gi)008:281: po bshes gnyen gyi rnam par snang ba yin no
NK033(gi)008:283: sa la gnas pa'i byang sems kyis //
NK033(gi)008:284: rgya mtsho'i bar du spel bar byed //
NK033(gi)008:285: ces lung bstan pa'i rgyal ba'i dbang po gsum pa
NK033(gi)008:286: rang byung rdo rjes thog mar rig 'dzin ku m+aa
NK033(gi)008:287: r+aa dza las gsang ba snying thig gi gdams khrid
NK033(gi)008:288: rdzogs par gsan / phyis bi ma las dngos su rjes su bzung ba ste /
NK033(gi)008:290: bdag ni bi ma la yis byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)008:291: karma'i yang dgon dben par 'dug pa'i tshe //
NK033(gi)008:292: nam langs dus mthar shar gyi phyogs rol nas //
NK033(gi)008:293: lta bas mi ngoms 'od kyis mdzes pa zhig /
NK033(gi)008:294: mngon sum ltar snang bdag gi mdzod spur thim //
NK033(gi)008:295: de nas 'bad med gnad 'di thams cad go //
NK033(gi)008:296: zhes gsungs pa ltar de la brten nas rdzogs pa
NK033(gi)008:297: chen po'i rgyud 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dgongs
NK033(gi)008:298: pa bde blag tu mkhyen pa'i tshul bstan /
NK033(gi)008:299: dgongs pa'i klong nas brdol ba'i karma snying thig ces mdzad cing /
NK033(gi)008:300: mkhas grub kyi zhal slob bzhi la bi ma la
NK033(gi)008:301: dang pad+ma'i snying thig gi chos rnams dbus gtsang khams
NK033(gi)008:302: gsum rgya nag la sogs pa rnams su spel bar
NK033(gi)008:303: bka' bsgos pas lung gi don mngon du gyur /
NK033(gi)008:304: des na skyes bu chen po 'di gnyis ni rdzogs
NK033(gi)008:305: chen bstan pa'i bdag po sgo thams cad nas 'gran
NK033(gi)008:306: zla dang bral ba yin cing /
NK033(gi)008:307: gnyis ka'i bla ma rig 'dzin ku m+aa ra yin pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:308: karma snying thig kyang tshig gi brjod pa phran bu'i
NK033(gi)008:309: khyad par las tshig don gnyis ka'i char bi ma
NK033(gi)008:310: snying thig dang khyad par ci'ang med pa ma zad
NK033(gi)008:311: gong ma rnams la bi ma snying thig ma bu
NK033(gi)008:312: dang karma snying thig gi brgyud srol chu bo gcig
NK033(gi)008:313: 'dres su gyur pas nyams len dang 'chad spel gang
NK033(gi)008:314: byas kyang gcig go gcig chod nges par yong ba
NK033(gi)008:315: yin ces kun mkhyen bstan pa'i nyin byed sogs kyis
NK033(gi)008:316: yang yang gsungs / 'on kyang 'dir gtso bor 'chad bya snying thig ma bu'i brgyud srol ni /
NK033(gi)008:317: kun mkhyen klong chen pa la /
NK033(gi)008:318: don gnyis mtha' ru phyin pa'i slob ma skyes chen mang du byon pa las /
NK033(gi)008:319: brgyud pa gtso che ba'i dbang gis mkhas grub khyab brdal lhun grub 'dir 'dren cing /
NK033(gi)008:321: des 'khrul zhig sangs rgyas dbon po //
NK033(gi)008:322: des kun mkhyen zla ba grags pa /
NK033(gi)008:323: des grub chen kun bzang rdo rje /
NK033(gi)008:324: des mtshungs med rgyal mtshan dpal bzang /
NK033(gi)008:325: des sprul sku sna tshogs rang grol /
NK033(gi)008:326: des grub mchog bstan 'dzin grags pa /
NK033(gi)008:327: des mkhas grub mdo sngags bstan 'dzin /
NK033(gi)008:328: des rig 'dzin phrin las lhun grub /
NK033(gi)008:329: des chos kyi rgyal po rgyan gter bdag gling pa la gnang /
NK033(gi)008:330: rje 'di'i phyag bzhes su bi ma la'i man ngag
NK033(gi)008:331: snying thig chen mo zhes yongs su grags pa dang
NK033(gi)008:332: / de nyid la chos rje kun mkhyen chen po
NK033(gi)008:333: dri med 'od zer gyis snying thig rtsa ba'i zab
NK033(gi)008:334: gnad gsal byed du mdzad pa'i bla ma yang thig
NK033(gi)008:335: gnyis gdams khrid so sor rang rkang du 'chad pa'ang
NK033(gi)008:336: / yod mod / gtso bor rtsa ba ma bu
NK033(gi)008:337: gnyis gang la brten kyang dmigs pa'i rkang grangs sems
NK033(gi)008:338: sbyor bdun sogs ngo bo mthun pa rnams gcig tu
NK033(gi)008:339: / yod mod / byas shing / sgos chos bye
NK033(gi)008:340: brag pa rnams man ngag gnyis bsdebs nas mdzad pa'i
NK033(gi)008:341: lugs srol 'di gnas skabs su 'jug pa bde zhing
NK033(gi)008:342: / yod mod / byas shing / / don gyi
NK033(gi)008:343: nyams len ma nor tshang phrugs su 'debs pa'i zab
NK033(gi)008:344: gnad gcig grogs gcig 'gro'i gnad kyis gnyis ka'i gdams
NK033(gi)008:345: khrid thob pa'i kun go gcig chod du 'gyur bar
NK033(gi)008:346: mdzad pa'i rgyun ni da lta'i phyag bzhes 'di nyid
NK033(gi)008:347: / yod mod / byas shing / / yin no // gter chen bla mas /
NK033(gi)008:348: rang sras bi ma'i sprul pa 'gyur med rin chen rnam rgyal dang /
NK033(gi)008:349: rje btsun ma mi 'gyur dpal gyi sgron ma sogs la stsal zhing /
NK033(gi)008:352: bstan pa 'di nyid bzung nas ni //
NK033(gi)008:353: tshe lo bcu pa'i dus su dar //
NK033(gi)008:354: de nas mi gnas rang sa 'o //
NK033(gi)008:355: zhes pa'i lung gis bstan pa ltar mkhyen rtogs 'gran
NK033(gi)008:356: zla dang bral zhing bstan pa'i rgyan la bka' drin
NK033(gi)008:358: khyad par snying thig ma bu'i khrid yig bde chen
NK033(gi)008:359: lam bzang sogs snying thig gdams srol gyi mig tu
NK033(gi)008:360: gyur pa'i yig cha'ang mang du mdzad cing /
NK033(gi)008:361: lcam dral dam pa de gnyis kyis g.yu sgra'i sprul pa mkhan chen o rgyan bstan 'dzin rdo rje /
NK033(gi)008:362: des gnubs chen yang srid khri chen phrin las rnam rgyal /
NK033(gi)008:363: des gter chen rnam 'phrul khri chen pad+ma dbang rgyal /
NK033(gi)008:364: de la dpal ldan dpa' bo gtsug lag chos rgyal
NK033(gi)008:365: gyis gsan pa las brgyud de dbang lung tshang ma
NK033(gi)008:366: skyes chen dam pa mgon sprul karma gzhan phan mtha'
NK033(gi)008:368: yang khri chen phrin las rnam rgyal nas rje btsun rin po che 'gyur med phrin las chos sgron /
NK033(gi)008:369: de las pan chen bi ma la'i rnam 'phrul klong
NK033(gi)008:370: chen gnyis pa kun mkhyen rdo rje gzi brjid rtsal
NK033(gi)008:371: gyis gsan / des kho bo cag la thugs brtse
NK033(gi)008:372: ba chen pos smin grol rgya mtsho lta bu'i bcud
NK033(gi)008:373: du stsal ba ni dbang lung khrid dang nyams rtogs
NK033(gi)008:374: bar ma chad pa'i brgyud tshul shin tu khyad par
NK033(gi)008:376: spyir snying thig ya bzhi zhes yongs su grags pa la gnyis bi ma dang /
NK033(gi)008:377: gnyis pad+ma snying thig yin la /
NK033(gi)008:378: de'i ngos 'dzin rnying phyogs phal mo ches bi ma'i snying thig chen mo /
NK033(gi)008:379: de'i bcud 'dril bla ma yang tig gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:380: las 'brel rtsal gyi gter ma mkha' 'gro snying thig /
NK033(gi)008:381: de'i zab gnad mkha' 'gro yang tig ste bzhir bzhed la /
NK033(gi)008:382: yang tig gnyis ni kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams kyi dgongs pa'i gter las 'khrungs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:383: kong po rdzogs chen pa dang rig 'dzin tshe dbang nor bu sogs ni /
NK033(gi)008:384: bi ma snying tig ma bu gnyis so sor bgrang /
NK033(gi)008:385: mkha' 'gro snying tig ma bu gcig tu bsdams /
NK033(gi)008:386: de steng rdor sems snying tig bcas bzhir bzhed cing
NK033(gi)008:387: phyi ma la bka' bab rim pa gsum mchis pa
NK033(gi)008:388: 'di ni bee ro'i snying tig gi mtshan gazhi'o //
NK033(gi)008:389: yang kha cig ni rdor sems snying thig mi bgrang
NK033(gi)008:390: bar karma snying thig bcas bzhir byed pa'ang snang la
NK033(gi)008:391: / rje rang byung bas las 'brel rtsal la mkha'
NK033(gi)008:392: 'gro snying tig gsan pa'i gter brgyud kyang da lta'i
NK033(gi)008:393: bar zam ma chad par bzhugs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:394: kho bo cag gis kyang de dag thams cad skal
NK033(gi)008:395: pa bzang po'i dpyid du nos pas sgo thams cad
NK033(gi)008:396: nas chu bo gcig 'dres su gyur pa ma zad
NK033(gi)008:397: / karma snying thig sger gyi brgyud pa'ang rang byung
NK033(gi)008:398: zhabs nas nyams khrid bar ma chad pa rim par
NK033(gi)008:399: / brgyud / dpal ldan dpal bo rdo rje gtsug lag dga' ba /
NK033(gi)008:401: rje bcu gsum pa bdud 'dul rdo rje /
NK033(gi)008:402: dpa' bo gtsug lag chos rgyal /
NK033(gi)008:403: thams cad mkhyen pa rgyal dbang karma pa theg pa
NK033(gi)008:404: mchog gi rdo rjes lung khrid kyi tshul du bka'
NK033(gi)008:405: drin stsal ba'o // 'dir mdo tsam smos pa yin la /
NK033(gi)008:406: rgyas par na gsang ba snying thig gi bab lugs chen mo'am /
NK033(gi)008:407: yang tig gi lo rgyus rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK033(gi)008:408: gter chen rin po ches mdzad pa'i snying thig ma
NK033(gi)008:409: bu'i brgyud pa'i kha skong nges shes 'dren pa'i lcags
NK033(gi)008:411: gnyis pa smin par byed pa dbang la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:416: dbang ni rnam pa bzhi yis kyang //
NK033(gi)008:417: skal ba ldan pa smin par bya //
NK033(gi)008:418: spros bcas nyid dang spros pa med //
NK033(gi)008:419: shin tu spros pa med pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:420: de bzhin rab tu spros pa med //
NK033(gi)008:421: dbye ba bzhi yi tshul gyis ni //
NK033(gi)008:422: skal ldan rang rgyud smin par byed //
NK033(gi)008:424: de'i spyir yo ga rnam pa gsum gyi skabs 'dir
NK033(gi)008:425: theg pa 'og ma ltar dka' spyad sogs la ma
NK033(gi)008:426: brten par / dug lnga lam khyer gyi gdams pas
NK033(gi)008:427: rnam smin kun rtog gi bag chags thabs khyad par
NK033(gi)008:429: rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum du ston par byed pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:430: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las gtor ba'am blugs pa zhes
NK033(gi)008:431: 'byung bas med snang 'khor ba'i bag chags ma lus
NK033(gi)008:432: pa dag par byed pa'i cha nas gtor ba dang
NK033(gi)008:433: / gzhi'i ngo bo gdod nas sku gsum rang chas
NK033(gi)008:434: su bzhugs pa nyid mthong gsal du byed pas blugs
NK033(gi)008:436: khyad par 'dir ni snang srid ye dag chos nyid
NK033(gi)008:437: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du rang bzhin spros
NK033(gi)008:438: bral rdzogs pa chen por dbang bskur nas gcer mthong
NK033(gi)008:440: de yang gang zag dbang rab rnams ni dbang dus su grol ba thob pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:441: 'bring gis brda don 'phrod de ye shes phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:442: tha mas kyang rgyud la thar pa'i sa bon 'jog pa yin te /
NK033(gi)008:443: dbang gi las kyis thar pa'i myu gu mngon du bskyed pa'am /
NK033(gi)008:444: skye nges kyi nus rung du smin pa /
NK033(gi)008:446: 'dir man ngag ma bu gnyis bsdebs kyi tshul du
NK033(gi)008:447: gnang yang dbang rnams bla ma yang thig gi nang
NK033(gi)008:448: ltar dang / bskur lugs kyang dang po khrid kyi sngon du spros bcas kyi dbang /
NK033(gi)008:449: khregs chod kyi sngon du spros med /
NK033(gi)008:450: thod rgal gyi sngon du shin tu spros med dang
NK033(gi)008:451: rab tu spros med gnyis sprel mar mdzad pa phyag
NK033(gi)008:452: bzhes yin no // gnyis pa dam tshig ni /
NK033(gi)008:454: dbang rten pa yi dam tshig ni //
NK033(gi)008:455: bye brag brjod kyis mi lang yang //
NK033(gi)008:456: mdor bsdus sku gsung thugs nyid bsrung //
NK033(gi)008:457: zhes pas bsrung bya'i don las nam yang mi 'da' ba'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:459: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gongs //
NK033(gi)008:460: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK033(gi)008:461: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK033(gi)008:463: dbye na sku gsung thugs re rer phyi'i phyi /
NK033(gi)008:466: de bzhin nang gsang gnyis la'ang sbyar bas rnam grangs nyi shu rtsa bdun /
NK033(gi)008:467: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi dam rdzas sha lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga sogs gsang bar 'os pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:468: bla ma dang mched rnams kyis spang blang bstan pa rnams gsang bar gnyen gtad pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:469: mdor na rang gis ji ltar khas blangs pa'i rtsa
NK033(gi)008:470: ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig thams cad bag
NK033(gi)008:471: yod dran shes ma bral ba'i sgo nas bsrung dgos
NK033(gi)008:472: te / dri med rgyal po bshags pa'i rgyud las /
NK033(gi)008:473: dam tshig sa gzhi lta bu la //
NK033(gi)008:474: thams cad 'bras bu lo tog smin //
NK033(gi)008:476: dam tshig mchog gi rgyud las /
NK033(gi)008:478: rdo rje 'dzin pa rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK033(gi)008:479: tshe 'di nyid la thob par nges //
NK033(gi)008:481: nyams len dngos gzhi 'bras bu rgyud la skye min thams cad 'di la rags las so //
NK033(gi)008:482: gsum pa grol bar byed pa khrid kyi rim pa bstan pa la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:485: tha ma rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams su grol ba bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:487: dmigs gtad gsal bar byed pa'i sgron me zhes bya
NK033(gi)008:488: ba nyams su len pa'i sgom khrigs chen mo las
NK033(gi)008:489: / dang po rigs pa gcer mthong la yid ma ches na /
NK033(gi)008:490: grub mtha' ngan par log par 'byung dogs srid pas /
NK033(gi)008:491: sngon du byang chub sems sbyong gi man ngag la bslab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:492: de nas sems 'byongs pa'i drod rtags gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:493: gsang sngags gzhan dag gi man ngag gis lam du drangs te /
NK033(gi)008:494: gang zag chags pa can dang chags pa med pa gnyis su byas nas /
NK033(gi)008:495: rtsa dang rlung dang thig le la bslab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:496: de lta rtsa rlung gi drod rtags gtan la phebs nas //
NK033(gi)008:497: dran pa rgyun gcod kyi man ngag gis rig pa nyid 'byung ba las ldog par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:498: de ltar 'byung ba lnga las bzlog nas /
NK033(gi)008:499: sbas pa mig 'byed kyi man ngag gis spyod pa sgom pa lta ba 'bras bu'i 'dug tshul blta /
NK033(gi)008:501: spyod pa sogs bzhi skor gyi gdams pa'i khrid tshul
NK033(gi)008:502: rgyas par bstan pa dang yang tig yid zhin nor
NK033(gi)008:503: bu'i rtsa ba'i sa bcad zung 'brel lag tu len
NK033(gi)008:504: pa la don gsum du bsdus te /
NK033(gi)008:505: lam sgom pa'i snod rung du bya ba sngon 'gro'i khrid bstan pa /
NK033(gi)008:506: dngos gzhi sems rig gtan la 'bebs pa 'od gsal snying po'i don khrid bstan pa /
NK033(gi)008:507: rjes gnad bzhi chos nyid kyi 'khor los chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bya ba'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:509: zab lam sgom pa'i mtshams sbyor med du mi rung ba thun gyi sngon 'gro bstan pa /
NK033(gi)008:510: gsang ba snying tig gi khyad chos sems sbyong bdun gyis lam gyi gzhi bca' ba /
NK033(gi)008:511: thun mong sngon 'gro bzhi sbyor gyis rgyud dag par byed pa /
NK033(gi)008:512: gsang sngags spyi mthun gyi thabs lam rlung thig gis lus sems sbyong ba /
NK033(gi)008:513: dran pa rgyun gcod kyi man ngag gis 'byung lnga rang sar dengs par byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:514: dang po thun gyi sngon 'gro ni /
NK033(gi)008:515: gnas dben par bde ba'i stan la lus gnad rnam snang chos bdun drang por bsrang /
NK033(gi)008:516: de'ang khrid rim sgom phyin chad spyi dang bye brag
NK033(gi)008:517: gi lus gnad skabs su babs par 'cha' ba las
NK033(gi)008:518: / lus nyal ba dang bsnyes pa sogs tha mal du nam yang sdod mi rung ste /
NK033(gi)008:519: de'i rgyu mtshan lus grong khyer dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)008:522: rnam shes mi zha bo dang 'dra bas byed pa
NK033(gi)008:523: bcings na srang sgo khegs pas mi rta nang du
NK033(gi)008:524: tshud de 'gro mi thub pa dang 'dra ste /
NK033(gi)008:525: dper na sbrul la yan lag yod kyang ma gcus na mi gsal ba bzhin /
NK033(gi)008:526: lus ma gcun na sems mi gnas pas rten 'brel
NK033(gi)008:527: lus la bsgrigs pas rtogs pa sems la 'char ba
NK033(gi)008:528: zhes gong ma rnams kyis zab mo'i gdams ngag gi
NK033(gi)008:530: de nas thun dang por rlung ro dgu phrugs 'og ma rnams la sum phrugs su bsal te /
NK033(gi)008:532: sna bug g.yon nas chung 'bring che gsum /
NK033(gi)008:534: gnyis ka chab gcig chung 'bring che gsum bsal ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:535: gnyis pa ni g.yon g.yas dbus nas lan re bsal /
NK033(gi)008:536: de'i tshe rang gzhan sems can thams cad kyi tshe
NK033(gi)008:537: rabs thog ma med pa nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib
NK033(gi)008:538: gegs dang bar chad mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad
NK033(gi)008:539: 'ub kyis 'dus nas sna sgo'i rlung dang 'grogs te
NK033(gi)008:540: phyir sang sang song bas lus kyi nang bshal btang
NK033(gi)008:541: ba ltar dag par gyur snyam du bsam mo //
NK033(gi)008:542: 'di ni dper na bcud bzang po zhig blugs par
NK033(gi)008:543: byed pa la snga logs su snod bkru bshal byed
NK033(gi)008:544: pa lta bu'o // de nas mkha' mnyam gyi sems
NK033(gi)008:545: can thams cad kyi don du man ngag rdzogs pa
NK033(gi)008:546: chen po'i gdams pa zab mo 'di nyid nyams su
NK033(gi)008:547: blang snyam du sems bskyed dung ba zhig sngon du
NK033(gi)008:548: pa lta bu'o // btang rjes / dpal ldan rtsa ba'i bla ma rin po che //
NK033(gi)008:549: bdag gi spyi bor pad+ma'i gdan bzhugs la //
NK033(gi)008:550: bka' drin chen po'i sgo nas rjes bzung ste //
NK033(gi)008:551: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)008:552: zhes brjod pas rang gi spyi bor pad+ma dang nyi
NK033(gi)008:553: zla'i gdan la ngo bo drin chen rtsa ba'i bla
NK033(gi)008:554: ma nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pa can
NK033(gi)008:555: / mtshan dpe rab tu rdzogs pa'i sku dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)008:556: phyag gnyis rdor dril 'dzin cing zhabs sems skyil gyis bzhugs pa zhig gsal btab nas ngag tu /
NK033(gi)008:557: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo bla ma rin po che mkhyen /
NK033(gi)008:558: bdag gi rgyud smin cing grol bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)008:561: zab lam gyi rtogs pa khyad par can rgyud la skye bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)008:562: tshe 'di nyid la phyag chen po mchog gi dngos
NK033(gi)008:563: grub myur du thob par byin gyis brlab tu gsol
NK033(gi)008:564: / zhes 'dod pa'i don la zhe thag pa nas gsol ba phur tshugs su btab pas /
NK033(gi)008:565: bla ma'i zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe bong las bdud rtsi dkar po'i rgyun babs /
NK033(gi)008:566: rang gi tshangs bug nas zhugs /
NK033(gi)008:567: lus thams cad gang bde ba chen po'i ye shes skyes /
NK033(gi)008:568: mthar bla ma 'od du zhu nas rang la thim
NK033(gi)008:569: pas rgyud byin gyis brlabs par bsams la rig pa
NK033(gi)008:571: 'di la rig 'dzin tshe dbang nor bu'i gsung rgyun
NK033(gi)008:572: du bla ma gzhi'i kun bzang gi rnam par mdun
NK033(gi)008:573: mkhar thig le sngon po'i dbus su bsgoms nas gsol
NK033(gi)008:574: ba btab rjes h'u mthing gar gyur pa 'chad 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:575: rdo rje'i lte bar byon par mos gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:576: 'di nyid kun mkhyen gyi gzhung khrid du dngos su
NK033(gi)008:577: ma bstan kyang rdo rje lam bstan nas thun mtshams
NK033(gi)008:578: thams cad du bsgom par gsungs pa ltar 'dir phyag
NK033(gi)008:580: der bla ma dngos sam rdor sems gang rung du
NK033(gi)008:581: bsgom par gsungs pa ltar rang byung zhabs kyis kyang
NK033(gi)008:582: de nyid drangs par mdzad do //
NK033(gi)008:583: gang ltar de'i mthar rang rdo rje sngon po rtse
NK033(gi)008:584: gsum par bsgoms na rdo rje'i 'dug stangs byas pas
NK033(gi)008:585: bar chad med pa'i rten 'brel dang /
NK033(gi)008:586: don dam gyi srung 'khor mchog tu 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:587: gnyis pa gsang ba snying tig gi khyad chos sems sbyong bdun gyis lam gyi gzhi bca' ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:590: rigs kyi bu rnams nyon cig /
NK033(gi)008:591: rig pa mngon sum gyi snang ba la blo mi
NK033(gi)008:592: phebs shing dbang po dman pa skal ba zhan pa'i
NK033(gi)008:593: mi rnams kyis 'di la yid mi ches pa 'ga'
NK033(gi)008:594: 'byung srid pas / de dag rnams rig pa mthong
NK033(gi)008:595: bar bya ba'i ched du 'di rnams la bslab par
NK033(gi)008:597: rkyen med pa'i phyogs su phyi nang gi bya ba btang ste /
NK033(gi)008:598: bsam gtan gyi 'jig pa rnams spangs la dang po sems sbyang bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:599: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pa ltar 'di la bdun /
NK033(gi)008:606: rnam par mi rtog pa la brten nas sems sbyong ba rnams so //
NK033(gi)008:607: dang po mi rtag pa la bsams te sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:608: phyi nam zla dus bzhi'i 'gyur ldog /
NK033(gi)008:609: nyin mtshan skad cig thang cig gis kyang mi rtag pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:610: nang 'byung bzhi'i phung po 'gyur ldog chu'i lbu ba
NK033(gi)008:611: spungs pa dang 'dra ba myur du 'jig cing snying
NK033(gi)008:612: po med pas kyang mi rtag pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:613: gsang ba pha ma gnyen 'dun shi bas kyang mi rtag pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:614: rang la'ang de lta bu'i gnas skabs nam 'byung na ang /
NK033(gi)008:615: de ring sang tsam la'ang mi 'chi ba'i gdings med de /
NK033(gi)008:616: do nub 'achi'am sang 'achi'am snyam du snying nas skad cig kyang ma yengs par bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)008:617: sems can gzhan mthong ba la'ang 'di kun kyang 'chi ba las ma 'das so //
NK033(gi)008:619: des na 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa'i rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)008:620: mi rtag pa'i dpe mthong nas blo sna thung du song ba ni 'byongs pa'i tshad do //
NK033(gi)008:621: de ltar bsgoms pas 'khor ba las blo ldog pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:622: de nyid gsal gdab pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)008:623: phyi rol nyin mtshan dus bzhi'i 'gyur ldog dang //
NK033(gi)008:624: nang gi phung po gsang ba gnyen 'dun sogs //
NK033(gi)008:625: 'dus byas chos rnams mi rtag myur du 'jig /
NK033(gi)008:626: snying po med pa chu lbur lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)008:628: gnyis pa 'phral gyi bde ba dang yun gyi bde
NK033(gi)008:629: ba la bsam ste sems sbyong ba ni las mi
NK033(gi)008:630: dge bas ngan song dang sdug bsngal gyi rigs thams
NK033(gi)008:631: cad bskyed la / dge bas mtho ris dang bde ba'i rigs thams cad bskyed cing /
NK033(gi)008:632: 'khor ba mtho dman gyi rang bzhin zo chu'i 'khyud mo 'dra ba /
NK033(gi)008:633: 'pho zhing rtag mi thub pa 'di mtshang re che /
NK033(gi)008:634: 'khor bar mi 'jug pa'i thabs dam pa /
NK033(gi)008:635: thar pa'i byang chub ma gtogs par yid brtan mi rung zhing bslu ba 'di ya cha /
NK033(gi)008:636: thar pa'i lam du zhugs na 'phral gyi bde ba
NK033(gi)008:637: mtho ris dang yon tan bzang po rgyud la 'thob
NK033(gi)008:638: ste rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa' rnams bzhin no
NK033(gi)008:639: // yun gyi bde ba bla na med pa'i byang chub 'grub ste sangs rgyas rnams bzhin no //
NK033(gi)008:640: de bas na gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi bde
NK033(gi)008:641: ba phun sum tshogs pa bsgrub par bya snyam du
NK033(gi)008:642: bsam mo // des na thar pa'i lam du ma tshud na /
NK033(gi)008:643: dge ba byas pas mtho ris su skyes kyang /
NK033(gi)008:644: slar ngan song du 'khor ba'i phyir /
NK033(gi)008:645: byas pa thams cad sdug bsngal gyi rgyur 'dug ang
NK033(gi)008:646: snyam pa snying nas byung ba ni goms pa'i tshad
NK033(gi)008:647: do // des ni 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las yid
NK033(gi)008:648: dbyung nas skyo shas drag po rgyud la skye ba'i
NK033(gi)008:651: dge sdig 'bras bus rigs drug gnas su 'khor //
NK033(gi)008:652: srid pa'i bde 'byor dug can kha zas bzhin //
NK033(gi)008:653: ltar snang bde yang nam phugs sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK033(gi)008:654: nges legs thar pa'i lam mchog kho na'o //
NK033(gi)008:655: gsum pa rkyen du ma la bsam ste sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:656: 'khor bar skyes dus na yid brtan dang blo gtad mi 'dug ste /
NK033(gi)008:657: phan btags kyang phan lan du gnod pa bskyal ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:658: zas skom zos kyang nad dang 'chi rkyen du 'gro ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:659: yo byad bsags kyang dgra rkun gyi 'dod pa sgrub pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:660: phan du re nas gnyen bshes su btags pas gnod pa'i dgrar 'gyur ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:661: gnod pa ma byas kyang don med pa'i ngan smras dang skur par 'gyur ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:662: gang byas kyang gzhan gyi yid mi mgu ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:663: zin pa'i dus med pa 'di mtshang re che /
NK033(gi)008:664: sems can gyi bsam spyod la snying nas bsams na gang ltar phan btags kyang /
NK033(gi)008:665: la la mgu dus la la mi mgu /
NK033(gi)008:666: ji ltar bsams kyang mtha' gcig tu phan med /
NK033(gi)008:667: cis byas thams cad sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin /
NK033(gi)008:668: nad rkyen dang 'chi rkyen grangs mang ba 'di dag la dngos su phan pa mi 'grub pas /
NK033(gi)008:669: blo ltos mi bslu ba bla ma dkon mchog las
NK033(gi)008:670: gzhan med pa'i phyir mos gus dang mchod pa byas
NK033(gi)008:671: na 'di phyir bde ba'i rgyu yin pas /
NK033(gi)008:672: blo sna dge ba 'ba' zhig la bsgyur dgos snyam du rkyen bzang ngan sngar byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:674: phyis byed 'gyur rnams la bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)008:675: skyo shas dang blo sna bstung bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:676: des na rigs drug gi sems can rnams la snying rje skye zhing /
NK033(gi)008:678: bla ma mchod na ci ma rung snyam pa ni 'byongs pa'i tshad do //
NK033(gi)008:679: des ni dad pa sngon du 'gro ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:681: rkyen snang 'khrul pa'i bya ba zin dus med //
NK033(gi)008:682: ji ltar byas kyang 'dod thog bab mi 'gyur //
NK033(gi)008:683: smig rgyu'i chu la ri dwags snyegs pa bzhin //
NK033(gi)008:684: de bas blo sna dge la bsgyur bar bya //
NK033(gi)008:685: bzhi pa byas pa thams cad don med par sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:696: gtam snyan 'dod pa la sogs pa nas /
NK033(gi)008:697: gnyen grogs dang lhan cig longs spyod dang bshes 'dris /
NK033(gi)008:698: gnas khyim mkhar las la sogs pa ci dang ci
NK033(gi)008:699: byas kyang shi ba'i nangs par 'grogs nas mi 'gro
NK033(gi)008:701: khar sang phan chad kyi bya byed ci dang ci
NK033(gi)008:702: byas dran pa'i yul tsam las phyir mi 'ong bas
NK033(gi)008:704: de ring gi snang ba do nub kyi rmi lam dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)008:705: sang phan chad byed pa rnams kyang sang dgong gi
NK033(gi)008:706: rmi lam dang 'dra ba zhig yin par 'dug pa
NK033(gi)008:707: la / don med pa'i chags sdang dang /
NK033(gi)008:710: bde sdug gsog 'jog bya byed rnam pa sna tshogs
NK033(gi)008:711: pa zhig gis dus 'das pa 'di mtshang re che
NK033(gi)008:712: / 'jig rten gyi snang ba sgyu ma'i bslu brid du 'dug pa /
NK033(gi)008:713: de ring las ma gtogs pa lings kyis blos btang la /
NK033(gi)008:714: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag gcig rgyud la nyams su blangs dgos snyam du bsam mo //
NK033(gi)008:715: de nas snang ba gang la'ang blo gtad med pas
NK033(gi)008:716: bla ma'i gdams ngag zhig thob par bya dgos snyam
NK033(gi)008:717: pa dung gis byung ba ni 'byongs pa'i tshad do
NK033(gi)008:718: // des ni bla ma'i gdams ngag la 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:720: 'jig rten bya bzhag don med chags sdang gzhi //
NK033(gi)008:721: gnyid thun gcig gi rmi lam bzang ngan ltar //
NK033(gi)008:722: snang ba sgyu mas bslus pa mtshang re che //
NK033(gi)008:723: lings kyis bor te zab mo'i gdams ngag bsgom //
NK033(gi)008:724: lnga pa sangs rgyas kyi yon tan la brten nas sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:725: 'khor ba'i nyes pa thams cad las 'das pa ni sangs rgyas te /
NK033(gi)008:726: sku mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba /
NK033(gi)008:727: gsung chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba /
NK033(gi)008:728: thugs ye shes kyi ngang las mi g.yo ba /
NK033(gi)008:729: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi 'dren
NK033(gi)008:730: pa dam pa gtso bo gcig pu skyabs dang dpung
NK033(gi)008:731: gnyen du gyur pa yin pas thob par bya dgos
NK033(gi)008:732: / sangs ma rgyas na phan mi 'dug sangs rgyas
NK033(gi)008:733: thob par byed pa la'ang lam ma bsgoms na mi
NK033(gi)008:734: / thob pas / cis kyang bsgom dgos /
NK033(gi)008:735: grub thob gong ma ngo mtshar can rnams kyi rjes bsnyags la sgrub pa rtse gcig tu bya dgos /
NK033(gi)008:736: khong rnam pas dka' ba du ma spyod /
NK033(gi)008:737: gcig pur dben par bsgoms pas grol ba ltar bdag
NK033(gi)008:738: gis kyang tshe 'di'i bya ba blos btang la gcig
NK033(gi)008:739: pur dben pa'i gnas su bsgrub dgos snyam du bsam
NK033(gi)008:740: mo // des na ma bsgoms na sangs mi rgya bas /
NK033(gi)008:741: cis kyang bsgom dgos snyam pa rgyud la skyes pa ni 'byongs pa'i tshad do //
NK033(gi)008:742: des ni bsgom pa la bsran tshugs pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:744: sangs rgyas sku gsum yon tan tshad med ldan //
NK033(gi)008:745: rang la yod pa de nyid bsgoms na thob //
NK033(gi)008:746: skyes bu 'brum nad 'byongs bzhin mi ldog pas //
NK033(gi)008:747: gtan bde'i go 'phang dka' ba spyad la bsgrub //
NK033(gi)008:748: drug pa bla ma'i gdams ngag la bsam ste sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:749: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho gting mtha' med pa las sgrol ba'i ded dpon ni bla ma yin la /
NK033(gi)008:750: sgrol ba'i thabs kyi gru bo che ni bla ma'i gdams ngag yin pas /
NK033(gi)008:751: ji skad gsungs pa bzhin du nyams su blang dgos te /
NK033(gi)008:752: ma blangs na sdug bsngal gyi nad kyis gtan du
NK033(gi)008:753: gdung ba'i phyir na bla ma sman pa'i rgyal po
NK033(gi)008:754: ni brtse ba chen po ste /
NK033(gi)008:755: gdams ngag sman gyi bdud rtsis nyin mtshan bsran tshugs par byas /
NK033(gi)008:756: nyams su blang dgos snyam nas rgyu mtshan du ma la bsam ste bsgoms pas /
NK033(gi)008:758: bla ma'i gdams ngag kho na nyams su blang dgos snyam pa ni 'byongs pa'i tshad do //
NK033(gi)008:759: des ni bya ba gzhan la blo mi 'jug par
NK033(gi)008:760: gdams ngag la rtse gcig tu 'jug pa'i dgos pa
NK033(gi)008:761: yod do // de gsal gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:762: bla ma sman pa gdams ngag bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK033(gi)008:763: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i gru bo che //
NK033(gi)008:764: thar pa'i khang bzang bgrod pa'i them skas mchog /
NK033(gi)008:765: nyin mtshan bsran btsugs de don nyams su blang //
NK033(gi)008:766: bdun pa rnams par mi rtog pa la brten nas sems sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:768: rnam rtog ma rig chen po ste //
NK033(gi)008:769: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung byed yin //
NK033(gi)008:770: ces gsungs pas sngon chad ma rig pa'i rnam par
NK033(gi)008:771: rtog pas khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnas su yang nas
NK033(gi)008:772: yang du 'khor zhing 'khyams pas sdug bsngal bar 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:773: la / da ni bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK033(gi)008:774: thob pa zhig bya snyam pa'i sgo nas sbyong ba
NK033(gi)008:778: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa la brten nas sbyong ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:780: lus gnad chos bdun bcas la rang lus stong chen
NK033(gi)008:781: sgrib thogs dang bral ba'i dbus su rtsa dbu ma
NK033(gi)008:782: mda' smyug 'bring po tsam phyi dkar la nang dmar
NK033(gi)008:783: ba / dwangs gsal sbubs stong gi yar sna tshangs bug dang /
NK033(gi)008:784: mar sna lte 'og sor bzhi'i thad du drang thal ler gnas par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:785: de ltar gsal ba'i yas snar thabs kyi rang bzhin
NK033(gi)008:786: ham yig dkar po mgo bo thur lta bde ba'i
NK033(gi)008:788: mas snar shes rab kyi rang bzhin a yig dmar
NK033(gi)008:789: po mgo bo gyen bstan 'bar la khad pa zhig
NK033(gi)008:790: gsal btab / de ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang rlung ro gsum phrugs su gsal /
NK033(gi)008:791: de nas steng rlung nar gyis rngubs rjes 'og rlung
NK033(gi)008:792: bskums pas a las gtum mo'i me chos bzhi ldan
NK033(gi)008:793: gyen du 'bar ba dbu ma'i khong seng du dmar
NK033(gi)008:794: khyug gis song / spyi bo'i ham la reg pas
NK033(gi)008:795: byang sems bde ba'i rgyun skya nar gyis babs pas
NK033(gi)008:796: sdong rtsa mar khus brlan pa ltar lte ba'i a
NK033(gi)008:798: zla ba bdud rtsir zhu ba'i dwangs mas dbu ma dang /
NK033(gi)008:799: lus nang 'khor lo bzhi sogs gang bas bde drod kyi ye shes skyes par bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)008:800: a ham la shes pa mi gtod par snying gar
NK033(gi)008:801: a yig dkar po gsal zhing 'tsher ba zhig la
NK033(gi)008:802: sems bzung ste bum can kha sbyor du 'ching /
NK033(gi)008:803: mi thub na rngub chung byas la gzhil ba bya /
NK033(gi)008:804: de nas phra la ring ba'i shugs kyis phyir 'phang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:805: de ltar bum can che 'bring chung gsum gang rung ma grub kyi bar du 'bad cing /
NK033(gi)008:806: ma goms bar rlung ha cang gi drags pa ma yin par 'jam zhing ran par bzung bar bya /
NK033(gi)008:807: de ltar goms pas bde bas thabs byas pa'i shes
NK033(gi)008:808: rab stong nyid kyi ye shes skye bar 'gyur ro
NK033(gi)008:810: sna bug gnyis nas rlung phra la ring ba phyir sang gis bsal la /
NK033(gi)008:811: tshogs drug gi yul snang thams cad nam mkha'i rang
NK033(gi)008:812: bzhin du sngo mer gyis zhu bar bsams pa la
NK033(gi)008:813: sems gtad de rlung phyir mnan /
NK033(gi)008:814: de nas rlung nar gyis rngubs pas snang yul nam
NK033(gi)008:815: mkha'i rang bzhin du gyur pa de nyid sna bug
NK033(gi)008:816: nas zhugs / lte bar sngo mer gyis gnas par bsams la bum can kha sbyor du 'ching /
NK033(gi)008:817: de yang lus tsha ba shas che na rlung bsil ba'i rang bzhin dang /
NK033(gi)008:818: grangs bshas che na reg bya tsha ba'i rang bzhin can du bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:819: de lta bu'i bum can sbyor ba bzhi ldan la
NK033(gi)008:820: 'bad rtsol chen pos bsgoms pas rlung yun ring bkag
NK033(gi)008:821: kyang ngal ba ma byung na gom pa'i rtags su
NK033(gi)008:822: gsungs shing / des ni gsal bas thabs byas pa'i
NK033(gi)008:823: stong nyid rnam par mi rtog pa rgyud la skye'o
NK033(gi)008:826: ngag gnad rlung rang babs su bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:827: sems gnad dus gsum gyi rnam par rtog pa gang
NK033(gi)008:828: yang mi mno mi sems bcas bcos mi bya ba
NK033(gi)008:829: rang babs bzo med du 'bol le yengs med du
NK033(gi)008:831: de ltar bzhag pas sems gar gtad la zin cing /
NK033(gi)008:832: rtog med rang gsal nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang du gnas pa ni goms pa'i tshad do //
NK033(gi)008:833: des ni byang chub kyi sems gong 'phel du 'gyur ba'i dgos pa khyad par can yod do //
NK033(gi)008:835: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog mkha' lta bu //
NK033(gi)008:836: bsam gtan dam pa'i bde bas rgyud dul ba //
NK033(gi)008:837: zhing sa gshin por lo tog legs pa bzhin //
NK033(gi)008:838: ting 'dzin kun gyi gzhi rten bsgrub par bya //
NK033(gi)008:840: 'dir rig 'dzin chen po'i khrid rgyun tu //
NK033(gi)008:841: mi rtag pa la sems sbyangs mtshams skyabs 'gro //
NK033(gi)008:842: sems sbyong gnyis pa'i rjes su sems bskyed /
NK033(gi)008:843: gsum pa dang bzhi pa gnyis kyi rjes su man+dala /
NK033(gi)008:844: lnga pa'i rjes su rdor sems sgom bzlas /
NK033(gi)008:845: drug pa'i rjes su bla ma'i rnal 'byor /
NK033(gi)008:846: de nas sems sbyong bdun pa'i rjes su rlung thig bslab pa la 'jug par mdzad do //
NK033(gi)008:847: gsum pa thun mong sngon 'gro bzhi sbyor gyi rgyud dag par byed pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:849: kun mkhyen chen po'i don khrid du gsal kha ma gsungs kyang /
NK033(gi)008:850: yi ge dmar ru'i rgyab yig las /
NK033(gi)008:851: dben pa'i gnas su bsod nams kyi tshogs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK033(gi)008:852: zhes gzhung gi shugs bstan tsam gyi gsungs shing /
NK033(gi)008:853: gter chen yab sras sogs brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyis phyag bzhes bar ma chad pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:855: lam dman pa las khyad par du gyur pa skyabs 'gro'i khrid /
NK033(gi)008:856: theg chen gyi rtsa ba sems bskyed pa'i khrid /
NK033(gi)008:857: sdig sgrib sbyong ba'i snying po rdo rje sems dpa'i bsgom bzlas kyi khrid /
NK033(gi)008:858: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed pa man+dala gyi khrid /
NK033(gi)008:859: byin rlabs myur du 'jug pa bla ma'i rnal 'byor gyi khrid do //
NK033(gi)008:864: de yang rang cag rnams mi dge bcu spong gi
NK033(gi)008:865: tshul khrims dge ba'i las kyis re zhig bde 'gro'i
NK033(gi)008:866: gnas su skyes kyang sdug bsngal spangs pa'i thar pa
NK033(gi)008:867: bla na med pa'i byang chub ma thob na sngar
NK033(gi)008:868: byas kyi dge ba'i 'phen pa zad nas slar yang
NK033(gi)008:870: yun ring la dos drag pa'i sdug bsngal mi bzod pa sna tshogs myong dgos pa 'dug /
NK033(gi)008:871: de las skyob nus pa ni dkon mchog rin po
NK033(gi)008:872: che rnam pa gsum ma gtogs gzhan su yang med
NK033(gi)008:873: / de yang rang la dngos su snang ba'i sangs rgyas ni bla ma dam pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:874: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dang dbyer med pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)008:875: skyabs gnas dkon mchog rin po che rnams pa gsum
NK033(gi)008:876: la skyabs dang ram zla zhu snyam du lus sems
NK033(gi)008:877: rnal du phab / rang gar gnas kyis phyogs de nyid rin po che /
NK033(gi)008:878: sna tshogs las grub pa'i zhing khams mdzes shing yid
NK033(gi)008:879: du 'ong ba'i dbus su dpag bsam gyi sdong po
NK033(gi)008:880: yal ga lo 'dab rab tu rgyas pas nam mkha'i
NK033(gi)008:881: khams kun yongs su khyab pa'i dbus kyi yal ga'i
NK033(gi)008:882: snying por seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK033(gi)008:883: sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan mtho zhing yangs
NK033(gi)008:884: pa'i steng du / ngo bo drin can rtsa ba'i
NK033(gi)008:885: bla ma nyid rnam pa dpal kun tu bzang po
NK033(gi)008:886: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i cha lugs can /
NK033(gi)008:887: sku mdog mthing ga gsal zhing 'tsher ba'i 'od zer 'phro ba /
NK033(gi)008:888: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan phun sum tshogs pas mdzes par spras pa /
NK033(gi)008:889: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK033(gi)008:890: zhabs rdo rje skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)008:891: mtshan dpe'i lang tsho rab tu rdzogs pa'i sku can
NK033(gi)008:892: du gsal ba'i mtha' bskor du brgyud pa'i bla ma
NK033(gi)008:894: phyogs bzhir gyes pa'i yal ga rnams la gdan gyi
NK033(gi)008:895: bkod pa mtho zhing yangs pa re re gsal bar
NK033(gi)008:896: gyur pa'i mdun ma la khyad par gyi sangs rgyas
NK033(gi)008:897: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la yi dam rgyud sde
NK033(gi)008:898: drug gi lha tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK033(gi)008:899: g.yas kyi gdan la thun mong gi sangs rgyas ston
NK033(gi)008:900: pa thub pa'i dbang po la phyogs bcu dus gsum
NK033(gi)008:901: gyi sangs rgyas mchog gi sprul sku rnams kyis bskor
NK033(gi)008:902: ba / rgyab kyi gdan la lung rtogs kyi dam
NK033(gi)008:903: chos dkon mchog rnams glegs bam brtsegs pa'i tshul du
NK033(gi)008:904: ba / bzhugs pa / g.yon gyi gdan la spyan
NK033(gi)008:905: ras gzigs dang 'jam dpal phyag rdor sogs byang chub
NK033(gi)008:907: 'phags pa sh+aa ri'i bu dang mo 'gal gyi bu sogs nyan thos kyi dge 'dun rnams bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)008:908: de dag gi bar mtshams rnams su khyad par gyi
NK033(gi)008:909: dge 'dun mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma ye shes
NK033(gi)008:910: kyi spyan dang ldan pa rnams sprin phung gtibs pa
NK033(gi)008:912: de'i mdun du rang dang sems can thams cad sa chen po'i dregs pa bzhin 'khod cing /
NK033(gi)008:913: thams cad kyang lus ngag yid gsum gus pa chen
NK033(gi)008:914: po dang ldan pas skyabs 'gro lhan cig tu byed
NK033(gi)008:915: par mos la / bdag dang mkha' mnyam gyi sems
NK033(gi)008:916: can thams cad 'khor ba dang sdug bsngal gyi rgya
NK033(gi)008:917: mtsho chen po las da lta nyid du drang zhing
NK033(gi)008:918: bskyab tu gsol snyam pa'i yid gzhan du ma yengs
NK033(gi)008:919: par mos la / par / nam mkha'i gnas su nam mkha' gang ba yi //
NK033(gi)008:920: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK033(gi)008:921: sangs rgyas chos dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun la //
NK033(gi)008:922: bdag sogs 'gro drug gus pas skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)008:923: zhes brgya stong sogs ci nus su 'don cing //
NK033(gi)008:924: thun bsdu ba'i tshe skyabs yul rnams kyi sku las
NK033(gi)008:925: 'od zer 'phros rang dang sems can thams cad la
NK033(gi)008:927: dag pa'i zhing du 'ur gyis song /
NK033(gi)008:928: brgyud pa'i bla ma dkon mchog gsum sogs 'khor gyi
NK033(gi)008:929: tshul du bzhugs pa rnams rtsa ba'i bla ma'i sku
NK033(gi)008:930: la bsdus / rtsa ba'i bla ma yang 'od du
NK033(gi)008:931: zhu ba rang gi spyi bo nas snying gar sib
NK033(gi)008:932: kyis thim par bsams la skyabs su 'gro bya 'gro
NK033(gi)008:933: byed mi dmigs pa'i ngang du ci nus mnyam par
NK033(gi)008:934: la bsdus / bzhag / nub mo nyal ba'i tshe
NK033(gi)008:935: tshogs zhing ma bsdus par de la sngas phyogs pas
NK033(gi)008:936: mos gus dung nge ba'i ngang la gnyid du 'gro
NK033(gi)008:937: la bsdus / bzhag / bar bya zhing / thun
NK033(gi)008:938: mtshams rnams su'ang tshogs zhing gsal btab la phyag mchod
NK033(gi)008:940: 'dir rig 'dzin chen po'i khrid rgyun tu /
NK033(gi)008:941: rang gi mdun gyi nam mkha'i dbus su rtsa ba'i
NK033(gi)008:942: bla ma de nyid sku dngos kyi rnam pa phyogs
NK033(gi)008:943: mtshams rnams su skyabs yul rnams sprin phung 'khrigs pa'am
NK033(gi)008:944: me tog gi tshom bu bkram pa'am nam mkha'i skar
NK033(gi)008:945: ma bzhin du go mtshams med par khyab pa'i tshul
NK033(gi)008:946: du sgom zhing skyabs yul mchog dman la ltos pa'i
NK033(gi)008:947: steng 'og mtho dman dang mtha' dbus kyi rnam pa
NK033(gi)008:948: tsam ma gtogs lnga tshom lta bus ka dpe ma
NK033(gi)008:949: mi dgos gsungs / mthar skyabs yul gshegs bsdu'i spros
NK033(gi)008:950: pa med pa dmigs med du 'jog pa'i lugs so
NK033(gi)008:951: mi dgos gsungs / // skyabs 'gro'i go don rnam
NK033(gi)008:952: bzhag phan yon sogs spro na spyi ltar 'chad par
NK033(gi)008:953: mi dgos gsungs / // bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:954: rang gi lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa 'dab dge 'dun /
NK033(gi)008:956: rlung lnga'i dwangs ma ye shes lnga ni /
NK033(gi)008:957: nyon mongs pa ye nas dag pa'i sangs rgyas sku
NK033(gi)008:958: gsum gyi bdag nyid du rang ngo shes nas bsgom
NK033(gi)008:959: snyam du / rlung lnga rnam dag dwangs ma'i sku //
NK033(gi)008:960: nyon mongs rnam dag ye shes lnga //
NK033(gi)008:961: sku gsum mdzad pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK033(gi)008:962: dkon mchog gsum la rtogs pas 'dud //
NK033(gi)008:963: ces lan ci rigs brjod la 'od gsal gyi rang ngor mnyam par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)008:964: gnyis pa sems bskyed la la'ang gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:968: don dam par gzod ma nas rnam par dag kyang /
NK033(gi)008:969: kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal gyi rgyu
NK033(gi)008:970: 'bras bsam gyis mi khyab pa la rtag par longs
NK033(gi)008:971: spyod pa'i ma rgan sems can thams cad gdod ma'i
NK033(gi)008:972: mgon po'i go 'phang la 'god pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:973: rang gi rig pa mngon sum gyi ye shes lam
NK033(gi)008:974: snang ba rnam pa bzhi nyams su blang snyam pa'i
NK033(gi)008:975: sems snga na med pa bskyed la /
NK033(gi)008:976: e ma hoh ma rig 'jig rten mun pa'i klong //
NK033(gi)008:977: rang gi thabs shes sgron me yis //
NK033(gi)008:978: rang la gnas pa'i ye shes de //
NK033(gi)008:979: bla ma'i drin gyis rtogs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:980: zhes lan grangs ci nus brjod la smon pa sems bskyed /
NK033(gi)008:981: dbyings ka dag chos sku skye med nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK033(gi)008:982: ye shes lhun grub rang rig sku gsum gyi ngo
NK033(gi)008:983: bo spros pa'i mtha' bzhi las 'das pa tshig dang
NK033(gi)008:985: smra bsam brjod med chen po nyid rang ngo shes par bya snyam du /
NK033(gi)008:986: e ma hoh sangs rgyas mthar thug dbyings rig gnyis //
NK033(gi)008:987: sku gsum ngo bo mtha' bral gzhi //
NK033(gi)008:988: tshig las 'das pa'i rang byung de //
NK033(gi)008:989: da lta nyid du rtogs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:990: zhes lan grangs ci nus su brjod la 'jug pa sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)008:992: don dam par chos thams cad gdod ma nas spang
NK033(gi)008:993: blang bcing grol med pa mnyam rdzogs chen po'i rang
NK033(gi)008:994: bzhin du sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba dang myang 'das
NK033(gi)008:996: bdag gzhan bzang ngan tha dad du grub pa med
NK033(gi)008:997: pa yin pa la yin par shes pas rgyu 'bras
NK033(gi)008:998: rtsol sgrub las 'das pa ye grol chos sku'i dgongs
NK033(gi)008:999: par rang chas lhun 'byams chen po'i ngang du la
NK033(gi)008:1001: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK033(gi)008:1002: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK033(gi)008:1003: yin par shes pa'i bdag nyid du //
NK033(gi)008:1004: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)008:1006: gzhan yang spro na kun rdzob byang sems kyi nyams
NK033(gi)008:1007: len gtso bor dbugs 'byung 'jug dang sbyar ba'i bde
NK033(gi)008:1008: sdug gtong len gyi dmigs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1009: 'khor gsum rang bzhin med pa don dam sems bskyed kyi rang ngo la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)008:1013: bslab bya sogs 'chad par spro na spyi ltar bshad do //
NK033(gi)008:1014: gsum pa sdig sgrib sbyong byed rdo rje sems dpa'i sgom bzlas kyi khrid la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:1018: rang gi spyi bor pad zla'i steng du a yig dkar po /
NK033(gi)008:1019: de las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK033(gi)008:1020: las bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i dpal rdo
NK033(gi)008:1021: rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po phyag g.yas gser
NK033(gi)008:1022: gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar 'dzin cing
NK033(gi)008:1023: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dkur brten pas yum
NK033(gi)008:1024: la 'khyud pa / zhabs sems skyil gyis bzhugs shing
NK033(gi)008:1025: yum snyems ma dkar mo gri thod 'dzin pa dang
NK033(gi)008:1027: gnyis ka'ang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can yab
NK033(gi)008:1028: kyi thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK033(gi)008:1030: de'i mtha' bskor du yi ge brgya pa'i sngags phreng
NK033(gi)008:1031: dkar po 'od zer phrom phrom 'phro ba g.yas su
NK033(gi)008:1033: de ltar spyi bo'i bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'
NK033(gi)008:1034: skyabs gnas kun 'dus su mos pa rten gyi stobs
NK033(gi)008:1035: / sngar byas kyi sdig pa mi dge ba'i las
NK033(gi)008:1036: thams cad la gnong 'gyod drag pos dpal ldan bla
NK033(gi)008:1037: ma rdo rje sems dpa' khyed mkhyen no //
NK033(gi)008:1038: bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi sngon chad sdig
NK033(gi)008:1039: pa'i las bgyis pa thams cad mthol zhing bshags so
NK033(gi)008:1040: // byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol snyam pa sun 'byin pa'i stobs /
NK033(gi)008:1041: da phyin chad 'chi ba srog la bab kyang sdig pa'i las dngos su lta ci /
NK033(gi)008:1042: rmi lam du'ang mi bgyid snyam pa nyes pa las sor chud pa'i stobs /
NK033(gi)008:1043: sngar byas kyi gnyen por rdo rje sems dpa'i sgom
NK033(gi)008:1044: bzlas la spyod pa gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1045: stobs te / de ltar stobs bzhi dran bzhin pas
NK033(gi)008:1046: yig brgya gsol 'debs kyi tshul du brgya stong sogs
NK033(gi)008:1048: sngags phreng rnams las bdud rtsi'i rgyun skya chil gyi
NK033(gi)008:1049: babs pa yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas thon
NK033(gi)008:1050: rang gi tshangs bug tu zhugs /
NK033(gi)008:1051: nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad dud khu dang rnag
NK033(gi)008:1052: khrag ljan ljin dang srog chags phra mo la sogs
NK033(gi)008:1053: pa'i rnam par ba spu'i khung bu dang /
NK033(gi)008:1054: gshang lam dang chu lam sogs nas phu chu drag
NK033(gi)008:1055: pos thal ba ded pa ltar thon par bsam la
NK033(gi)008:1056: de nyid gsal gdab pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)008:1057: rang lus tha mal spyi gtsug tu //
NK033(gi)008:1058: pad dkar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor steng //
NK033(gi)008:1059: a las rdo rje sems dpa' dkar //
NK033(gi)008:1061: rin chen rgyan spras sems skyil bzhugs //
NK033(gi)008:1062: thugs kar zla steng h'u gi mthar //
NK033(gi)008:1063: snying po yi ge brgya pas bskor //
NK033(gi)008:1064: sku dang sngags las bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK033(gi)008:1065: dkar nar babs te spyi bor zhugs //
NK033(gi)008:1066: bdag gi lus kun gang ba yis //
NK033(gi)008:1067: sdig sgrib dag nas shel gong ltar //
NK033(gi)008:1068: dri ma med pa'i lus su gyur //
NK033(gi)008:1069: ces ngag tu brjod cing dmigs pa rtse gcig tu gcun la yig brgya bzla /
NK033(gi)008:1070: mthar lus shel gong dri ma med pa ltar gyur
NK033(gi)008:1071: pa'i nang bdud rtsi'i rgyun gyis mer khrig gis gang
NK033(gi)008:1072: bar gyur pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK033(gi)008:1073: kyi dngos grub thob par bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1074: mthar mos gus gdung shugs drag pos /
NK033(gi)008:1075: mgon po bdag ni mi shes rmongs pa yis //
NK033(gi)008:1076: dam tshig las ni 'gal zhing nyams //
NK033(gi)008:1077: bla ma mgon pos skyabs mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)008:1078: gtso bo rdo rje 'dzin pa ste //
NK033(gi)008:1079: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid can //
NK033(gi)008:1080: 'gro ba'i gtso la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK033(gi)008:1081: sku gsung thugs rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag thams cad mthol zhing bshags so //
NK033(gi)008:1082: sdig sgrib nyes ltung dri ma'i tshogs thams cad byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1084: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal nas /
NK033(gi)008:1085: rigs kyi bu khyod kyi sdig sgrib thams cad dus
NK033(gi)008:1086: da lta nas dag go zhes gnang ba stsal te
NK033(gi)008:1087: 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas rang sems
NK033(gi)008:1088: dang dbyer med bshags bya bshags byed mi dmigs pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1089: ngang la yun ji srid gnas kyi bar mnyam par
NK033(gi)008:1090: bzhag / tshul de lta bus sdig sgrib dag pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1091: rtags ma mthong gi bar du 'bad par bya zhing
NK033(gi)008:1092: bzhag / / spro na nyes ltung dang gnyen po'i
NK033(gi)008:1093: rnam bzhag bsgom bzlas kyi phan yon spyi ltar 'chad
NK033(gi)008:1095: skad cig gis pad zla'i dbus su rang nyid rdo
NK033(gi)008:1096: rje sems dpa' dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK033(gi)008:1097: / g.yas rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing //
NK033(gi)008:1098: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK033(gi)008:1099: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung can /
NK033(gi)008:1100: dar dang rin po che'i brgyan pa'i snying nang zla
NK033(gi)008:1101: ba'i dbus su rdo rje dkar po tshon gang ba
NK033(gi)008:1102: lte bar h'u gis mtshan pa'i mtha' skor du yi
NK033(gi)008:1103: ge brgya pa dkar ser mar me 'bar ba lta
NK033(gi)008:1104: bu'i 'od kyis bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)008:1106: snang ba thams cad rdo rje sems dpa'i sku /
NK033(gi)008:1107: sgra skad thams cad yi ge brgya par bsams la /
NK033(gi)008:1110: badz+ra sa t+wa t+we no pa tish+tha /
NK033(gi)008:1112: su to sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NK033(gi)008:1113: su po sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NK033(gi)008:1114: a nu rak+to me b+ha wa /
NK033(gi)008:1116: sarba karma su tsa me tsit+tam sh+re yahku ru h'u /
NK033(gi)008:1117: ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK033(gi)008:1118: sarba ta th+aa ga ta hri da ya /
NK033(gi)008:1121: ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+wa +aa /
NK033(gi)008:1122: zhes ci 'grub bzlas pa'i rjes la snang ba thams cad thugs ka'i h'u la bsdu /
NK033(gi)008:1123: h'u mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)008:1124: bsngo ba byas pas bskal pa 'bum phrag du mar
NK033(gi)008:1125: bsags pa'i sdig sgrib dag cing nyams chag thams cad
NK033(gi)008:1126: bskangs nas / sems nyid kyi don rtogs pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:1127: 'di ni yang tig yid bzhin nor bu'i rtsa ba'i
NK033(gi)008:1128: chos sde snyan brgyud ye shes rang snang las sgrib
NK033(gi)008:1129: pa sbyong ba rdo rje sems dpa' rnal 'byor gyis
NK033(gi)008:1130: blo sbyong ba zhes dngos su bstan pa lugs 'di'i
NK033(gi)008:1131: thun mong ma yin pa nyid do //
NK033(gi)008:1132: 'dir rig 'dzin chen po'i khrid rgyun du /
NK033(gi)008:1133: phyi bya rgyud ltar bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i spyi bor bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)008:1134: nang spyod rgyud ltar snying gar bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)008:1135: gsang ba rnal 'byor rgyud ltar sems dpa' sum brtsegs su bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)008:1136: yang gsang bla med ltar khyer so gsum ldan du bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)008:1137: de kho na nyid chos kyi dbyings su la bzla ba dang lnga las /
NK033(gi)008:1139: rang gi spyi bor pad+ma dkar po 'dab brgyad de
NK033(gi)008:1140: las 'dab ma gcig la gcig mthud kyi tshul du
NK033(gi)008:1141: nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa'i bar du khyab pa /
NK033(gi)008:1142: de lta bu'i 'dab ma re re'i 'og tu sems can re re 'khod pa /
NK033(gi)008:1143: de re re'i spyi gtsug gi pad 'dab steng du yang rdo rje sems dpa' re bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)008:1144: de thams cad kyang rdor sems spyi mthun yab rkyang sems skyil can /
NK033(gi)008:1145: thugs kar sa bon sngags phreng dang bcas pa las 'od 'phros sangs rgyas sras bcas bstim /
NK033(gi)008:1146: bzlas pa dang bdud rtsi 'bebs sbyong mthar /
NK033(gi)008:1148: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK033(gi)008:1150: rdo rje sems dpas dbugs dbyung ste /
NK033(gi)008:1151: gnyis pa dang sbrel na rang gi spyi bor bzhugs
NK033(gi)008:1152: pa'i mu nas sku'i byin rlabs bdud rtsi byang chub
NK033(gi)008:1153: sems kyi rnam par slar yang babs mgrin pa yan
NK033(gi)008:1154: chad gang lus kyi sdig sgrib dag /
NK033(gi)008:1155: sku'i byin rlabs thob par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:1156: yang rdor sems mgrin par byon gsung gi byin rlabs
NK033(gi)008:1157: bdud rtsi'i rnam par babs snying ga yan gang ngag
NK033(gi)008:1159: yang snying gar byon thugs kyi byin rlabs bdud rtsi'i
NK033(gi)008:1160: rnam par babs lte ba yan chad gang 'di la
NK033(gi)008:1162: thugs kyi byin rlabs thob par mos /
NK033(gi)008:1163: de dag gi skabs su yig brgya bzla /
NK033(gi)008:1164: de nas gsum pa dang sprel na /
NK033(gi)008:1165: bdud rtsis lus thams cad gang sgrib pa mtha' dag dag /
NK033(gi)008:1166: rnam smin gyi phung po gnas 'gyur nas rang nyid
NK033(gi)008:1167: rdo rje sems dpar gyur pa'i thugs kar rang 'dra'i
NK033(gi)008:1169: de'i thugs kar ting 'dzin sems dpa' rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa'i lte bar h'u /
NK033(gi)008:1170: der dmigs nas yig brgya bzla /
NK033(gi)008:1172: de'i mthar snang grags rig gsum rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs su mos te /
NK033(gi)008:1175: dmigs bral ka dag gi ngang du mnyam par bzhag par gsungs so //
NK033(gi)008:1176: bzhi pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs byed man+dala gyi khrid ni /
NK033(gi)008:1177: tshogs zhing skyabs yul ltar gsal gdab par bshad pa
NK033(gi)008:1178: ni dmigs pa'i rnam grangs mang po mi 'chun pa
NK033(gi)008:1179: dang spyi mthun gyi phyag len stabs bde ba la
NK033(gi)008:1181: 'dir rang lugs thun mong ma yin pa ni phyi nas rim bzhin 'chad par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:1182: man+dala gyi rgyu rab rin po che gser dngul /
NK033(gi)008:1184: tha ma rdo shing lta bu dngos po dman na gru gang las mi chung ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:1185: tshom bu'i rgyu'ang rab rin po che /
NK033(gi)008:1187: tha ma 'bru gtsang ma dri bzang gis kha bsgyur
NK033(gi)008:1188: ba la sman khrol bu sogs gang 'dzom bsres shing
NK033(gi)008:1189: gsher gyis brlan pa dang dri bzang ba byung yang
NK033(gi)008:1190: 'du bya / rang dang sems can thams cad lhan
NK033(gi)008:1191: cig pa lus kyi las su tshom bu 'god pa
NK033(gi)008:1192: 'du bya / / ngag gi las su 'bul tshig rnam 'ur dir gyis 'don pa /
NK033(gi)008:1193: yid kyis tshig phyir sems ma yengs par bya ba rnams sum phrugs su bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1194: man+dala gyi cho ga dngos la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:1195: dang po sprul sku'i man+dala ni /
NK033(gi)008:1196: tshogs zhing mdun du rdo rje'i zhing khams chen po
NK033(gi)008:1197: rnam par dag pa'i rin po che'i rang bzhin ri
NK033(gi)008:1198: rab gling bzhi dang bcas pa'i ri rtser pad zla'i
NK033(gi)008:1199: gdan la rtsa ba'i bla ma sprul pa'i sku'i rnam
NK033(gi)008:1200: pa can la dgongs brda snyan brgyud kyi bla ma
NK033(gi)008:1202: gling dang gling bar rnams su khyad par gyi dkon
NK033(gi)008:1203: mchog skyabs yul gyi skabs ltar bzhugs par mos la
NK033(gi)008:1204: / thog mar sems kyi rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i brdar man+dala lan gsum phyis /
NK033(gi)008:1205: byang chub sems kyi rlan mi yal ba'i phyir dri bzang dang ba byung chus chag chag gdab /
NK033(gi)008:1206: tshom bu rab bzhi bcu rtsa gcig /
NK033(gi)008:1208: bsdus pa la dgu dgod par gsungs pa las 'bring
NK033(gi)008:1209: po'i lugs byed na ri rab gling bzhi gling phran
NK033(gi)008:1210: bcas bcu gsum / phyogs mtshams brgyad du brgyad bkod
NK033(gi)008:1211: pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad sogs mchod rdzas phyogs bsdus
NK033(gi)008:1212: bcas bcu gsum / / mdun rgyab gnyis su gnyis bkod pa nyi zla mtshon pa yin la /
NK033(gi)008:1213: de dag kyang 'jig rten khams rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i
NK033(gi)008:1214: phyi nang snod bcud kyi dpal 'byor rigs lnga gangs
NK033(gi)008:1215: chen mtsho'i zhing khams kyi bkod pa la brten pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1216: tshangs chen gyi bskal pa chen po nam mkhas khyab
NK033(gi)008:1217: tshad du sprul nas dus chad pa med par 'bul
NK033(gi)008:1218: bar bsam la ngag 'don dang dmigs pa sbrags te
NK033(gi)008:1220: dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi /
NK033(gi)008:1227: rnga yab dang rnga yab gzhan /
NK033(gi)008:1229: sgra mi snyan dang sgra mi snyan gyi zla /
NK033(gi)008:1232: rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun /
NK033(gi)008:1238: shin tu mdzes pa'i lha mo /
NK033(gi)008:1241: dbus su lha dang mi'i 'dod yon ma tshang ba med pa /
NK033(gi)008:1242: 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho legs par bkod de
NK033(gi)008:1243: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad la sogs
NK033(gi)008:1244: pa phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK033(gi)008:1245: rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho'i sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK033(gi)008:1246: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo la brten pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1247: zhing khams rab 'byams mtha' klas pa tshangs chen gyi
NK033(gi)008:1248: bskal pa chen pos legs par brgyan pa 'di nyid
NK033(gi)008:1249: bla ma dang yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK033(gi)008:1250: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams la
NK033(gi)008:1251: / kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa'i sprin phung chen
NK033(gi)008:1252: po bsam gyis mi khyab par dmigs te 'bul lo
NK033(gi)008:1253: / // phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rgya mtsho'i rdul snyed ri rab gling bzhi'i 'jig rten khams /
NK033(gi)008:1254: lha dang mi yi 'dod yon phun tshogs bde gshegs mchod pa'i sprin phung can /
NK033(gi)008:1255: tshangs chen bskal pas legs par brgyan te dge legs rgya mtsho'i bsod nams zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1256: bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul /
NK033(gi)008:1257: rin chen man+dala yid 'ong mchod pa'i sprin /
NK033(gi)008:1258: rgyal ba'i 'byor tshogs dpag med dang ldan pa //
NK033(gi)008:1259: dpag yas nam mkha'i rgyan gyur 'di phul bas //
NK033(gi)008:1260: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing la spyod par shog /
NK033(gi)008:1261: ces tshom bu gso zhing sh+lo ka phyi ma la grangs bzung ste ci nus su 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)008:1262: gnyis pa longs sku'i man+dala ni /
NK033(gi)008:1263: tshogs zhing 'og min stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams
NK033(gi)008:1264: gzhi dang rgya tshad rgyan bkod pa'i khyad par bsam
NK033(gi)008:1265: gyis mi khyab par bla ma longs sku rigs lnga
NK033(gi)008:1266: 'khor dpag tu med pa dang bcas pa bzhugs par
NK033(gi)008:1267: mos la / tshom bu rgyas pa nyer lnga /
NK033(gi)008:1270: stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams thar pa chen po'i
NK033(gi)008:1271: gzhal med khang bsam las 'das pa'i bkod pa yid
NK033(gi)008:1272: du 'ong ba'i lha mo ngo mtshar ba'i mchod rdzas
NK033(gi)008:1273: thogs pas gang ba tshangs pa rnga sgra'i zhing khams
NK033(gi)008:1274: chen po ye shes rin po che'i sprin gyi d+r+wa
NK033(gi)008:1275: bas legs par brgyan pas 'khor ba ma stong gi
NK033(gi)008:1276: bar du rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor mchod par
NK033(gi)008:1278: 'og min gyi gnas rnam dag stug po bkod pa bde ba'i zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1279: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa'i zhing khams na /
NK033(gi)008:1280: shin tu yid 'ong ba'i gzhal med khang chen po /
NK033(gi)008:1281: sgo bzhi gru bzhi rta babs bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK033(gi)008:1283: chos kyi 'khor lo shin tu mdzes pa'i ri dwags /
NK033(gi)008:1284: lha'i gos rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan /
NK033(gi)008:1286: zla ba rlung gis bskyod pa /
NK033(gi)008:1287: rnga yab nor bu'i yu ba can /
NK033(gi)008:1288: gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha'i phreng ba /
NK033(gi)008:1289: rdo rje dang nor bu rin po che'i tog /
NK033(gi)008:1290: rtsig pa lnga dang ldan pa'i steng na /
NK033(gi)008:1292: nor bu sna tshogs kyi d+r+wa phyed /
NK033(gi)008:1293: rdo kre ma sh+ai na'i mda' yab /
NK033(gi)008:1296: rab tu mtho ba'i phyur bu /
NK033(gi)008:1308: mchod pa'i sprin phung chen po bsam gyis mi khyab
NK033(gi)008:1309: pas phyi nang kun tu yang legs par brgyan te
NK033(gi)008:1310: bkod pa'i gnas tshangs pa rnga sgra'i zhing khams chen
NK033(gi)008:1311: po / ye shes rin po che sprin gyi d+r+wa bas legs par brgyan pa 'di nyid /
NK033(gi)008:1312: bla ma dang yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK033(gi)008:1313: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams la
NK033(gi)008:1314: ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du rtag
NK033(gi)008:1316: bde chen gnas ni shin tu mtha' yas bkod pa'i sprin gyi 'od zer can //
NK033(gi)008:1317: sgo bzhi gru bzhi rta babs bzhi ldan ye shes rnam lnga'i rtsig pas brgyan //
NK033(gi)008:1318: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar mchod pa'i sprin gyi 'od 'phro ba //
NK033(gi)008:1319: bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK033(gi)008:1320: 'og min bde chen rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)008:1321: sna tshogs mchod pa'i sprin gyi bla bre can //
NK033(gi)008:1322: nam mkha' gang bar dmigs te phul ba yis //
NK033(gi)008:1323: lhun grub longs sku'i zhing la spyod par shog /
NK033(gi)008:1324: ces sh+lo ka phyi ma la grangs bzung zhing 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)008:1325: gsum pa chos sku'i man+dala ni /
NK033(gi)008:1326: tshogs zhing chos sku thig le nyag gcig 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:1327: rdo rje snying po'i zhing khams su bla ma chos
NK033(gi)008:1328: sku gdod ma'i mgon po 'khor rang snang ye shes
NK033(gi)008:1329: rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas rang gsal lhun grub tu
NK033(gi)008:1331: tshom bu rgyas pa nyer lnga /
NK033(gi)008:1334: chos dbyings 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i zhing khams
NK033(gi)008:1335: tshad dpag tu med cing nam mkha'i mtha' klas par
NK033(gi)008:1336: rig gdangs 'od lnga'i thig le thig phran 'ja' 'od
NK033(gi)008:1337: zer thag mer mer shig shig tu g.yo ba'i sku
NK033(gi)008:1338: dang ye shes kyi snang ba tshad med pas brgyan
NK033(gi)008:1339: pa nyid mchod bya mchod byed med par rang byung
NK033(gi)008:1340: rang shar rang thim du 'bul bar mos /
NK033(gi)008:1342: chos nyid 'od gsal gyi zhing khams gdod ma nas ngo bo nyid kyi rnam par dag cing /
NK033(gi)008:1343: nam mkha' ltar stong la mtha' dbus med pa /
NK033(gi)008:1344: nyi zla ltar bkra zhing lhun gyis grub pa /
NK033(gi)008:1345: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gang du
NK033(gi)008:1346: yang ma bye mi 'byed 'byed pa med pa'i rang
NK033(gi)008:1347: bzhin / sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang 'gro ba drug
NK033(gi)008:1348: gi rnam par 'phrul pa dpag tu med pa'i 'byung
NK033(gi)008:1349: bzhin / gnas chen po / lhun grub chen po che'i sbubs /
NK033(gi)008:1351: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK033(gi)008:1352: gzhon nu bum pa sku'i zhing khams phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa /
NK033(gi)008:1357: ljang khu'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1358: nam mkha'i mtha' klas par sku dang ye shes kyi
NK033(gi)008:1359: snang ba chen pos legs par brgyan pa'i bkod pa
NK033(gi)008:1360: tshad med pa'i mnga' thang chen po la dbang 'byor
NK033(gi)008:1361: ba / 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i zhing khams /
NK033(gi)008:1362: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing lhun gyis grub pa 'di nyid /
NK033(gi)008:1363: bla ma dang yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK033(gi)008:1364: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams la
NK033(gi)008:1365: / dgongs klong rnam par dag pa'i ngang du ye shes kyi mchod pa dam par 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)008:1366: gdod nas rnam dag 'od gsal zhing ni ma skyes lhun rdzogs 'dus ma byas /
NK033(gi)008:1367: sna tshogs mi dmigs spos kun nyer zhi ye shes rnam lnga'i gzhal yas khang /
NK033(gi)008:1368: sku gsum mdzad pa'i 'od zer dang bcas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas /
NK033(gi)008:1369: bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul /
NK033(gi)008:1370: 'od gsal lhun grub ye shes rigs lnga'i zhing //
NK033(gi)008:1371: sku dang thig les ye nas brgyan pa 'di //
NK033(gi)008:1372: rang snang dag pas legs par phul ba yis //
NK033(gi)008:1373: kun bzang chos sku'i zhing la spyod par shog /
NK033(gi)008:1374: ces sh+lo ka phyi ma la grangs bzung ste ci nus 'bul /
NK033(gi)008:1375: mthar man+dala 'bul yul mchod rdzas dang bcas pa h'u sngon po'i rnam par bsdus /
NK033(gi)008:1376: de yang rang la thim par bsam zhing tshogs chen
NK033(gi)008:1377: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i 'od gsal gyi ngang du mnyam
NK033(gi)008:1378: par bzhag go // 'dir yang spyi dang bye brag
NK033(gi)008:1379: gi rnam bzhag dgos pa phan yon sogs 'chad par
NK033(gi)008:1380: spro na gzhan nas blang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:1381: lnga pa byin rlabs myur du 'jug pa bla ma'i rnal 'byor gyi khrid la'ang gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:1385: gsol ba 'debs pa'i rten gsal 'debs pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1386: snod bcud dag pa'i zhing khams 'byams klas pa'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)008:1387: rang gi spyi bo'i nam mkhar ye shes lnga'i rang
NK033(gi)008:1388: mdangs 'ja' tshon 'od lnga'i gur khyim rab tu 'khrugs
NK033(gi)008:1389: pa'i dbus su seng khri pad+ma nyi zla brtsegs pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1390: gdan gyi steng du rtsa ba'i bla ma dang gnyis
NK033(gi)008:1391: su med pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang po sku
NK033(gi)008:1392: mdog mthing ga in+d+ra n+ai la'i lhun po la nyi
NK033(gi)008:1393: ma shar ba lta bu'i gzi byin rab tu 'bar
NK033(gi)008:1394: zhing phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK033(gi)008:1395: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs shing dar
NK033(gi)008:1396: gyi chas gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad
NK033(gi)008:1398: sku la mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus spras pa /
NK033(gi)008:1399: shin tu dwangs pa'i sku las dri ma med pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1400: 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang ba re re
NK033(gi)008:1401: yang bye ba phrag drug drug tu 'phro zhing 'bar
NK033(gi)008:1402: ba'i klong na lham mer bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)008:1403: gsung yan lag drug cu'i chos sgra sgrog pa /
NK033(gi)008:1404: thugs ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo brgya phrag du ma la mnyam par bzhag pa /
NK033(gi)008:1405: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i bdag nyid can du gsal ba'i
NK033(gi)008:1406: steng gi cha la brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang
NK033(gi)008:1407: / mtha' bskor du theg pa che chung gi yi dam sangs rgyas /
NK033(gi)008:1409: mkha' 'gro dam can srung ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa
NK033(gi)008:1410: thams cad sprin gyi phung po gtibs pa lta bur
NK033(gi)008:1411: bzhugs par bsam la de nyid gsal gdab pa'i slad
NK033(gi)008:1412: du / snod bcud dag pa'i zhing khams chen po'i dbus /
NK033(gi)008:1413: rang mdun nam mkhar ye shes 'od lnga'i klong //
NK033(gi)008:1414: seng khri pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK033(gi)008:1415: skyabs gnas kun 'dus rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK033(gi)008:1416: dbyer me gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang //
NK033(gi)008:1417: mthing gsal zhal gcig phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag can //
NK033(gi)008:1418: dar dang rin chen rgyan rdzogs skyil krung bzhugs //
NK033(gi)008:1419: steng gi cha la brgyud pa'i bla ma dang //
NK033(gi)008:1420: mtha' bskor mchog gsum mkha' 'gro chos srung tshogs //
