NK033(gi)008:1421: snang stong zung 'jug ye shes sgyu ma'i sku //
NK033(gi)008:1422: gsang gsum mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo' sprin //
NK033(gi)008:1423: gang 'dul mos ngor cir yang 'char bar gyur //
NK033(gi)008:1425: de nas rang dang sems can thams cad sa chen po'i rdul ltar 'khod par gyur pa la /
NK033(gi)008:1426: thams cad lus gus pas thal mo sbyar /
NK033(gi)008:1427: ngag gus pas gsol 'debs kyi tshig dir dir brjod /
NK033(gi)008:1428: yid gus pas skyid sdug legs nyes thams cad khyed gyis mkhyen snyam pa'i blo gtad ling gis 'gel /
NK033(gi)008:1429: de yang bla ma ni sku dge 'dun /
NK033(gi)008:1431: thugs sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin du bzhugs par ma zad /
NK033(gi)008:1432: rang la sngon gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhal mjal
NK033(gi)008:1433: zhing gsung thos pa'i skal ba ma mchis pa'i dus
NK033(gi)008:1434: 'dir de rnams kyis mdzad rgyu bla ma dam pas
NK033(gi)008:1435: mdzad pa dang / rang rgyud la sangs rgyas dngos
NK033(gi)008:1436: su ston pa'i ded dpon bla na med pa yin
NK033(gi)008:1437: pa'i phyir dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun las lhag
NK033(gi)008:1438: cig bka' drin che snyam pa'i blo sna mos gus
NK033(gi)008:1439: su hril gyis dril la brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs yid
NK033(gi)008:1441: bsdu na gten chen rin po ches mdzad pa rje
NK033(gi)008:1442: bla ma'i kha skong dang bcas pa nyid brjod la
NK033(gi)008:1443: / rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma rnams kyi yon tan rjes su dran bzhin pas gsol ba gdab cing /
NK033(gi)008:1444: slar yang rtsa ba'i bla ma la phur tshugs su gsol ba 'debs pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1446: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1447: khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnyen gcig pu //
NK033(gi)008:1448: 'gro ba skyabs med rnams kyi skyabs //
NK033(gi)008:1449: thar pa'i them skas chen po ste //
NK033(gi)008:1450: ma rig sel ba'i sgron me la //
NK033(gi)008:1451: mun pa'i tshogs bdag skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)008:1453: bying ba skyabs med bdag la skyobs //
NK033(gi)008:1454: nyon mongs me yis gdungs pa la //
NK033(gi)008:1455: thugs rje'i char gyis bsil bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1456: bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK033(gi)008:1457: bdag la re sa gzhan na med //
NK033(gi)008:1458: deng nas byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK033(gi)008:1459: skyid sdug re ltos khyed mkhyen pas //
NK033(gi)008:1460: mgon med bdag la thugs rjes gzigs //
NK033(gi)008:1461: nad gdon bgegs dang bar chad sol //
NK033(gi)008:1462: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)008:1463: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK033(gi)008:1464: ces pas mos gus kyi nyams ma skyes bar du gsol ba btab pa'i mthar dbang blang ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:1465: 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams rtsa ba'i bla ma'i sku
NK033(gi)008:1466: la thim pas bla ma sngar bas kyang gzi byin
NK033(gi)008:1467: cher 'bar ba'i gnas gsum du +aahmh'u dkar dmar mthing
NK033(gi)008:1468: gsum 'od 'bar bas mtshan pa de bzhin gshegs pa
NK033(gi)008:1469: thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum gyi bdag nyid du
NK033(gi)008:1470: gyur / bdag dang mkha' khyab kyi sems can thams
NK033(gi)008:1471: cad dbang bzhi'i chu bos rgyud smin cing grol bar
NK033(gi)008:1474: gu ru'i spyi bo'i las 'od zer dkar po 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:1475: rang gi spyi bor thim pas bum pa'i dbang thob /
NK033(gi)008:1477: lam bskyed rim bsgom pa la dbang /
NK033(gi)008:1478: 'bras bu sprul sku thob pa'i skal ba can du byas /
NK033(gi)008:1479: mgrin pa'i +aah las 'od zer dmar po 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:1480: rang gi mgrin par thim pas gsang ba'i dbang thob /
NK033(gi)008:1482: lam rtsa rlung bsgom pa la dbang /
NK033(gi)008:1483: 'bras bu longs sku thob pa'i skal ba can du byas //
NK033(gi)008:1484: thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer sngon po 'phros //
NK033(gi)008:1485: rang gi snying gar thim pas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob /
NK033(gi)008:1487: lam thig le bsgom pa la dbang //
NK033(gi)008:1488: 'bras bu chos sku thob pa'i skal ba can du byas /
NK033(gi)008:1489: slar yang gnas gsum las 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:1490: rang gi gnas gsum du thim pas dbang bzhi pa thob //
NK033(gi)008:1491: ye shes kyi dri ma sbyangs /
NK033(gi)008:1492: lam rdzogs pa chen po bsgom pa la dbang /
NK033(gi)008:1493: 'bras bu ngo bo nyid sku thob pa'i skal ba can du byas so //
NK033(gi)008:1494: slar yang dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad ngo bo
NK033(gi)008:1495: sku bzhi'i bdag nyid dpal ldan bla ma dam pa
NK033(gi)008:1497: bdag la dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1498: zab lam gyi rtogs pa khyad par can rgyud la skye bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)008:1499: ka dag gnas lugs kyi lta ba rtogs par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)008:1500: lhun grub snang bzhi'i ye shes mthar phyin par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)008:1501: zhes mos gus gdung shugs drag pos gsol ba btab
NK033(gi)008:1502: pas bla ma 'od lnga'i gong bur gyur pa rang
NK033(gi)008:1503: gi tshangs bug nas sib kyis thim pas /
NK033(gi)008:1504: rang gi sgo gsum dang bla ma'i rdo rje gsum
NK033(gi)008:1505: dbyer med gyur par bsam la blo 'das gnyug ma'i
NK033(gi)008:1506: rang ngo la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)008:1507: gnyis pa bye brag bla ma'i rim pa dngos grub rgya mtsho ltar nyams su len pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1510: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)008:1511: nges pa'i don du sems bskyed nas //
NK033(gi)008:1512: 'gro la phan phyir bla ma bsgom //
NK033(gi)008:1513: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'i ngang las //
NK033(gi)008:1514: rang gi spyi bor pad+ma dkar po dang nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor bsam pa'i nang na /
NK033(gi)008:1515: a dkar po las 'od 'phros pas rtsa ba'i bla ma spyan drangs nas /
NK033(gi)008:1516: skyil krung phyed pas bzhugs pa la /
NK033(gi)008:1517: brgyud pa'i bla ma dang chos 'brel yod tshad thams cad thim pa'i mthar /
NK033(gi)008:1518: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs mkha' 'gro dam
NK033(gi)008:1519: can rgya mtshos bskor ba sprin phung 'thibs pa ltar
NK033(gi)008:1520: bsam / 'dir yid kyis mchod cing bstod par gsungs
NK033(gi)008:1521: pas de kho nas chog kyang da lta'i gang zag
NK033(gi)008:1522: phal cher la ngag 'don med na rnam pa mi
NK033(gi)008:1525: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)008:1526: skye med bla ma gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1527: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)008:1528: gsal dag bla ma gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1529: sprul pa sku yi pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)008:1530: thugs rje can rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1532: sku dang thig le shigs se shig /
NK033(gi)008:1533: spyi gtsug nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK033(gi)008:1534: bdag dang dbyer med brtan par bzhugs //
NK033(gi)008:1535: lus ngag yid gsum gus phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)008:1536: phyi nang gsang gsum mchod pa 'bul //
NK033(gi)008:1537: sku gsung thugs kyi nyams chag bshags //
NK033(gi)008:1538: smin grol dbang dang gdams pa zhu ///
NK033(gi)008:1539: sku skye ba med pa gsal la dwangs //
NK033(gi)008:1540: rdo rje'i sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)008:1541: lus la bde bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)008:1542: +aah gsung 'gags pa med pa chos kyi sgra /
NK033(gi)008:1544: ngag la nus par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)008:1546: thugs ka dag chen po kun bzang klong //
NK033(gi)008:1547: cir mi dgongs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)008:1548: zad sar 'khyol bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)008:1549: zhes chos spyod chen mo nas 'byung ba ltar brjod //
NK033(gi)008:1551: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa ni //
NK033(gi)008:1552: khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnyen gcig po //
NK033(gi)008:1553: 'gro ba mgon med rnams kyi skyabs //
NK033(gi)008:1554: thar pa'i them skas chen po ste //
NK033(gi)008:1555: ma rig sel ba'i sgron me la //
NK033(gi)008:1556: mun pa'i tshogs dag skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)008:1558: bying ba skyabs med bdag la skyobs //
NK033(gi)008:1559: dug gsum me yis gdungs pa la //
NK033(gi)008:1560: rang byung rlan gyis bsil bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1561: ma rig 'khrul pas bcings pa yi //
NK033(gi)008:1562: gdos bcas lus ngag yid rnams kun //
NK033(gi)008:1563: rang dengs 'od kyi rang bzhin du //
NK033(gi)008:1564: lhag med mya ngan 'das thob mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1565: bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK033(gi)008:1566: bdag la re sa gzhan na med //
NK033(gi)008:1567: thugs rje'i spyan gyis gzigs mdzod la //
NK033(gi)008:1568: 'khor ba'i mtsho las bsgral du gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1570: bgegs dang bar chad med pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:1572: bar do'i 'phrang las sgrol bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1573: lus dang ngag yad brtsams pa kun //
NK033(gi)008:1574: rtag tu gzhan la phan pa dang //
NK033(gi)008:1575: rkyen rnams byang chub lam mchog tu //
NK033(gi)008:1576: de ring nyid nas bsgyur du gsol //
NK033(gi)008:1577: bdag gis 'bad kyang thar pa dka' //
NK033(gi)008:1578: mgon po khyed kyi thugs rje'i grus //
NK033(gi)008:1579: mgon med bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK033(gi)008:1580: thar pa'i gling du phyin par mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1581: gang dag bdag la dad gyur tam //
NK033(gi)008:1582: smod dam skur pa 'debs kyang rung //
NK033(gi)008:1583: de dag sdig byang nyon mongs med //
NK033(gi)008:1584: srid pa'i chu bo spang par shog /
NK033(gi)008:1585: nam zhig bdag gi ming tsam gyis //
NK033(gi)008:1587: phyogs bcu gang ba'i zhing rnams su //
NK033(gi)008:1588: mchod pa'i sprin gyis char 'bebs shog /
NK033(gi)008:1589: dge ba 'di yis lus can kun //
NK033(gi)008:1590: thams cad srid las rnam grol nas //
NK033(gi)008:1591: ye shes dam pa gnyis thob ste //
NK033(gi)008:1592: don gnyis lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)008:1593: ces gsol ba drag tu btab pas //
NK033(gi)008:1594: zhabs kyi mthe bong las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs //
NK033(gi)008:1595: bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi spyi bo nas zhugs lus phyi nang thams cad la khyab pas /
NK033(gi)008:1606: yon tan gyi dngos grub thob /
NK033(gi)008:1608: phrin las kyi dngos grub thob /
NK033(gi)008:1609: bde ba dang stong pa gnyis su med par gyur /
NK033(gi)008:1610: mthar mos gus kyi shugs kyis bla ma 'od du
NK033(gi)008:1611: zhu nas rang la thim pas dbyer med du gyur
NK033(gi)008:1612: par mos la bcos bslad bral ba'i rang rig gi
NK033(gi)008:1613: ngo bo ci nus bskyang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:1615: rang bzhin dag pa'i dge ba 'dis //
NK033(gi)008:1616: 'khor ba ngan song dong sprugs te //
NK033(gi)008:1617: srid na 'ga' yang mi gnas par //
NK033(gi)008:1618: thams cad sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK033(gi)008:1619: ces sogs bsngo smon gyis mtshams sbyar te spyod lam la 'jug /
NK033(gi)008:1620: thun mtshams thams cad du'ang snang grags rigs gsum bla
NK033(gi)008:1621: ma'i gsang ba gsum gyi ye shes su lam du
NK033(gi)008:1622: khyer zhing tshogs gnyis zung 'brel gyi rnal 'byor la
NK033(gi)008:1623: brtson par bya'o // 'dir rnams bzhag go don phan yon sogs spro na spyi dang mtshungs par 'chad /
NK033(gi)008:1624: tshogs bsags kyi rim pa 'di dag so sor 'bum
NK033(gi)008:1625: ther la sogs pa thun du bcad de brtson pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1626: skabs so so'i rjes su bsngo smon gyi rgyas gdab
NK033(gi)008:1627: pa dang / thun mtshams rnams su skabs de dang
NK033(gi)008:1628: der 'brel ba'i lam khyer gyi gnad sogs kyang spyi
NK033(gi)008:1630: sngon 'gro spyir bshad pa de rnams smin gling khrid rgyun dkyus su 'byung ba yin cing /
NK033(gi)008:1631: de'ang khrid tshul spyi dang mthun pa'i 'don sgom zor yang gtso bor bton par snang la /
NK033(gi)008:1632: bye brag tu bstan pa rnams ni yang tig yid
NK033(gi)008:1633: bzhin nor bu las dngos su gsal ba'i thun mong
NK033(gi)008:1635: rje bla mas kyang 'di ltar legs zhes dngos su bkas gnang ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:1636: rig 'dzin chen po sogs kyi khrid rgyun las kyang
NK033(gi)008:1637: 'byung bar snang bas 'don sgom mdzad na dgos pa
NK033(gi)008:1638: che snyam yig tshogs la ma 'dzem par dkyus su
NK033(gi)008:1640: bzhi pa gsang sngags spyi mthun gyi thabs lam rlung thig gis lus sems sbyong ba la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:1641: chags bral rlung la bslab pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1642: chags can thig le la slob pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:1644: rlung gi kha dog la slob pa /
NK033(gi)008:1648: bum pa can la slob pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:1650: lus gnad chos bdun drang por bsrangs la mig gnad mtho dman bying rgod dang mthun par blta /
NK033(gi)008:1651: ngag gnad sna bug gnyis nas rlung ro dal la ring ba gsum bsal /
NK033(gi)008:1652: yid kyi gnad smin mtshams su rlung rnams 'dus pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1653: ngo bo thig le dkar po yungs 'bru tsam gsal
NK033(gi)008:1654: zhing 'bar ba zhig gsal btab la re dogs skyon
NK033(gi)008:1655: yon dgag sgrub sogs dus gsum gyi rnam par rtog
NK033(gi)008:1656: pa kun spangs te thig le'i rnam pa de kha
NK033(gi)008:1657: la sems rtse gcig tu gtad la bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:1658: rnam rtog che phra ji ltar shar yang 'phro bcad
NK033(gi)008:1659: la thig le'i steng du hril gyis bsgrims la 'jog
NK033(gi)008:1660: / yang rig pa g.yer zhing 'phro rgod cher song
NK033(gi)008:1661: na thig le'i rnam pa yid kyi yul du lam
NK033(gi)008:1662: mer gsal ba la ha cang grims ma drags tsam
NK033(gi)008:1663: gyis dran pa'i rgyang so btsugs la lhod kyis 'jog
NK033(gi)008:1664: / ste / rang rig dang thig le so sor
NK033(gi)008:1665: mi blta bar dbyer med rang gsal zhen 'dzin med
NK033(gi)008:1667: thig le'i rnam pa kho na la sems zin cing brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1668: thig le'i mdangs 'od kyis rang gi mgo bo dang de nas lus /
NK033(gi)008:1669: de nas tho phyi dang yul khams thams cad khyab /
NK033(gi)008:1670: mthar snang ba thams cad rlung gi rang bzhin dkar me re ba la shes pa gtad /
NK033(gi)008:1672: smin mtshams rtsa ba'i thig le la shes pa gtad /
NK033(gi)008:1673: de ltar spro bsdu res 'jog la bslab pas lus yang /
NK033(gi)008:1675: sems gnas pa sogs rtags ma thon gyi bar du bsgom pa ni phyi ma rnams la'ang 'gre /
NK033(gi)008:1677: sna rtser rlung gi thig le dkar sngo che chung bod sran tsam pa zhig gsal btab /
NK033(gi)008:1678: de gsal ba dang sna bug gi rlung 'gro 'ong
NK033(gi)008:1679: dal ba la brten nas rlung phyir dbyung tshe thig
NK033(gi)008:1680: le de rlung dang 'grogs nas skya yer gyis song
NK033(gi)008:1681: / nang du 'jug tshe rlung dang lhan cig byung ba sna rtser grang bsil gyis gnas par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:1682: de yang lus grang shas che na thig le kha dog dmar po reg bya tsha bar bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:1683: yang na mdzod spur bsgoms kyang chog gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:1685: rlung dang shes pa 'gro dog gcig tu byas te /
NK033(gi)008:1686: rgyun gyi dbugs 'byung 'jug gnas gsum pa 'di ga
NK033(gi)008:1687: rang bab tu bgrang ba la shes pa rtse gcig
NK033(gi)008:1688: tu gtad de khug pa re la gcig tu brtsis
NK033(gi)008:1689: pa'i grangs ma yengs par bzung /
NK033(gi)008:1690: rim gyis rgyu ba je dal je ring la btang
NK033(gi)008:1691: nas mthar yun ring gnas pa ma byung gi bar
NK033(gi)008:1692: du sbyang ngo // bzhi pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1693: rang lus stong chen sgrib thogs dang bral ba'i lte
NK033(gi)008:1694: bar thod pa phyi dkar la nang dmar ba dpral
NK033(gi)008:1695: ba mdun phyogs su bstan pa zhig gsal gdab /
NK033(gi)008:1696: de'i nang du rlung gi rdo rje sngon po gyen
NK033(gi)008:1697: langs nas 'bras tsam pa la sems gtad nas ci
NK033(gi)008:1698: nus bsgom / de la gsal brtan gyi nyams skyes
NK033(gi)008:1699: pa na sna sgo'i rlung 'gro 'ong dang bstun nas
NK033(gi)008:1700: nus bsgom / / rlung phyir 'gro ba'i tshe rdo rje sna bug g.yas nas sngo rgyang gis song /
NK033(gi)008:1701: tshur 'ong ba na g.yon nas zhugs te thod par gnas par bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1702: lus sems bde phril phril ba la blo bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:1703: goms nas sems gnas je brtan du song rim bzhin
NK033(gi)008:1704: rdo rje phyir 'gro ba'i tshad je thung du btang
NK033(gi)008:1705: / mthar sna rtse'i sor bcu drug gi tshad tsam du 'gro 'ong byed par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:1707: snga ma goms pa dang dmigs pa'i gzhi sngar gyis
NK033(gi)008:1708: 'gro 'ong de ka lan kha shas byas rjes rlung
NK033(gi)008:1709: phral ring ba zhig 'phangs pas rdo rje sna bug
NK033(gi)008:1710: g.yas kyi lam nas rgyang ring por song bar bsam
NK033(gi)008:1712: de nas rlung nang du shar gyis drangs pas rdo rje sna bug g.yon nas zhugs /
NK033(gi)008:1713: lte ba'i thod pa la sib kyis thim par bsam la bum can g.yo med kha sbyor du 'ching /
NK033(gi)008:1714: de'i tshe thod pa yang zhu nas ha yig dmar
NK033(gi)008:1715: po'i rnam par gyur pa la blo bzhag ste rlung
NK033(gi)008:1716: dang lus thams cad na bun yal ba ltar bun
NK033(gi)008:1717: long du gyur par bsam la /
NK033(gi)008:1718: bum pa can gyi rlung sbyor ba bzhi ldan drag tu dgang /
NK033(gi)008:1719: rlung gtong ba'i tshe rlung sems nam mkha' dang bsres nas mi rtog pa'i ngang du bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:1720: gong du bum can 'byongs zin pa yin na 'dir ci nus re bsgoms pas chog go //
NK033(gi)008:1721: de min rab 'bring tha ma gang rung ma 'grub
NK033(gi)008:1722: kyi bar du sbyang zhing de'ang thog mar ha cang
NK033(gi)008:1723: ma drags pa'i ran par bzung na gegs chung ba
NK033(gi)008:1724: yin no // lus gnad dang rlung ro bsal ba
NK033(gi)008:1725: ni spyi gnad yin pas gong smos ltar thams cad
NK033(gi)008:1726: yin no // la sbyar ro // gnyis pa chags can thig le'i rnal 'byor la bslab pa la /
NK033(gi)008:1727: dngos rig ma la brten nas yum gyi bde ba
NK033(gi)008:1728: la slob pa ni lag tu mi lon pas khrid
NK033(gi)008:1730: de'i tshul bde stong bdud rtsi'i sprin phung sogs su gsal ba ltar ro //
NK033(gi)008:1731: rjes mthun rlung rig gi bde ba la slob pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1732: lus gnad rkang pa skyil krung /
NK033(gi)008:1733: lag pa khu tshur kha sbub pus mo'am barla steng du bzhag la lag ngar bsrang /
NK033(gi)008:1734: mig thad kar cher re mig 'bras mi bsgyur zhing rdzi ma mi brdeb /
NK033(gi)008:1735: sems gnad rang lus stong gsal phru ma phus btab pa ltar gyur pa'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)008:1736: rtsa dbu ma sbom phra mda' smyug 'bring po tsam pa /
NK033(gi)008:1737: kha dog dmar skya'am phyi dkar la nar dmar ba
NK033(gi)008:1738: yid yul du gsal gang bde ba zhig bsgoms la
NK033(gi)008:1739: / de yang yar sna tshangs bug dang mar sna
NK033(gi)008:1740: lte 'og sor bzhi'i thad du chu shing gi sdong
NK033(gi)008:1741: po ltar drang zhing til gyi mar me bzhin du
NK033(gi)008:1743: pad+ma'i snal ma lta shin tu srab pa /
NK033(gi)008:1744: de'i g.yas su ro ma dmar po dang g.yon du
NK033(gi)008:1745: rkyang ma dkar po dbu ma las ldabs 'gyur gyis
NK033(gi)008:1746: phra ba / yar sna smin mtshams kyi thad nas
NK033(gi)008:1747: gugs te sna bug g.yas g.yon du zug cing mas
NK033(gi)008:1748: sna gnyis dbu ma'i mas snar tshud pa /
NK033(gi)008:1749: de ltar rtsa gsum sum gshibs su thal gyis yod
NK033(gi)008:1750: pa las 'khor lo bzhi'i mtshams rnams su ro rkyang
NK033(gi)008:1751: gnyis dbu ma la thim pa'i tshul gyis nang khongs
NK033(gi)008:1753: de las gyes pa'i 'khor lo bzhi bsgom ste /
NK033(gi)008:1754: de yang dbu ma'i yar sne las rtse sor gnyis
NK033(gi)008:1755: gzhal ba'i mtshams na rtse mo rnam par bkod pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1756: 'khor lo / mgrin pa'i phrag pa skye mtshams nas ro rnams 'dus pa'i 'khor lo /
NK033(gi)008:1757: snying ga'i nu phrag gi thad nas dran pa 'dus pa'i 'khor lo /
NK033(gi)008:1758: lte khung gi thad nas skyed byed kyi 'khor lo ste /
NK033(gi)008:1759: thams cad kyang kha dog dmar skya dwangs gsal sbubs stong gi rnam pa gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)008:1760: de nas spyi bor rtse mo rnam bkod kyi 'khor
NK033(gi)008:1761: lo'i dbus su thig le stong pa'i sgron ma kha
NK033(gi)008:1762: dog dkar la snum zhing 'dril ba sran ma tsam
NK033(gi)008:1763: zhig gsal btab nas de nyid la sems rtse gcig
NK033(gi)008:1765: de la sems zin pa na rlung ro lan gsum bsal la steng rlung nar gyis rngubs /
NK033(gi)008:1766: lte bar bskyur thabs su mnan cing 'og rlung drag
NK033(gi)008:1767: tu bskums pas thig le de nyid 'dar phri li
NK033(gi)008:1769: de las byang sems bde ba'i rgyun sran chung tsam
NK033(gi)008:1770: gcig rjes gcig non du bde phri li li babs
NK033(gi)008:1771: pa'am / yang na ba thag lta bu na ra ra babs pa gang bde byas la spyi bo /
NK033(gi)008:1774: lte ba'i 'khor lo bzhi rim par gang bas dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes skyes par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:1775: thig le gsang bar brtan par gyur pas dngos po
NK033(gi)008:1776: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong bar
NK033(gi)008:1777: bsam zhing / de re re'i ngang mdangs bskyangs la
NK033(gi)008:1778: bum can ci nus bzung bas bde ba je rgyas
NK033(gi)008:1779: bsam zhing / su song / lus sems bde bas khyab /
NK033(gi)008:1780: slar yang gyen du rim gyis drangs pas mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi nyams su myong /
NK033(gi)008:1781: spyi bo'i thig le la sib sib thim zhing brtan
NK033(gi)008:1782: par gyur pas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK033(gi)008:1783: shes nyams su myong bar bsam la de'i ngang mdangs
NK033(gi)008:1784: ci nus bskyang / mthar thig le de je phrar
NK033(gi)008:1785: gyur te mi dmigs spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK033(gi)008:1787: bde stong zung 'jug rang rig rang gsal de nyid thun mtshams rnams su yang bskyang ci thub bya /
NK033(gi)008:1788: 'dir lte bar a thung mi bsgoms pa ni man ngag gi khyad par yin cing /
NK033(gi)008:1789: bde stong bdud rtsi'i sprin phung gi rang lus sbyong
NK033(gi)008:1790: skabs lte ba'i a thung bsgom par yang gsungs pas
NK033(gi)008:1791: bde drod skye dka' ba'i rigs la de ltar yang
NK033(gi)008:1793: de ltar 'bad pas lus sems bde stong du 'gro
NK033(gi)008:1794: zhing rlung thig las su rung bas 'byung ba lnga
NK033(gi)008:1796: zas skom gyi sred pa las grol /
NK033(gi)008:1798: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i bsam gtan gyi rim
NK033(gi)008:1799: pa dpag tu med pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa
NK033(gi)008:1801: de ltar chags bral rlung gi rnal 'byor dang /
NK033(gi)008:1802: chags can thig le'i rnal 'byor ni lam gzhan las
NK033(gi)008:1803: rlung 'byongs pa'i gang zag la ma bshad kyang chad
NK033(gi)008:1805: kun mkhyen chen po'i don khrid du'ang ma gsungs pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1806: rtsa rlung mi chun pa'i gang zag la ma bstan
NK033(gi)008:1808: lnga pa dran pa rgyun gcod kyi man ngag gis
NK033(gi)008:1809: 'byung bar rang sar dengs par byed pa'i gnad bstan
NK033(gi)008:1810: pa la gnyis / a lnga skye med kyi don nyams su len pa /
NK033(gi)008:1811: 'byung 'khrungs byings rgod kyi gegs sel ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:1813: 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud chen nam mkha' la //
NK033(gi)008:1814: 'khrul gzhi zad pa'i rig pa rgod yan de //
NK033(gi)008:1815: sna tshogs khyab brdal chen po'i khang bzang du //
NK033(gi)008:1816: 'dzin byed dran pa zad pa'i lcags kyu yis //
NK033(gi)008:1817: gsal byed steng 'og med pa'i snying nang ni //
NK033(gi)008:1818: ma yengs bsam pa zad pa'i tshul gyis bzung //
NK033(gi)008:1820: a lnga'i don skye ba med pa nyams su blang
NK033(gi)008:1821: bar bagyi'o snyam nas lus gnad rnam snang chos bdun
NK033(gi)008:1822: bca' / rlung kha nas drangs te dal bus phyir btang /
NK033(gi)008:1823: dal bus nang du rngubs la rtsol ba lhod pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1824: ngang cung zad 'then la snying gar nam mkha' rnam
NK033(gi)008:1825: par dag pa'i ngo bo a sngon po tshon gang
NK033(gi)008:1827: der shes pa gtad de rlung sems kyi 'du byed
NK033(gi)008:1828: thams cad bstims nas rtog med spros bral gyi ngang
NK033(gi)008:1829: la bzhag pas nam mkha' dag parabyeda do //
NK033(gi)008:1830: de bzhin du spyi bo'i 'khor lo'am sna rtse'i thad
NK033(gi)008:1831: kyi mdun du rlung rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo
NK033(gi)008:1832: +aa ljang gu nyis brtsegs la shes pa gtad de
NK033(gi)008:1833: rlung dang rnam rtog g.yo ba thams cad bstims nas
NK033(gi)008:1834: sngar ltar bsgoms pas rlung dag par byed do //
NK033(gi)008:1835: yang snying ga'am sna rtser chu rnam par dag pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1836: ngo bo +aaa&a&a&a dkar po sum brtsegs la shes pa
NK033(gi)008:1837: gtad de 'du shes dang rlung thams cad dran pa
NK033(gi)008:1838: rang yal du btang nas rlung phyir 'dzin cung zad
NK033(gi)008:1839: dang dbugs kyi 'gyu ba bcad de bzhag pas chu
NK033(gi)008:1841: yang mgrin pa'i mdun mkhar me rnam par dag pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1842: ngo bo +aaaa&a&a&a dmar po bzhi brtsegs la shes pa
NK033(gi)008:1843: gtad de 'dzin yul tshor sogs sdud byed kyi dwangs
NK033(gi)008:1844: ma mig gi rnam shes rang dag la sems bzung
NK033(gi)008:1845: bas me dag par byed do //
NK033(gi)008:1846: yang lte ba'i bar snang la sa rnam par dag
NK033(gi)008:1847: pa'i ngo bo yi ge +aa aaa&&& ser po lnga
NK033(gi)008:1848: brtsegs la shes pa gtad de bzung yul mched pa
NK033(gi)008:1849: thams cad bstims nas sgo lnga 'dzin med du bzhag
NK033(gi)008:1850: pas sa rnam par dag par byed do //
NK033(gi)008:1851: rang byung zhabs kyi man ngag tu rlung ro bsal
NK033(gi)008:1852: ba dang bcas bum pa can gyi rlung sbyor byas
NK033(gi)008:1853: / rtsa gsum 'khor lo bzhi gsal btab /
NK033(gi)008:1854: 'khor lo so so'i lte bar gnas kyi rang mdog dang mtshungs pa'i a lnga brtsegs re re bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:1855: re re bzhin rlung sems bstims la rlung khug ji ltar rigs pa bzung /
NK033(gi)008:1856: mthar de rnams rang yal mi rtog pa'i ngang du blo 'jog par gsung so //
NK033(gi)008:1858: de ltar sgom pa'i skabs su 'byung ba 'khrugs pa
NK033(gi)008:1859: dang bying rgod shas che bar gyur na de dag
NK033(gi)008:1861: snying thig chen mo ltar na /
NK033(gi)008:1862: sa'i skyon gyis lus lci zhing sems bying 'thibs su
NK033(gi)008:1863: gyur pa la spyi bo'i 'khor lor yam ljang nag
NK033(gi)008:1864: bsgoms pa la rlung sems gtad de rlung bzung /
NK033(gi)008:1865: gtong ba na nam mkhar sngo phyur phyur song bar bsams pas sel lo //
NK033(gi)008:1866: yang chu'i skyon gyis grang zhing 'dar na mgrin pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1867: 'khor lor ram dmar po 'bar ba sgom zhing rlung
NK033(gi)008:1868: drag gcun pas lte 'og rtsa gsum 'dus mdo'i ha
NK033(gi)008:1869: yig dmar po las kyang me 'bar bas lus kyi
NK033(gi)008:1870: nang gang bar bsam na sel lo //
NK033(gi)008:1871: yang me'i skyon gyis tsha zhing lus gtse ba sogs
NK033(gi)008:1872: byung na snying ga'i 'khor lo'am pho bar kham dkar
NK033(gi)008:1873: bsil 'khyag pa lta bu bsgom la so bar nas
NK033(gi)008:1874: sid kyi sgras rlung dbyung bas sel lo //
NK033(gi)008:1875: yang rlung gi skyon gyis shes pa 'phyo zhing stod
NK033(gi)008:1876: 'tshangs pa sogs byung na lte bar lam ser po
NK033(gi)008:1877: lci thibs zhig bsgoms la rlung sems mthur du gtad
NK033(gi)008:1878: pas sel lo // de dag thams cad la'ang bum pa can gyi rlung sbyor bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:1879: yang tig yid bzhin nor bu ltar na /
NK033(gi)008:1880: bde chen 'khor lo'i ham las thig le dkar bsil babs pas nad song bar bsgoms la /
NK033(gi)008:1881: rlung phyir sangs sangs phul la phyir gzung /
NK033(gi)008:1882: grang ba la lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lor ram /
NK033(gi)008:1883: de las me 'bar bas bsreg par bsam la /
NK033(gi)008:1884: rlung kha sbyar la nang du gzung /
NK033(gi)008:1885: bad kan la'angade dang 'dra ba las /
NK033(gi)008:1886: khyad par du longs spyod 'khor lo'i t+r+aam las bdud rtsi babs pas nad sangs bar bsams te /
NK033(gi)008:1887: rlung phyir gsum gsum phul la nang du re re gzung /
NK033(gi)008:1888: sems rgod cing pra yas na bde skyong 'khor lo'i ham las /
NK033(gi)008:1889: bde drod 'bar ba la sems bzung zhing rlung bzung /
NK033(gi)008:1890: sgom dus ting nge 'dzin ji ltar byas kyang ma
NK033(gi)008:1891: skyes na chos kyi 'khor lo'i h'u las spyi bo'i
NK033(gi)008:1892: dwangs ma babs par bsams te rlung nang du bzung
NK033(gi)008:1893: bas / nad kun zhi zhing ting nge 'dzin rang lugs su skye ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:1895: 'di'i dus su yi ge de dag ngag tu yang brjod cing /
NK033(gi)008:1896: ha dang h'u dang a mang po 'don pa ni thabs so //
NK033(gi)008:1898: gnyis pa dngos gzhi sems rig gtan la 'bebs pa
NK033(gi)008:1899: 'od gsal snying po'i don khrid bstan pa la gnyis
NK033(gi)008:1900: / sems gtan la dbab pa'i man ngag gzhi khregs chod /
NK033(gi)008:1901: rig pa gtan la dbab pa'i man ngag lam thod rgal gyi khrid bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:1903: lta sgom 'byed pa'i lde'i mig sbas pa mig 'byed las /
NK033(gi)008:1904: 'dzin chags med pa'i spyod pa'i man ngag gis snang ba zil gyis mnan pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1905: dmigs gtad med pa sgom pa'i man ngag gis dran byed kyi yid zil gyis mnan pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1906: gza' gtad med pa lta ba'i man ngag gis zhen pa'i gzhi nyon mongs zil gyis mnan pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1907: spangs thob med pa 'bras bu'i man ngag gis rig pa phyir mi ldog par bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:1909: de dag la'ang chos can spyi ste rdzogs pa chen po spyi dang /
NK033(gi)008:1910: chos nyid rang gi bye brag ces yang gsang thig
NK033(gi)008:1911: le'i man ngag 'di nyid kyi lugs dang sbyar ba'i
NK033(gi)008:1912: gnyis gnyis / de re re la'ang gang gis /
NK033(gi)008:1915: gang thob ces don bzhi bzhi'i sgo nas bstan pa
NK033(gi)008:1916: rnams spyod pa bsdus pa'i sgron ma sogs sgron ma
NK033(gi)008:1917: skor bzhi las rim gyis rtogs par bya dgos shing
NK033(gi)008:1918: / 'dir spyi tsam du bstan pa la bzhi /
NK033(gi)008:1923: dang po 'dzin chags med pa spyod pa'i man ngag la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:1924: las dang po pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1925: mi dge ba cha dang bcas pa 'dor zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1926: dge ba cha dang bcas pa spel ba ste /
NK033(gi)008:1927: rnal 'byor pas kyang spang blang shes nas /
NK033(gi)008:1928: bla ma dam pa'i drung du song la /
NK033(gi)008:1929: thos pas chos dang chos ma yin pa shes shing /
NK033(gi)008:1930: zab mo'i gdams pa kha tshang ba nyan la tshig gi sgro 'dogs bcad cing /
NK033(gi)008:1931: bsam pas de'i don nor 'khrul med pa'i gnad mi 'chug par bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:1932: 'khor ba las blo ldog pa'i thabs la bslab bo //
NK033(gi)008:1933: snying po lhur blang ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1934: de nas rgyus med pa'i sa phyogs su phyin la /
NK033(gi)008:1935: sprang po'am ri dwags ltar gcig pur bla ma'i gdams
NK033(gi)008:1936: ngag la spyad de zas gos ngan ngon gyis chos
NK033(gi)008:1938: gdams pa gzhan la dngo mtshar du mi 'dzin par
NK033(gi)008:1939: rang gi man ngag la yid ches par bya zhing
NK033(gi)008:1940: / bya byed rtsol sgrub kyi chos tshe 'di'i 'khri
NK033(gi)008:1941: ba dang bcas pa thams cad lings kyis bsgyur nas
NK033(gi)008:1943: sngon du 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pas
NK033(gi)008:1944: lus ngag yid gsum gyi zhen pa log par bya
NK033(gi)008:1945: zhing / de nas su dang yang 'brel 'dris med
NK033(gi)008:1946: par lkugs pa lta bu'i spyod pas ngag bcad la
NK033(gi)008:1947: brda tsam yang mi bya bar bu chung lta bu'i
NK033(gi)008:1948: spyod pa tshogs drug lhug par klod nas chos nyid
NK033(gi)008:1949: kyi don la bsgom par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:1950: brtul zhugs lam slong gi spyod pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1951: de nas mi phod pa la thog 'gel du byed pas /
NK033(gi)008:1952: sems kyi 'khri ba btsan thabs su bcad cing /
NK033(gi)008:1953: gtsang btsog med pa khyi phag lta bu'i spyod pas blang dor gyi zhen pa 'dor ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:1954: shugs 'byung 'gags med smyon pa lta bu'i spyod pas
NK033(gi)008:1955: rig pa'i sna mi bskyil bar zang thal la spyod
NK033(gi)008:1956: pas snang ba thams cad grogs su 'char ba yin
NK033(gi)008:1957: no // de nas gzhan gyi mi dad pa bsgyur nus pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1958: bsad pa gso nus pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1959: 'byung bzhi dang rlung sems la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)008:1960: zhen 'khris bag la nyal ba gcad pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)008:1961: rig pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa tshong dus la sogs par yang byas pas /
NK033(gi)008:1962: nang gi nyon mongs pa chod pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:1963: phyi'i snang ba dbang du 'dus pa dus mnyam du
NK033(gi)008:1964: 'byung ste snang ba dbang sgyur gyi spyod pa zhes
NK033(gi)008:1965: bya'o // mdor na spyod pa dus tshod dang 'grel ba la bslab bo //
NK033(gi)008:1966: gnyis pa dmigs gtad med pa sgom pa'i man ngag la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:1967: sems kyi sna khrid pa sgo gsum gyi sngon 'gro sems rnal du dbab pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:1972: dang po lus rdo rje'i 'dug stangs la slob pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:1973: sgrub pa pos 'jig rten gyi bya ba thams cad
NK033(gi)008:1974: blos ling gis btang nas gcig pur dben par gnas
NK033(gi)008:1975: te rang gi mdun gyi nam mkhar thig le mthing
NK033(gi)008:1976: kha'i dkyil na bka' drin mnyam med drin can rtsa
NK033(gi)008:1977: ba'i bla ma de nyid sku dngos kyi rnam pa
NK033(gi)008:1978: la gcer bu ang rag gsol ba /
NK033(gi)008:1979: rdo rje'i 'dug stangs can zhig bsgoms te de la
NK033(gi)008:1980: dmigs nas gdung shugs kyi gsol 'debs drag tu bya
NK033(gi)008:1981: / lus brdab chag mi 'byung ba'i gdan 'bol ba
NK033(gi)008:1982: rgya cher bting ba sogs nyer bsdogs legs par byas
NK033(gi)008:1983: / nas / gcer bur ang rag dang ldan pas lus bsrangs te rkang mthil gnyis sprad /
NK033(gi)008:1985: lag gnyis gru mo brgyangs te thal mo mgo la
NK033(gi)008:1986: ma reg par sbyar ba rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i
NK033(gi)008:1987: 'dug stangs byas la mig bar snang la ha re
NK033(gi)008:1988: gtad / dmigs pa rang lus rdo rje sngon po me 'bar ba zhig tu bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:1989: mdun gyi bla ma h'u mthing nag tu gyur /
NK033(gi)008:1990: rang lus rdo rje'i rnam pa'i lte ba hril po'i nang du bzhugs pa la cung zad sems gtad /
NK033(gi)008:1991: de yang yal nas snying ga'i mi shigs pa'i thig
NK033(gi)008:1992: le'i dwangs ma dang dbyer med du gyur par mos
NK033(gi)008:1993: la / 'a a sha sa ma ha /
NK033(gi)008:1994: zhes rdzogs chen yig drug brjod /
NK033(gi)008:1995: de nas sems dus gsum gyi spros pa bcad nas
NK033(gi)008:1996: spros bral rnam par mi rtog pa kho na ma
NK033(gi)008:1997: gtogs 'gyu ba'i rnam pa phra mos kyang ma rig
NK033(gi)008:1998: par rtog med du bzhag nas lus rang shugs kyis
NK033(gi)008:1999: hal te ma 'gyel bar du bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:2000: 'gyel rjes kyang 'gyel lugs ji ltar byas pa'i steng
NK033(gi)008:2001: de na lus g.yo 'gul bzo bcos mi bya zhing
NK033(gi)008:2002: / sems kyang rtog med du 'jog pa rgyang tsam bya /
NK033(gi)008:2003: yang bla ma bsgom nas brtsams sngar bzhin bya ba
NK033(gi)008:2004: ci nus su thun du bcad nas nyi ma gsum
NK033(gi)008:2007: dang po lus na zhing sha kor rtser 'phar ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2008: khang rul zhig pa'i rnam pa ltar shag shag tshugs
NK033(gi)008:2009: mi thub pa 'byung yang sran bskyed nas bsgoms pas
NK033(gi)008:2010: mthar lus 'bol le shig ge ba dang bde drod
NK033(gi)008:2011: skye ba byung na gnad du song ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:2012: de la thun mong gi dgos pa ni lus kyi mngon zhen bzlog pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2016: lus mngal gyi grong khyer mi 'jug pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2018: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sku rdo rje dang gnyis su med par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:2019: gnyis pa ngag gi sngon 'gro la bzhi /
NK033(gi)008:2025: phyi snang ba la rgyas gdab pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2026: nang phung po la rgyas gdab pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2028: mdun mkhar ram sku dngos kyi rnam pa thig le
NK033(gi)008:2029: mthing kha'i dkyil du rdo rje skyil krung gis bzhugs
NK033(gi)008:2030: pa la mos gus drag pos gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)008:2031: rang nyid lus gnad rnam snang chos bdun lta stangs sna rtser gtod nas /
NK033(gi)008:2032: rang gi snying ga yang gzhir gnas kyi h'u sngon po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)008:2033: mthar mdun gyi bla ma h'u du gyur /
NK033(gi)008:2034: snying kha'i h'u la thim par bsam la dar cig
NK033(gi)008:2035: klod rjes mchu so gnyis ma reg tsam byas la
NK033(gi)008:2036: h'u gi glu che chung ran par brjod pas /
NK033(gi)008:2037: snying ga'i h'u las h'u mang po sna bug g.yas nas thon /
NK033(gi)008:2038: rang gang gnas kyi khang khyim sogs rim gyis gang /
NK033(gi)008:2039: mthar phyi rol gyi snang ba thams cad h'u gis me re re gang bar gyur cing /
NK033(gi)008:2040: thams cad h'u gi sgra dir dir sgrog pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2041: yom yom shig shig g.yo ba la shes pa gtad de cung zad klod la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)008:2043: h'u de dag slar sna bug g.yon nas zhugs /
NK033(gi)008:2044: rang lus kyi spyi bo nas rkang sen gyi bar
NK033(gi)008:2045: du mer khrig gtem tser gyis gang ba la dmigs
NK033(gi)008:2047: rig 'dzin chen pos 'di gnyis so sor bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2048: rjes ma'i skabs phyi rol nas thol byung gi h'u
NK033(gi)008:2049: mang po sna bug nas zhugs pa las snga ma
NK033(gi)008:2050: tshur bsdu ba 'di mtha' gcig tu mi dgos gsungs
NK033(gi)008:2051: / gnyis pa rtsal sbyong ba la'ang gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:2052: dang po phyi snang ba la rtsal sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:2053: mdun du bla ma bsgom pa dang gsol 'debs sngar ltar la /
NK033(gi)008:2054: rang gi snying khar gzhir gnas kyi h'u mthing nag me 'bar ba gcig tu bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:2055: mthar bla ma yang de lta bu'i h'u du gyur nas de la bstim pa ni khyad par ro //
NK033(gi)008:2056: de nas ngag tu h'u thung la drag par brjod
NK033(gi)008:2057: pas snying ga'i h'u las h'u tsha ba me lta
NK033(gi)008:2058: bu / myur ba glog lta bu /
NK033(gi)008:2059: rno ba spu gri lta bu /
NK033(gi)008:2060: shugs thog lta bu thol thol 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:2061: thog mar rang gi mdun gyi dngos po gang rung
NK033(gi)008:2062: de shog bu la me stag phog pa ltar phar
NK033(gi)008:2063: thal tshur thal du phug pas khral khrol la song
NK033(gi)008:2064: / de nas dngos po rnams rim gyis phug cing sbyangs nas mthar /
NK033(gi)008:2065: dngos por grub pa til 'bru tsam yang ma lus
NK033(gi)008:2066: par thams cad h'u gi rang bzhin du shig shig
NK033(gi)008:2067: gang bar bsam la cung zad mnyam par 'jog go
NK033(gi)008:2068: // gnyis pa nang phung po la rtsal sbyong ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:2070: snying ga'i h'u las h'u yig khyad chos bzhi ldan mang po 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:2071: rang lus spyi bo nas rkang mthil gyi bar rta
NK033(gi)008:2072: rnga gshags pa'i cha tsam yang ma lus par yar
NK033(gi)008:2073: thal mar thal / phar thal tshur thal dang /
NK033(gi)008:2074: phyi nas kyang thol skyes rang shar du byung ba'i
NK033(gi)008:2075: h'u yig khyad chos bzhi ldan nang du 'ong bas
NK033(gi)008:2076: kyang de bzhin du thogs pa med par phug nas
NK033(gi)008:2078: h'u drag la thung ba ngar bskyed nas ngag tu
NK033(gi)008:2079: yang brjod pas sha 'phar ba dang khral khrol du
NK033(gi)008:2081: 'dis gdon gyi gnod pa la sogs pa yod kyang 'joms zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2082: gdon thon pa'i rtags su 'dar ba dang 'khrigs pa la sogs pa 'byung /
NK033(gi)008:2083: de dus bar bar du ngal gso zhing bsgom pas gdon las grol bar 'gyur /
NK033(gi)008:2084: mthar dmigs med nam mkha' lta bur bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2085: gsum pa mnyen btsal ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:2086: mdun du dbyug pa 'dom phyed tsam zhig btsugs /
NK033(gi)008:2087: bla ma bsgom bstim sngar dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)008:2088: snying ga'i h'u las h'u rang 'dra ba gnyis pa zhig spros /
NK033(gi)008:2089: snying kha nas thogs med du thon /
NK033(gi)008:2090: dbyug pa'i rtse mor 'khod cing gsal brtan 'bar ba la sems bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2091: yang gzhir gnas kyi snying ga'i h'u la tshur bsdu /
NK033(gi)008:2092: yang phar spro ba de 'dra lan kha shas kyis dmigs pa'i gzhi btsal nas /
NK033(gi)008:2093: mdun du shing 'dom gang tsam btsugs pa la snying
NK033(gi)008:2094: kha'i h'u las h'u mang po gcig rjes gcig mthud
NK033(gi)008:2095: breng chags su phreng ba brgyus pa ltar 'phros /
NK033(gi)008:2096: mdun gyi dbyug pa'i rtsa ba nas bzung rim pas g.yas bskor du je mtho je mthor dkris nas /
NK033(gi)008:2097: h'u sngon ma de dbyug pa'i rtse mor yer gyis phyin pa na cung zad de la sems bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2098: yang h'u yig rjes ma spro gzhi la sdud pa
NK033(gi)008:2099: nas brtsams phyi rim g.yon bskor du shig shig 'ong
NK033(gi)008:2100: nas snying kha'i h'u la thim par bsams te dkrol
NK033(gi)008:2101: / yang snga ma bzhin du spro ba sogs bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2102: de'i skabs su ngag tu yang h'u sgra 'bol la ring ba brjod nas h'u gi glu len /
NK033(gi)008:2103: de la goms nas dngos su dbyug pa 'dom do tsam btsugs /
NK033(gi)008:2104: dmigs pas de nyid dpag bsam gyi shing du gyur
NK033(gi)008:2105: pa'i rtse mo srid rtser slebs pa zhig tu bsgoms
NK033(gi)008:2106: nas / yang h'u gi glu len pa dang dmigs
NK033(gi)008:2107: pa'i spro bsdu bshad ma thag pa ltar yang yang
NK033(gi)008:2108: nas / bya / de nas dngos po thams cad
NK033(gi)008:2109: la yang de ltar du sbyangs pas sems gar gtad
NK033(gi)008:2110: du zin pa snyam 'byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2111: dmigs pa snga phyi thams cad la gsal snang thob na 'byongs pa'i tshad yin /
NK033(gi)008:2112: 'di dag gi skabs su h'u gi phreng ba de'i
NK033(gi)008:2113: thog mtha' bar gsum gcig bsgom dus gcig mi gsal
NK033(gi)008:2114: ba lta bu ma yin pa thams cad kyi rnam
NK033(gi)008:2115: pa spyi lam pa gcig car du gsal thebs shing
NK033(gi)008:2116: rtog pa gzhan gyis bar ma chod pa zhig gal
NK033(gi)008:2117: che'o // bzhi pa lam du gzhugs pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2118: bla ma bsgom bstim snga ma bzhin la dmigs pa thun mong ba ltar na /
NK033(gi)008:2119: rang gi snying khar h'u dkar po 'od lnga ldan pa zhig bsam /
NK033(gi)008:2120: h'u snyan la ring ba brjod pas snying ga'i h'u
NK033(gi)008:2121: las h'u gcig rgyang gis chad de srin 'gros lta
NK033(gi)008:2123: thog mar gnas khang gi phyi tsam /
NK033(gi)008:2125: rim gyis ri brag dang yul ljongs sogs brgal nas
NK033(gi)008:2126: 'jig rten gyi khams blos mi 'khyud pa'i pha mthar
NK033(gi)008:2128: 'ga' zhig tu cung zad 'dug par bsam la gsal snang 'don bskyor bya /
NK033(gi)008:2129: res 'ga' dal bus 'gro bar bsam la h'u ring por brjod /
NK033(gi)008:2130: res 'ga' mda' 'phang ba ltar 'gro bar bsam la h'u thung ngur brjod /
NK033(gi)008:2131: yang rim gyis tshur ldog ste mdun nam snying gar gnas par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:2132: h'u brjod dus rlung rig gcig tu dril zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2133: phyi nang gang du 'gro 'ong byed pa de la sems rtse gcig tu gtod pa gal che'o //
NK033(gi)008:2134: 'dir ngal gso ba'ang srin 'gros kyi 'khyog mtshams re dang /
NK033(gi)008:2135: h'u yang skabs der drag la thung ba re re brjod gsung ba'ang yod cing /
NK033(gi)008:2136: khyad par thun mong ma yin pa bla ma'i man
NK033(gi)008:2137: ngag zhal shes kyi dbang du byas na thog ma
NK033(gi)008:2138: nas ngo bo rang gi lus ngag sems gsum rnam
NK033(gi)008:2139: pa h'u dkar po 'od lnga ldan pa zhig tu
NK033(gi)008:2140: bsgom pa de nyid 'khyogs 'gros su song nas shul
NK033(gi)008:2141: du lus dang spro gzhi'i h'u lus rgyu med par
NK033(gi)008:2142: bsgom pa de nyid zhing khams bgrod pa la sogs
NK033(gi)008:2143: pa la snga ma las zab khyad thon pa'i dmigs
NK033(gi)008:2144: pa yin gsungs / de'ang 'jig rten gyi khams mang
NK033(gi)008:2145: po bgrod pa'i mthar shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i
NK033(gi)008:2146: zhing du phyin nas ston pa bcom ldan 'das rgyal
NK033(gi)008:2147: ba mi bskyod pa'i thugs klong bde ba chen po
NK033(gi)008:2148: dang h'u yig dbyer med du 'dres par bsam la
NK033(gi)008:2149: pa yin gsungs / / tshur mi bsdu bar rtog med du mnyam par bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2151: dmyal ba sogs ma dag pa'i gnas rnams su'ang bgrod nas /
NK033(gi)008:2152: h'u yig gang du slebs pa'i gnas de nyid snod
NK033(gi)008:2153: bcud dag pa lha dang gzhal yas khang gi rang
NK033(gi)008:2154: bzhin du lam lam bsgyur nas mthar de kun mi
NK033(gi)008:2155: dmigs pa h'u dang bcas rang yal du bsam nas
NK033(gi)008:2156: stong nyid spros bral mi rtog pa la mnyam par
NK033(gi)008:2157: bzhag / 'di dag thams cad dal bus rkang thang
NK033(gi)008:2158: du bgrod pa lta bur byas nas sems sbyong ba
NK033(gi)008:2159: las yud kyis bgrod cing phyin pa bya rgyu min
NK033(gi)008:2160: bzhag / / h'u gang du slebs pa der rang
NK033(gi)008:2161: nyid dngos su slebs pa lta bur bsgoms pas mthar
NK033(gi)008:2162: dngos su song ba dang khyad med pa'i gsal snang
NK033(gi)008:2163: bzhag / / thob pa dang / rmi lam 'dzin spel sbyang ba sogs la'ang tshegs med cing /
NK033(gi)008:2164: de dag la brten nas zhing khams bgrod pa la sogs pa'ang 'byung gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:2165: de ltar ngag gi sngon 'gro la 'bad pas gnas skabs su ngag gi mngon zhen bzlog /
NK033(gi)008:2169: ngag 'khor bar mi 'jug longs skur grol /
NK033(gi)008:2170: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung rdo rje thob par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:2171: gsum pa sems kyi sngon 'gro la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:2176: sems ni dang po byung sa dang //
NK033(gi)008:2177: bar du gnas dang tha mar 'gro //
NK033(gi)008:2178: de ltar gsum la brtag dpyad pas //
NK033(gi)008:2179: sems sbyang sems kyi gnas lugs shes //
NK033(gi)008:2181: dang po byung sa dang 'byung mkhan la brtag pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2182: mdun du bla ma sngar ltar bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:2183: lus gnad rnam snang chos bdun spyi 'gre bcas nas gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)008:2184: bla ma rang la bstims te sems dang dbyer med du bsres /
NK033(gi)008:2185: rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang babs su ci gnas kyi yun la mnyam par bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2186: de nas kha nang du phyogs te rang gi lus ngag yid gsum gtso gang che /
NK033(gi)008:2187: 'khor bar skyur mkhan dang myang 'das thob mkhan 'di
NK033(gi)008:2188: lus ngag yid gsum gang yin brtags shing dpyad pas
NK033(gi)008:2189: / sems gtso bor gtan la phebs pa na /
NK033(gi)008:2190: rang gi sems mi 'char dgu 'char sna tshogs su 'phro ba 'di phyi 'byung ba'i dngos po /
NK033(gi)008:2192: snang ba stong pa pha ma'i rkyen sogs dang po gang las byung /
NK033(gi)008:2194: ji lta bu zhig las byung /
NK033(gi)008:2199: de ltar dpyad pas byung sa byung mkhan med par shes nas shar ba 'dra yang /
NK033(gi)008:2200: shar dus nas ma grub pa de ni thog mar
NK033(gi)008:2201: skye ba med pa gdod ma'i gshis chos sku'i bzhugs
NK033(gi)008:2202: tshul yin pas rang ngo 'phrod pa'i dgos pa yod
NK033(gi)008:2203: do // gnyis pa bar du gnas pa la brtag pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2204: sems 'di 'dra zhig nas byung snyam pa'am /
NK033(gi)008:2205: rnam rtog thol gyis shar ba'i dus su de ltar
NK033(gi)008:2206: shar ba'i sems de nyid phyi snang ba la gnas
NK033(gi)008:2207: sam / nang phung po la gnas /
NK033(gi)008:2208: gnas mkhan gyi shes pa de nyid dngos po dngos
NK033(gi)008:2209: med dbyibs kha dog la sogs pa ji ltar 'dug
NK033(gi)008:2210: brtag pas cir yang ma grub par gsal stong nam
NK033(gi)008:2211: mkha' lta bu'i dgongs pa shar ba ni bar du
NK033(gi)008:2212: gnas pa med par ngo 'phrod pa ste mthar thug
NK033(gi)008:2213: longs sku 'grub pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:2214: gsum pa tha mar 'gro sa la brtag pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2215: rnam rtog wal gyis shar nas yal gyis song snyam byed pa 'di gang du 'gro /
NK033(gi)008:2217: rnal rtog yal nas song snyam na gang du yal
NK033(gi)008:2218: bltas pas 'gro ba ltar snang yang song ba med
NK033(gi)008:2219: pa / 'gags pa ltar snang yang 'gags pa med
NK033(gi)008:2220: par shes pa ni rig stong rjes med rang ngo
NK033(gi)008:2221: pa / 'phrod pa ste / mthar thug 'bras bu sprul sku dang mjal ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:2222: gzhan yang sems 'di dngos po dang dngos med gang yin /
NK033(gi)008:2223: dngos po'i snyam na dbyibs dang kha dog che chung byed las ngo bo gang gis mtshon /
NK033(gi)008:2224: rtog byed kyi shes pa la tshur blta /
NK033(gi)008:2225: blta bya'i shes pa la phar blta /
NK033(gi)008:2226: de gnyis kyang gcig yin nam so so yin sogs
NK033(gi)008:2227: rig pa rkyang ded kyis skad cig kyang ma yengs
NK033(gi)008:2228: par blta / de ltar phu 'ded mda' 'ded du
NK033(gi)008:2229: brtags shing btsal ba'i ngang nas rgan po nyi ma
NK033(gi)008:2230: par blta / 'de ba'am / bya ba zin pa'i skyes bu ltar lhod kyis klod la bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2231: yang rnam rtog thol thol 'phro na de bya shor
NK033(gi)008:2232: du ma song bar dran pas tshir gyis bzung nas
NK033(gi)008:2233: rnam rtog de ga gang las skyes blta /
NK033(gi)008:2234: de sems las skyes snyam na sems de ga gang las byung /
NK033(gi)008:2238: de'i dmigs e rnyed skad cig kyang ma yengs par
NK033(gi)008:2239: bltas pas cir yang ma mthong ba'i ngang du lhod
NK033(gi)008:2240: de bzhag go // yang rnam rtog wal gyis shar
NK033(gi)008:2241: na sngar ltar sems kyi phu thag ma chod kyi
NK033(gi)008:2242: de bzhag go // bar du blta / de ltar
NK033(gi)008:2243: brtags shing dpyad pas ci yang ma rnyed pa'i ngang
NK033(gi)008:2244: der ngos bzung la dpyad ra med par gtan la
NK033(gi)008:2245: ma phebs kyi bar du bskyar ro //
NK033(gi)008:2246: de ltar 'bad pas gnas skabs su sems kyi mngon zhen bzlog /
NK033(gi)008:2249: mthar thug mchog gi dgos pa sems 'khor bar mi 'jug chos sku nyag gcig tu grol /
NK033(gi)008:2250: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rdo rje dang gnyis su med par 'gyur pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:2252: bsam du rdugs par gzhug pa 'di nyid kyis //
NK033(gi)008:2253: dran pa rnams ni zad pa'i sar bskyal lo //
NK033(gi)008:2256: khregs chod ye bab sor bzhag gi don khrid ltar
NK033(gi)008:2257: sngon 'gro sems kyi khang bu bshigs pa'i gdams ngag
NK033(gi)008:2258: / skye 'gags gnas gsum la brtags pas sems nyid brjod du med pa'i ngo bo mthong /
NK033(gi)008:2259: gcig tha dad la brtags pas sems kyi gnas lugs rtogs /
NK033(gi)008:2260: rang ngo gcer mthong la brtags pas sems las 'das
NK033(gi)008:2261: pa'i ye shes ngos bzung ba rnams rgyas par grub
NK033(gi)008:2263: gnyis pa sems rnal du dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2264: mdun gyi nam mkhar stong gzugs kyi thig le sngo
NK033(gi)008:2265: dwangs kyi dkyil du drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma
NK033(gi)008:2266: sku mi g.yo / spyan zim bu /
NK033(gi)008:2268: thugs spros med kyi rnam par bzhugs pa gsal btab pa'i thugs kar a dkar po gcig bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:2269: gsol ba btab nas rang la bstim /
NK033(gi)008:2270: de nas lus sog phon gyi thag pa klod pa ltar bde lugs su bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2271: ngag pi wam gi rgyun thag bcad pa bzhin ma bcos par 'jog /
NK033(gi)008:2272: yid rang 'thag gi ltag chu bcad pa bzhin rtog
NK033(gi)008:2273: dpyod kyis 'tshol 'phro mi bya bar rang babs su
NK033(gi)008:2274: 'jog go // de ltar bzhag pas dge sdig dgag
NK033(gi)008:2275: sgrub sogs shes pa'i spros pa nye bar zhi ba
NK033(gi)008:2276: lan tsh+wa chur thim pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)008:2277: gsal stong lhan cig skyes pa gdod ma'i ngang du ma bcos par 'jog ste /
NK033(gi)008:2278: de yang blo la yul snang ngam yul la blo
NK033(gi)008:2279: gang snang yang phar gang snang ba ma 'gags la
NK033(gi)008:2280: / tshur gang snang la der 'dzin blo'i dri ma dang bral ba /
NK033(gi)008:2281: snang sems dbyer med yul dang yul can 'di zhes
NK033(gi)008:2282: ngo bo ngos bzung thams cad dang bral ba'i rig
NK033(gi)008:2283: pa gsal hrig rjen ne ba'i ngang du 'jog /
NK033(gi)008:2284: des sngar sems tshol sogs dmigs pa gzhur po byas
NK033(gi)008:2285: pas thang chad pa lta bu de 'dir ngal sos
NK033(gi)008:2286: pa'i tshul gyis ting nge 'dzin skye ba'i dgos pa
NK033(gi)008:2287: yod / de'i ngang nas lus bsgul bskyod 'dod pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2288: sems la rtog pa 'gyu na de'i ngo bo la gcer gyis bltas nas lhod kyis glod /
NK033(gi)008:2289: ngag brjod 'dod byung na dmigs med kyi ngang nas a a a zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)008:2290: 'di'i skabs su 'phro rgod kyi gegs byung na /
NK033(gi)008:2291: rang gi lus sems thams cad rdo rje pha lam
NK033(gi)008:2292: gyi rang bzhin pha bong gru bzhi par bsgoms nas
NK033(gi)008:2293: mnyam par bzhag / byings na lus sems a dkar por bsgoms nas der 'dzin /
NK033(gi)008:2294: rmug na lus hril po'am yang na lus nang snying
NK033(gi)008:2295: thad du mar me 'od gsal ba zhig ta ler
NK033(gi)008:2296: 'bar ba la sems gtad pa ste gegs sel bog
NK033(gi)008:2298: rjes thob kyi gnas skabs su'ang gang shar dgag sgrub
NK033(gi)008:2299: blang dor sogs re dogs med par bskyangs pas gang
NK033(gi)008:2300: snang sgom gyi grogs su 'char bar 'gyur zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2301: rtog pa nan gyis bkag na mi gnas pa'i khar gegs su 'gro la /
NK033(gi)008:2302: yid shes tshogs drug gi yul snang der 'dzin med
NK033(gi)008:2303: cing gnyen pos ma bslad par skyong ba nyid gal
NK033(gi)008:2304: che / ka dag gi ngang du bzhag dus su
NK033(gi)008:2305: 'char 'char 'dra yang don la shar ba med pas
NK033(gi)008:2306: rig pa zang thal rjen par ngos bzung la ka
NK033(gi)008:2307: dag rig stong spros bral gyi ngang du la zlo
NK033(gi)008:2308: che / bar bya'o // gsum pa gza' gtad med pa lta ba'i man ngag bstan pa la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:2309: don nyams su blang ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2310: ngo gcer phog tu sprad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2315: khregs chod kyi rgyab yig nam mkha' dri med dang /
NK033(gi)008:2316: rtog med nam mkha' sprin phung sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2318: bla ma'i rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro bas sprul pa
NK033(gi)008:2319: sku'i 'das rjes tshig gsum gnad du rdeg pa'i sgo
NK033(gi)008:2320: nas rang gi rig pa chos sku dri ma med
NK033(gi)008:2321: par rtogs par byed pa la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:2322: ngo rang thog tu sprad pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2323: da ltar gyi shes pa bcos bslad gnyen po dang bral ba /
NK033(gi)008:2324: ngo bo ngos gzung las 'das pa /
NK033(gi)008:2325: rig pa mtshan mar ma grub par /
NK033(gi)008:2326: stong gsal rang byung gi ye shes dran bsam blo
NK033(gi)008:2327: 'das chen po wa le sang nge phyam mer gnas
NK033(gi)008:2328: pa 'di nyid rang byung gi ye shes chos sku
NK033(gi)008:2329: ka dag gi dgongs par ngo shes par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2330: thag gcig thog tu bcad pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2331: chos sku blo 'das kyi dgongs pa bzhi cha gsum
NK033(gi)008:2332: bral gyi ngang la mi g.yo bar gnas pa ste
NK033(gi)008:2335: da ltar gyi shes pa gang du'ang bcos bslad bral
NK033(gi)008:2336: ba'i ngang la rig pa'i gdangs ma 'gags par chu
NK033(gi)008:2337: rnyogs ma dwangs pa dang 'dra ba'i ngang la ched
NK033(gi)008:2339: yengs pa phyal bar ma shor bar /
NK033(gi)008:2340: tha mal gyi rig pa sor bzhag gcig pu rig
NK033(gi)008:2341: ge sang nge ye re wa la ler bzhag par
NK033(gi)008:2342: bya'o // gding grol thog tu bca' ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:2343: de lta ngang dwangs spros pa dang bral ba rgya mtsho dwangs pa lta bu'i ngang la bzhag dus /
NK033(gi)008:2344: tha mal gyi shes pa yul thog tu 'phro yang
NK033(gi)008:2345: rang shar rang grol du bstan pa rba rlabs chur
NK033(gi)008:2347: shar dus yengs med bcos bslad med pa'i ngang du glod pas /
NK033(gi)008:2348: dran rtog rjes med du yal nas byung tshor gzhi
NK033(gi)008:2349: thim la song ba ni rang grol zhes bya ste
NK033(gi)008:2350: / rang shar ris med 'dzin rtsol spang blang gnyen po med par gdengs 'chos pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2351: gnyis pa ngo gcer thog tu sprad pa la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:2352: byin rlabs 'pho ba'i stobs kyis ngo sprad pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2353: nyams myong sgom pa'i thog tu ngo sprod pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2355: dben pa'i gnas su tshogs gtor rgya cher bsham zhing
NK033(gi)008:2356: slob ma rnams kyis man+dala dbul la lus gnad drang
NK033(gi)008:2357: por bsrang / ngo sprod 'debs pa po bsgom gzhir
NK033(gi)008:2358: byas nas sngar bla ma'i rnal 'byor du bshad pa'i
NK033(gi)008:2359: dmigs pa phog la de yang skyon kun zad /
NK033(gi)008:2362: skyabs gnas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor nges shes khyad
NK033(gi)008:2363: par can bskyed nas ci mdzad khyer shes kyis blo
NK033(gi)008:2365: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma dam pa rnams kyis tshad
NK033(gi)008:2366: med pa'i thugs rjes dgongs nas bdag gi rgyud byin
NK033(gi)008:2368: zab lam gyi rtogs pa khyad par can dus da
NK033(gi)008:2369: lta nyid du skye bar byin gyis rlobs shig snyam
NK033(gi)008:2370: du mos gus gdung shugs drag po mchi ma 'khrugs
NK033(gi)008:2371: pa tsam du skyed cig byas la /
NK033(gi)008:2372: spos dang gu gul sreg cig bla mas d+aa dril 'khrol ba dang bcas nas /
NK033(gi)008:2373: chos sku kun tu bzang po la gsol ba 'debs so //
NK033(gi)008:2374: zab lam gyi nyams rtogs rgyud la skye bar byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK033(gi)008:2375: ces sogs brgyud pa'i gshar 'debs kyi byin phab barjesa
NK033(gi)008:2376: bla ma nyid tshad med pa'i thugs rjes 'od du
NK033(gi)008:2377: zhu / slob ma'i spyi bo nas thim pas slob
NK033(gi)008:2378: ma'i sgo gsum dang bla ma'i rdo rje gsum dbyer
NK033(gi)008:2379: med spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang la shes pa
NK033(gi)008:2380: klod la 'jog tu bcug pas byin rlabs 'ur langs
NK033(gi)008:2381: zhu / / sgo gsum gyi snang ba bla mar 'dres /
NK033(gi)008:2382: rnam rtog mos gus su lhang nger shar /
NK033(gi)008:2383: gshis 'dzin med du khro ler grol /
NK033(gi)008:2384: de'i ngang la bzo med du lhod kyis glod la
NK033(gi)008:2385: bzhag pas rang rig ka dag chos sku'i dbyings su
NK033(gi)008:2386: grol ba zhes bya ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2387: 'di ni rtsa ba'i dngos bstan la med kyang nyams
NK033(gi)008:2388: myong bogs chod du skye ba'i phyir gter chen rin
NK033(gi)008:2389: po che'i phyag bzhes su mdzad pa byin rlabs shin
NK033(gi)008:2390: tu che ba yin no gsungs so //
NK033(gi)008:2394: zung 'jug gi dgongs pa ngo sprod pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2395: dang po don skye med du rtsad bcad nas gnas
NK033(gi)008:2396: thog tu gzhi bcings grol med pa'i gnas lugs chos
NK033(gi)008:2397: zad ka dag gidagongasa par ngo sprad pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2398: slob ma rnams sngar ltar lus gnad chos bdun bca' /
NK033(gi)008:2399: ngag gnad rlung rang babs su bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2400: sems gnad rtog pa snga ma 'gags /
NK033(gi)008:2402: da lta'i rig pa bzhi cha gsum bral gshis gang du yang ma grub cing /
NK033(gi)008:2403: mdangs bde chen du ma 'gags la /
NK033(gi)008:2404: rtsal sna tshogs su snang yang ngo bo smra bsam
NK033(gi)008:2405: brjod med blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i rig pa
NK033(gi)008:2409: sang nge ba 'di rang byung gi ye shes chos
NK033(gi)008:2410: sku blo 'das chen po'i dgongs pa yin pas de
NK033(gi)008:2411: bcar phog tu ngos bzung la /
NK033(gi)008:2412: mtha' bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang du dar cig mnyam par zhog cig /
NK033(gi)008:2414: de ltar bzhag pas rnam rtog gi spros pa nye
NK033(gi)008:2415: bar zhi nas bya byed dran rtog thams cad bde
NK033(gi)008:2416: gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rol
NK033(gi)008:2417: par 'char te mnyam rjes kyi ris med /
NK033(gi)008:2421: bsgom bya sgom byed thams cad las 'das pa'i gnas
NK033(gi)008:2422: lugs chos zad ka dag gi dgongs par la bzla
NK033(gi)008:2423: ba'o // de ltar yang gsang ba sgra rgyud las /
NK033(gi)008:2424: snga phyi dran rtog med pa yi //
NK033(gi)008:2425: rig ge seng nge gsal le ba //
NK033(gi)008:2426: da lta'i shes pa 'di nyid la //
NK033(gi)008:2427: chos sku bzhi ldan ngos bzung ngo //
NK033(gi)008:2429: de'i tshe sems spros bral du gsan pa chos sku /
NK033(gi)008:2430: gsal la der 'dzin med pa longs sku /
NK033(gi)008:2431: sna tshogs snang ba'i 'char gzhir ma 'gag pa sprul sku ste /
NK033(gi)008:2432: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dbyer med pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2434: rdzogs sangs rgyas ni rang rig nyid //
NK033(gi)008:2435: ngo bo dus gsum 'gyur ba med //
NK033(gi)008:2436: rang bzhin rtag tu 'gag pa med //
NK033(gi)008:2437: thugs rje kun la rang snang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:2439: 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i phyag bzhes ni //
NK033(gi)008:2441: ka ba lta bu'i dngos po gsum mam 'das ma
NK033(gi)008:2442: 'ongs da lta ste dus gsum lta bu gang yang
NK033(gi)008:2443: rung ba'i dngos po gsum la dus gcig car skad
NK033(gi)008:2444: cig ma gcig gi steng nas rnam spyi lam pa
NK033(gi)008:2446: bye brag phra mo la'ang dus gcig tu sems bsgrims
NK033(gi)008:2447: nas gtad pas 'char tshul khyad par bzhig yod pa
NK033(gi)008:2448: yin / de la brten nas bla mas ngo sprod mdzad pa ni bzhi cha gsum bral te /
NK033(gi)008:2450: bzhi mtshon dngos gzhi rnams dang bral //
NK033(gi)008:2451: ces gsungs pa'i dgongs don no //
NK033(gi)008:2452: gnyis pa rtsal snang 'gag med du gtan la phab
NK033(gi)008:2453: nas 'gyu thog tu spang gnyen med pa rang grol
NK033(gi)008:2455: sems nyid bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ngang las ma
NK033(gi)008:2456: 'gags pa'i rtsal snang dran rig 'phro 'du gang shar
NK033(gi)008:2457: de ka phyi'i snang ba ma 'gags la /
NK033(gi)008:2458: nang 'dzin zhen gyi gnyen pos ma bcings pa'i steng du snga phyi bsu skyel dang /
NK033(gi)008:2459: spang blang dgag sgrub sogs gang gis kyang bcos bslad
NK033(gi)008:2460: med pa'i rig pa gcer bu har sang rjen pa
NK033(gi)008:2461: / gsal rig de ka'i ngang mdangs rang babs su
NK033(gi)008:2462: bskyangs pas rgya mtshor rlabs ji ltar shar yang brgya
NK033(gi)008:2463: mtsho'i chu nyid las ma 'das pa ltar gang shar
NK033(gi)008:2464: gyi rtog pa thams cad ma spangs ma bsgyur bar
NK033(gi)008:2465: chos nyid kyi rol pa las mi 'da' zhing mi
NK033(gi)008:2466: / 'gyur ba'i phyir / de yang phyi sna tshogs
NK033(gi)008:2467: su 'phro yang snang bas sems mi g.yo ba sgyu
NK033(gi)008:2468: ma'i skyes bu ltar chags zhen gyi rtsis gdab med
NK033(gi)008:2470: nang sna tshogs su snang yang zhen 'dzin med pa
NK033(gi)008:2471: bu chung gi shes pa ltar 'di zhes ngos bzung
NK033(gi)008:2472: med par gnas pas byung tshor gyi rtog pa thams
NK033(gi)008:2473: cad lan tsh+wa chur thim pa ltar rang zhi rang
NK033(gi)008:2474: sangs la song bas cir snang rang grol zhes bya
NK033(gi)008:2476: ji ltar shar ba'i rig pa ni //
NK033(gi)008:2477: sbrul mdud bzhin du rang grol lo //
NK033(gi)008:2478: gnyen po med phyir 'bad rtsol zhig /
NK033(gi)008:2479: ngo bo nyid kyis ye grol lo //
NK033(gi)008:2481: gsum pa gnas 'gyu ngo bo dbyer med du thag
NK033(gi)008:2482: bcad nas zung 'jug tu gang shar rig pa rjen
NK033(gi)008:2484: sgo gsum rang bzhin lhug par gnas pa'i ngang las
NK033(gi)008:2485: rtsal snang ma 'gags pa'i rnam rtog ji snyed cig
NK033(gi)008:2486: 'char yang dgag sgrub blang dor med par rang babs
NK033(gi)008:2487: su bzhag pas chos nyid kyi ngang du mi g.yo
NK033(gi)008:2488: bar gnas zhing gnas pa'i rang rtsal 'gag pa med
NK033(gi)008:2490: de ltar gnas pa dang 'phro ba'i rang bzhin gnyis su med cing dbyer med pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:2491: de yang gnas 'gyu ngo bo ltos bzhag can ma
NK033(gi)008:2492: yin pa'i gnad kyis tshogs drug gi snang ba gang
NK033(gi)008:2493: gi yang phyogs su ma lhungs par rig pa rjen
NK033(gi)008:2494: par bzhag pas / rnam rtog che phra thams cad thol skyes thol nub 'khyags rom chur zhu ba'am /
NK033(gi)008:2495: na bun nam mkhar yal ba ltar chos nyid kyi
NK033(gi)008:2496: rol pa las mi 'da' zhing mi g.yo bar shes
NK033(gi)008:2497: par bya'o // de ltar yang rmad byung las /
NK033(gi)008:2498: ji ltar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs bzhin //
NK033(gi)008:2499: sems kyi rba rlabs g.yo ba kun //
NK033(gi)008:2500: gdod ma gzhi yi rgya mtshor thim //
NK033(gi)008:2502: de ltar sems gnas na gdod ma'i ngang du gnas /
NK033(gi)008:2503: 'phro na ye shes kyi rol par shar /
NK033(gi)008:2504: mnyam na gnyis med kyi ngang du yan pas ji
NK033(gi)008:2505: ltar shar yang chos nyid kyi ngang mdangs las ma
NK033(gi)008:2510: ji ltar shar yang rang gi rig pa'i cho 'phrul las ma 'das te /
NK033(gi)008:2512: dri med dag pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK033(gi)008:2513: rang rig chos sku 'gyur ba med //
NK033(gi)008:2514: sal le sang nge wal le ba //
NK033(gi)008:2515: sprin med ston ka'i nam mkha' bzhin //
NK033(gi)008:2516: mi 'gyur brtan pa ri bo bzhin du zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2517: mi g.yo dwangs pa rgya mtsho bzhin du zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2518: yangs dog bral ba nam mkha' bzhin du zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2519: gang ltar gnas kyang rig pa'i ngang yin zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2520: 'phro gnas rang rig dwangs sangs phyed par zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2521: ji ltar bya rnams nam mkhar 'phur ba yang //
NK033(gi)008:2522: mkha' las ma 'das de bzhin rig pa'i ngang //
NK033(gi)008:2523: chos rnams rang gsal g.yo ba med par zhog /
NK033(gi)008:2524: ces gsungs pa ltar bzo bcos med par rang babs
NK033(gi)008:2525: su klod pas dgag sgrub blang dor re dogs med
NK033(gi)008:2526: pa'i zhi chal pa zhig 'char te /
NK033(gi)008:2527: de ni rig pa rang gnas kyi bsam gtan yin par shes par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)008:2528: 'di ngos zin pa na shes pa gnas 'gyu dgag
NK033(gi)008:2529: sgrub bzang rtog ngan rtog gi dus thams cad du
NK033(gi)008:2530: rang rig rang gsal rang babs la ce re bltas
NK033(gi)008:2531: pas 'dzin med rang gnas kyis bsam gtan rjen sang
NK033(gi)008:2532: gis 'char te / de rtsol med chu bo'i rgyun
NK033(gi)008:2533: bzhin du 'jug pa'i dran 'dun gyis bskyang ba ste
NK033(gi)008:2534: gis 'char te / / de dag gis ni /
NK033(gi)008:2535: ji ltar snang zhing myong ba'i chos thams cad dgag
NK033(gi)008:2536: sgrub blang dor re dogs mtshan 'dzin las 'das par
NK033(gi)008:2537: ngo sprod pa'o // yang na ngo sprod phyi ma
NK033(gi)008:2538: 'di dag gi tshab tu khregs chod ye babs sor
NK033(gi)008:2541: dran rig 'char nub med par ngo sprod pa'i tshul gnyis gdab na'ang ches legs so //
NK033(gi)008:2542: de'ang skal ba dang ldan pa'i gang zag gis don
NK033(gi)008:2543: nyams su blangs pa'i rgyud thog tu bla mas ngo
NK033(gi)008:2544: sprad thebs par btab pas gnas lugs zab mo'i don
NK033(gi)008:2545: la sgro 'dogs chod cing de'i rgyun ma nyams par
NK033(gi)008:2546: bskyangs pas brtan pa myur du thob par 'gyur zhing
NK033(gi)008:2547: / bsgom don la myong ba ma skyes shing go
NK033(gi)008:2548: yul du song ba rnams la ngo sprod btab kyang
NK033(gi)008:2550: slar yang dmigs rim rnams la myong ba thon thon gyi bar 'bad nas sgom zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2551: nyams rtogs skyes rim dang bstun nas ngo sprod btab
NK033(gi)008:2552: pas rim gyis nyams myong gi sne zin par 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:2553: ro // bzhi pa spang thob med pa 'bras bu'i man ngag ni /
NK033(gi)008:2554: de la 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni rig stong chos sku ste /
NK033(gi)008:2555: ye grol du 'dug pas da gdod bskyar nas grol rgyu med par yid ches /
NK033(gi)008:2556: rang grol du 'dug pas gnyen po gzhan la rag ma lus par thag chod /
NK033(gi)008:2557: yang grol du 'dug pas grol thog nyid las spang blang mi dgos par gding 'chos te /
NK033(gi)008:2558: sor bzhag rig stong rjes med kyi ngang la ye yin rdzogs pa chen por thag bcad nas /
NK033(gi)008:2559: bzo med re dogs dang bral bar rang bzhag pas /
NK033(gi)008:2560: blo bde chos nyid du grol ba gzhi gdod ma'i gnas lugs la /
NK033(gi)008:2561: da ltar gyi rig pa rang gnas chen por ngo 'phrod nas /
NK033(gi)008:2562: rtsol sgrub bcos bslad med par tha mal gyin 'dar glod pas /
NK033(gi)008:2563: chos sku rang gnas chen por la zlo ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:2564: gnyug ma lhun grub chen po'i 'bras bu'o //
NK033(gi)008:2565: mdor na rang sems sangs rgyas su thag bcad nas /
NK033(gi)008:2566: re dogs bcos bslad dang bral ba rang rig ste /
NK033(gi)008:2567: bya byed rtsol sgrub zhig pa'i shes pa sor bzhag
NK033(gi)008:2568: ye grol chen por khong lhod pa ni gshis rdzogs
NK033(gi)008:2569: pa chen po'i gnas lugs te /
NK033(gi)008:2570: byar med chu bo'i rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la bslab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2571: 'dir gsung rgyun snga mar spyod pa dang 'bras bu gnyis spyi'i tshul tsam bshad kyang /
NK033(gi)008:2572: lta sgom gnyis rang gnad thun min du song bas
NK033(gi)008:2573: 'dir spyod 'bras gnyis kyang yang gsang gnad kyi nges
NK033(gi)008:2574: pa dang sbyar ba khregs chod kyi rgyab yig dang
NK033(gi)008:2575: / rtog med nam mkha' sprin phung las byung ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2576: de rnams kyis sems gtan la dbab pa'i man ngag
NK033(gi)008:2577: khregs chod spros pa kun zhi'i khrid rim dngos gzhi
NK033(gi)008:2578: bshad zin to // gnyis pa rig pa gtan la
NK033(gi)008:2579: dbab pa'i man ngag lam thod rgal gyi khrid bstan
NK033(gi)008:2580: bshad zin to // pa la bzhi / sngon 'gro lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnad sbyong ba /
NK033(gi)008:2581: gnad lnga la brten nas mngon sum rang thog tu dbab pa /
NK033(gi)008:2582: nyams su blangs pas snang ba bzhi'i 'char tshul bstan pa /
NK033(gi)008:2583: mtha' rten gyi man ngag bshad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2586: sgo gsum gyi bya ba dgu phrugs su btang ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:2588: thog mar spyod pa brtsams pa la bar chad mi 'jug pa'i phyir du bsrung ba bya ste /
NK033(gi)008:2589: grub na tshogs gtor bshams la tshogs mchod yid bzhin rgya mtsho ltar 'bul /
NK033(gi)008:2590: bla ma la gser gyi man+dala phul la slob ma
NK033(gi)008:2591: rnams rig pa sgrib g.yogs med pa mtshon pa'i phyir
NK033(gi)008:2592: lus gcer bu'am / ma bde na stod g.yogs tsam phud la /
NK033(gi)008:2593: bla ma zhal shar du phyogs la bzhengs pa'i mdun
NK033(gi)008:2594: du long bu gshibs la langs te thal mo snying
NK033(gi)008:2595: gar sbyar / mig bla ma'i thugs kar gtad /
NK033(gi)008:2596: mngon du spyod pa la bar chad kyi bgegs mi 'jug pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2597: rnam shes tshogs brgyad yul du mi 'phro bar bya ba'i don du /
NK033(gi)008:2598: bla ma sku sngo nag rab tu 'jigs shing skra
NK033(gi)008:2599: bardzesa pa mche ba gtsigs shing ljags 'gyur ba zhig
NK033(gi)008:2601: bla mas phyag g.yon rked par brten /
NK033(gi)008:2602: g.yas pas sdigs mdzub thog mar shar nas brtsams phyogs
NK033(gi)008:2603: kun tu gtod cing lta stangs dang bcas pas bgegs
NK033(gi)008:2604: bskrad / bla ma'i thugs ka nas slob ma'i spyi
NK033(gi)008:2605: bor h'u sngon po 'phros d+r+wa ba can gyi rtsa
NK033(gi)008:2606: bskrad / las brgyud / lus h'u mthing gar gyur
NK033(gi)008:2607: par sgom du bcug la dpon slob thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)008:2609: des 'gres te thog mar bla ma'i gnas so sor yi ge gsal /
NK033(gi)008:2610: de las 'phros te slob ma'i gnas rnams su thim par mos te /
NK033(gi)008:2611: rkang mthil g.yon du yam ljang gu /
NK033(gi)008:2616: pus mo g.yas la ha dkar po /
NK033(gi)008:2617: rkang mthil g.yas su phata sngo nag ste yi ge brgyad re re bzhin spros la /
NK033(gi)008:2618: ngag tu'ang yi ge re re nas dbugs thengs re la nyer gcig re brjod la bsrung ba bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2619: karma snying thig lugs su 'dir srung ba'i don du phata nyer gcig mnyam du brjod /
NK033(gi)008:2620: rig 'dzin chen po'i phyag srol du /
NK033(gi)008:2622: bla ma'i thugs ka'i h'u las h'u spros /
NK033(gi)008:2623: slob ma'i snying gar zhugs h'u gis lus gang bar
NK033(gi)008:2624: bsam la dpon slob mnyam du ha ngar dang ldan
NK033(gi)008:2625: pa gsum brjod par mdzad do //
NK033(gi)008:2626: 'dir spros pa bsdu na tshogs ma grub kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK033(gi)008:2627: de ltar yi ge brgyad kyis srung ba byas nas /
NK033(gi)008:2628: ru shan dbye ba dngos ni /
NK033(gi)008:2631: khams gsum lus ngag yid kyi yang //
NK033(gi)008:2634: zhes gsungs pas sems can rnams kyi lus ngag yid
NK033(gi)008:2635: gsum gyi chos nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK033(gi)008:2636: par dag kyang / gnas skabs 'khrul pa'i zhen snang
NK033(gi)008:2637: gis bsgribs pas thog ma med pa nas da lta
NK033(gi)008:2638: yan chad rigs drug gi gnas su bar med du
NK033(gi)008:2639: par dag kyang / 'khor zhing / rigs drug so so'i rnam 'gyur /
NK033(gi)008:2641: sems kyi rtog dpyod sdug bsngal gyi myong tshul grangs
NK033(gi)008:2642: kyis mi chod pa zhig myong yang don med kho
NK033(gi)008:2644: da dung zin med kyi las la chags pas ci zhig bya /
NK033(gi)008:2645: des na da res lus ngag yid gsum 'khor 'das
NK033(gi)008:2646: ru shan phyed par byas te phyin chad 'khor bar
NK033(gi)008:2647: skye ba'i gzhi rtsa chod pa zhig bya dgos la
NK033(gi)008:2648: / ji ltar dbye na 'khor ba'i las snang dang
NK033(gi)008:2649: mthun par lam du byas pas las ngan gyi mtshang
NK033(gi)008:2650: rtogs nas phyin chad zhen 'dzin las grol bar 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:2651: / ba'i phyir te / gsang sngags thun mong pa las kyang /
NK033(gi)008:2652: rnam rtog las ni rnam rtog dang //
NK033(gi)008:2653: srid pa nyid kyis srid pa dag /
NK033(gi)008:2654: ji ltar rna bar chu zhugs pa //
NK033(gi)008:2655: chu gzhan gyis ni dgug par bya //
NK033(gi)008:2656: de bzhin dngos po'i rnam rtog kyang //
NK033(gi)008:2657: rnam rtog nyid kyis sbyang bar bya //
NK033(gi)008:2659: de yang dur khrod dam lung stong sogs dben pa'i gnas su song ste /
NK033(gi)008:2660: mkha' 'gro dang gzhi bdag la gtor ma byin nas
NK033(gi)008:2661: 'khor 'das ru shan dbye bar byed pa la bar
NK033(gi)008:2662: chad mi byed pa'i bka' bsgo /
NK033(gi)008:2663: da ni sems can gyi don du 'khor 'das ru
NK033(gi)008:2664: shan phye ste phyin chad 'khor bar mi ldog par
NK033(gi)008:2665: bya'o snyam du sems bskyed nas dmyal ba tsha grang
NK033(gi)008:2670: lha 'pho ltung sogs rigs drug gi spyod tshul bde sdug sogs lus kyi so so'i rnam 'gyur /
NK033(gi)008:2671: ngag gis de dag gi sgra skad sna tshogs /
NK033(gi)008:2672: sems kyis de re re'i sdug bsngal rang rgyud la myong bar bsam la /
NK033(gi)008:2675: sems 'gyu ba spun thag chad par ma gyur gyi bar du 'bad par bya /
NK033(gi)008:2676: de dag gi skabs su bla ma khro bo'i rnam
NK033(gi)008:2677: pas kyang sgo gsum gyi spyod pa rang dang mnyam
NK033(gi)008:2678: du mdzad par mos gsungs pa'ang yod /
NK033(gi)008:2679: de dag gis sun pa dang lus gnad drang por bsrang /
NK033(gi)008:2680: ngag rlung rang babs su bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:2681: sems de ltar myong byed kyi ngo bo la cher re bltas la 'jog cing ngal gso /
NK033(gi)008:2682: yang lus kyis bde bar gshegs pa zhi khro'i sku'i rnam 'gyur /
NK033(gi)008:2683: ngag gis de dag gi snying po sgra skad /
NK033(gi)008:2684: yid kyis de dag gi rnam pa lam me ba la sems gtad /
NK033(gi)008:2685: skabs skabs su a a zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)008:2686: rjes shes kyi rang ngo bskyang /
NK033(gi)008:2688: lus sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs stangs /
NK033(gi)008:2690: sems rtog med du mnyam par bzhag pa la 'jog go //
NK033(gi)008:2691: de ltar byas pas lus la tsha grang bkres skom la chags sdang dang dgag sgrub med pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2692: ngag bla ma'i gdams ngag la yid ches shing go ba rang brdol du shar ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2693: sems gsal stong 'gag med rang byung gi ye shes
NK033(gi)008:2694: rtsol med du 'char ba ma byung gi bar du
NK033(gi)008:2695: bskyar ba shin tu nas gal che bar gsungs la
NK033(gi)008:2696: / de dag gi dgos pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2697: thun mong du lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig pa 'dag cing bar chad zhi /
NK033(gi)008:2699: mthar thug sku gsung thugs rdo rjer mngon par 'tshang rgya ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:2700: de nas shin tu spros med dang /
NK033(gi)008:2701: rab tu spros med kyi dbang bskur te /
NK033(gi)008:2703: de nas lus ngag yid gsum po //
NK033(gi)008:2704: rnal du dbab la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)008:2706: gong du ru shan dbye bas 'byung ba 'khrugs shing
NK033(gi)008:2707: ngal bar gyur pa nyid ngal bsol la rnal du
NK033(gi)008:2708: dbab pa'i tshul ni khregs chod kyi skabs su bshad
NK033(gi)008:2709: pa ltar bya'o // 'di dag gi skabs su rtags
NK033(gi)008:2710: tshad thun mong ma yin pa sogs ni snying tig
NK033(gi)008:2711: pa ltar bya'o // chen mo dang / theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2714: mngon sum gnad la dbab ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)008:2715: phyi nang gsang ba'i bya ba ni //
NK033(gi)008:2716: lus ngag yid kyi dgu sprug btang //
NK033(gi)008:2718: dang po lus kyi gsum ni /
NK033(gi)008:2719: phyi 'jig rten 'khrul pa'i bya byed dang rnam g.yeng thams cad /
NK033(gi)008:2720: nang phyag dang bskor ba sogs dman pa'i dge ba rnams /
NK033(gi)008:2721: gsang ba rnam g.yeng bsgul bskyod thams cad spangs te gcig pur 'dug pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2722: gnyis pa ngag gi gsum ni /
NK033(gi)008:2723: phyi 'jig rten gyi 'khrul gtam sna tshogs /
NK033(gi)008:2724: nang kha ton dang bzlas brjod sogs /
NK033(gi)008:2725: gsang ba smra brjod thams cad spangs te gnas par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2726: gsum pa yid kyi gsum ni /
NK033(gi)008:2727: phyi 'jig rten gyi 'khrul rtog thams cad /
NK033(gi)008:2728: nang bskyed rdzogs kyi sems 'dzin sna tshogs /
NK033(gi)008:2729: gsang ba rnam rtog gi 'phro 'du thams cad spangs
NK033(gi)008:2730: te rtog med kyi ngang du gnas par byas pas
NK033(gi)008:2734: skabs 'di dag tu bdud rtsi ljon shing 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:2735: gyi gnad yig ltar thun mong ma yin pa'i bla
NK033(gi)008:2736: sgrub phyi nang gsang ba yang gsang rnams ji ltar
NK033(gi)008:2737: nus pa nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:2738: gnyis pa gnad lnga la brten nas mngon sum rang thog tu dbab pa la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:2739: zag med kyi ye shes rgyud la brten pa /
NK033(gi)008:2740: mngon sum rang gnad du phab pa'i don ngo sprad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2741: de'ang gdams pa 'di ni sngar las khyad par bdun gyis 'phags te /
NK033(gi)008:2744: nyams len lag len du 'dril ba'i khyad par /
NK033(gi)008:2745: rang gnad mngon sum du gzir ba'i khyad par /
NK033(gi)008:2747: mthong ba dbang po'i khyad par /
NK033(gi)008:2748: rang rig yul gyi khyad par /
NK033(gi)008:2749: nyams myong gong 'phel gyi khyad par bdun gyis 'phags pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2750: khyad par de ldan gyi gdams pa nyid gnad lnga la brten nas nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK033(gi)008:2759: thog mar chos sku seng ge'i bzhugs stangs ni /
NK033(gi)008:2762: lag pa'i mthe bong gis srin lag gi rtsa ba
NK033(gi)008:2763: mnan pa'i rdo rje khu tshur bcangs pa rting pa'i
NK033(gi)008:2764: rtsar sa la btsugs la lag yu drang por bsrang
NK033(gi)008:2765: / ro stod gsengs te dpung pa gyen du then /
NK033(gi)008:2766: mjing pa yid tsam gyen du gtod /
NK033(gi)008:2767: mig gnyis mig 'bras mi bsgul zhing rdzi ma mi
NK033(gi)008:2768: brdebs par lta stangs klod la smin phrag gi nam
NK033(gi)008:2769: mkha' la blta / lce cung zad gyen la bsgril lo //
NK033(gi)008:2770: gnyis pa longs sku glang po che'i bzhugs stangs ni /
NK033(gi)008:2771: kha sbub tu pus brang sbyar /
NK033(gi)008:2772: gru mo sa la btsugs te lag mthil gyis ol ko brten pa'i sor mo 'gram pa la sbyar /
NK033(gi)008:2773: sgal tshigs drang po bsrangs nas thad ka'i nam mkha'
NK033(gi)008:2774: la zur mig hril gyis mgo gyen du dgye tsam
NK033(gi)008:2776: gsum pa sprul sku drang srong gi bzhugs stangs ni /
NK033(gi)008:2777: rkang pa'i long bu gshibs te tsog pur 'dug /
NK033(gi)008:2778: lag gnyis pus mo la bskor /
NK033(gi)008:2779: sgal tshig drang por bsrangs te /
NK033(gi)008:2780: mig zim bur bar sna la gtod do //
NK033(gi)008:2781: de ltar byas pas bzhugs stangs dang pos 'byung ba rang sar dag /
NK033(gi)008:2782: gnyis pas g.yo byed kyi rlung zin /
NK033(gi)008:2783: gsum pas drod skyed cing 'byung bsnyoms par byed /
NK033(gi)008:2784: mthar thug sku gsum du grol nas mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:2785: de'ang rig pa'i ye shes lus la gnas kyang thabs
NK033(gi)008:2786: lus gnad kyis ma gzir na dbang po'i mngon sum
NK033(gi)008:2788: sprul la yan lag yod kyang ma gcus na mi gsal ba bzhin no //
NK033(gi)008:2790: smra brjod cung zad kyang mi smra bar lung dal
NK033(gi)008:2791: bar brten te mchu so ma reg tsam byas la
NK033(gi)008:2792: kha nas btang ba dang cung zad phyir 'dzin pa
NK033(gi)008:2793: la bslab bo // gsum pa sems gnad ni /
NK033(gi)008:2794: khregs chod kyi lta ba gzhir byas te /
NK033(gi)008:2795: sprin dang khu rlangs med pa'i nam mkha' stong sang
NK033(gi)008:2796: nge ba la mig dang nam mkha' rig pa gsum
NK033(gi)008:2797: so sor mi blta bar dbyer med byas pas blta'o
NK033(gi)008:2798: // bzhi pa sgo'i gnad la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:2799: dang po chos sku'i gzigs stangs ni /
NK033(gi)008:2800: mig gi a 'bras gyen la zlog pa gtsug tor
NK033(gi)008:2801: rnam par lta ba'i tshul gyis bltas pas dbyings rig
NK033(gi)008:2802: gi 'phel che / gnyis pa longs sku'i gzigs stangs
NK033(gi)008:2803: thad kar blta ba mda' mkhan smyug ma srong ba
NK033(gi)008:2804: lta bus ye shes kyi snang ba mthong /
NK033(gi)008:2805: gsum pa sprul sku'i gzigs stangs cung zad mthur du
NK033(gi)008:2806: phab pa drang srong bsam gtan sgom pa lta bus
NK033(gi)008:2807: 'od khyim gyi sgron ma mthong ngo //
NK033(gi)008:2808: spyir phyi'i nam mkha' la dbang po mdung tshugs su gtad de bsgoms pas phyi'i dbyings mthong /
NK033(gi)008:2810: yang na zim bus nyi ma la bltas pas nang gi dbyings rig mthong /
NK033(gi)008:2811: de nas dbang po bar snang la 'khrid cing bltas
NK033(gi)008:2812: pas 'khrul snang zhing khams su 'char bar 'gyur ro
NK033(gi)008:2813: // de ltar lta stangs gsum po gang rung gis blta ba la bslabs pas /
NK033(gi)008:2814: mig yul la ji tsam gtad kyang tshugs nus par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:2815: gzigs stangs gang la'ang ha cang rtsol bas bsgrims shing
NK033(gi)008:2816: bsdams na rlung btsan thams su gcun pas gegs su
NK033(gi)008:2817: 'gyur pa'i phyir dal bus bya ba gnad yin no
NK033(gi)008:2818: // lnga pa yul gyi gnad ni /
NK033(gi)008:2819: sprin med pa'i nam mkha' dwangs pa la snga dro
NK033(gi)008:2820: kha nub dang phyi dro kha shar du blta ba'am
NK033(gi)008:2821: / 'od gsal 'char sla ba'i ched du zer gnyis
NK033(gi)008:2822: dang sbyar nas snga dro shar dang phyi dro nub
NK033(gi)008:2823: tu nyi ma las 'og tu khru gang tsam du
NK033(gi)008:2824: bltas pas 'od gsal 'char sla ba'i dgos pa yod
NK033(gi)008:2825: / do // de'ang thag ring po las je thung du 'khrid par bslab pa ni gnad do //
NK033(gi)008:2826: de dag las thog mar longs sku'i bzhugs stangs kyis gzhi bca' /
NK033(gi)008:2827: sprul sku'i bzhugs stangs kyis gnad gzir la lus gcun /
NK033(gi)008:2828: de nas chos sku'i bzhugs stangs kyis rig pa gcun la rtsal sbyang bar gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:2829: yang na chos sku'i bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs snga dro /
NK033(gi)008:2831: sprul sku phyi dro la gtso bor bya /
NK033(gi)008:2832: de'ang rtsa ba'i 'dug stangs gsum po 'byongs nas yan
NK033(gi)008:2833: lag gi 'dug stangs bdun la slob pa'ang gsungs te
NK033(gi)008:2834: / stag skyug khyung dang skyes bu dang /
NK033(gi)008:2835: wa dang bya rgod gyad dang drug /
