NK033(gi)008:2836: chu srin 'dug stangs lus gnad bdun //
NK033(gi)008:2838: yang zab chos nyid kyi 'khor lo las gsungs pa'i
NK033(gi)008:2839: 'dug stangs dang lta stangs rtsa ba yan lag gzhan
NK033(gi)008:2840: rnams dgos shing skabs su babs na de nyid du
NK033(gi)008:2841: shes par bya'o // de'ang re zhig sku gsum gyi
NK033(gi)008:2842: bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs la bsgril na legs par
NK033(gi)008:2843: shes par bya'o // ma zad / las dang po
NK033(gi)008:2844: pas chos sku seng ge'i 'dug stangs kho na la
NK033(gi)008:2845: gtsor 'don byas pa nyid legs par 'gyur gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:2846: yang tig gi nyams len gnad sgron du /
NK033(gi)008:2847: bzhugs stangs gsum las gtso bor drang srong tsog pu bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:2848: gzigs stangs gsum las thur du cung zad phab la blta'o //
NK033(gi)008:2849: gzhan rnams grogs tsam du bslab bo //
NK033(gi)008:2850: zhes gsungs pa nyid da lta lag len bde bas phal cher byed par snang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:2851: gnad de dag la brten nas mngon sum gyi ye
NK033(gi)008:2852: shes nyams su blang ba'i tshe rig pa mi gnas
NK033(gi)008:2853: pa gnas par byed pa la sogs pa nyams su
NK033(gi)008:2854: len pa'i gnad drug ni gnad gsum chos nyid kyi
NK033(gi)008:2855: 'khor lor shes par bya dgos la /
NK033(gi)008:2856: mdor bsdu na bshad ma thag pa de dag la don tshang ngo //
NK033(gi)008:2857: skabs 'dir shes par bya ba nyams len gnad kyi sgron me las 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK033(gi)008:2858: nyams su len dus su dkar lang lang las thig
NK033(gi)008:2859: le ma mthong na mig gnyis mnyam par thad drang
NK033(gi)008:2860: du blta'o // dbyings ma mthong na nyi ma'i drung
NK033(gi)008:2861: nas zur la bltas te khad kyi drang la blta
NK033(gi)008:2862: du blta'o // ba gnad do // de nas dkar shas che na g.yas su bzlog pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2863: ser shas che na gyen la bzlog pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2864: ljang shas che na g.yon du bzlog pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2865: dmar shas che na thur du dbab pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2866: mthing shas che na dbus su dril ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2867: lnga ldan snyoms par gsal na gzigs stangs gang yin las mi 'gyur ba gnad yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2868: 'di'i dus su chos sku'i rten nyi ma la bslab pa yang /
NK033(gi)008:2869: nyin mo nyi ma las gru gang gi 'og gam /
NK033(gi)008:2870: g.yon du nam mkha' la mig 'bras cung zad bzlog la bltas pas /
NK033(gi)008:2871: dbyings 'od lnga'i dbus su rdo rje lu gu rgyud thig le dang bcas pa mthong dus /
NK033(gi)008:2872: longs sku'i gzigs stangs kyis nyi ma las je ring
NK033(gi)008:2873: du zur la khrid la yas man nam phan tshun
NK033(gi)008:2874: gyi thad drang du bzhag pa'am /
NK033(gi)008:2875: sprul sku'i gzigs stangs kyis thur du khrid la sems ma yengs /
NK033(gi)008:2878: bzhugs stangs mi g.yo bar gnas pas /
NK033(gi)008:2879: dbyings 'od lnga dang rig pa lu gu rgyud thig
NK033(gi)008:2880: le dang bcas pa'i snang ba gong du mched par
NK033(gi)008:2881: 'gyur ro // mtshan mo longs sku'i rten zla ba
NK033(gi)008:2882: la bslab pa yang tshul de dang 'dra ba las
NK033(gi)008:2883: 'gyur ro // / khyad par du mig zla ba'i
NK033(gi)008:2884: dkyil du gtad nas sems ma yengs par bzung bas
NK033(gi)008:2886: nyin mo mig gi tsha ba 'phel nas cung zad
NK033(gi)008:2887: mi gsal ba grang bas snyoms te gsal bar byed
NK033(gi)008:2889: sprul sku'i rten sgron me la bslab pa yang de dang mtshungs pa las /
NK033(gi)008:2890: mar me'i dkyil nas gzhan du khrid la bsgom pa gnad yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2891: de yang nyin mo me shel la bslab pas 'od snang gong du mched pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:2892: nyin dus kyi 'khrul snang 'gags pas mya ngan las 'das pa'i rang sa zin par byed la /
NK033(gi)008:2893: mtshan mo zla ba ste chu shel dri ma med
NK033(gi)008:2894: pa dang 'od gsal sgron me la bslabs pas lnga
NK033(gi)008:2895: ldan 'od du snang bas mtshan mo'i 'khrul pa 'khor
NK033(gi)008:2896: ba'i cha gzugs sku gnyis su dag pa gdod mar
NK033(gi)008:2897: grol ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:2898: de yang snga dro phal cher shar phyogs su 'od dkar po ma byung gi bar du gtad la /
NK033(gi)008:2899: de nas snang ba de lhor khrid nas dar cig
NK033(gi)008:2900: bzhag cing phar phar khrid nas nub tu 'od lnga'i
NK033(gi)008:2901: snang ba 'khrigs pa la gtad cing /
NK033(gi)008:2902: phyi dro nub tu gtad dus za 'og ris su snang ba de byang du khrid la bslab bo //
NK033(gi)008:2903: cung zad tsam las khrid mi nus par yal na
NK033(gi)008:2904: rten dang ma reg tsam du yun ring bar bslab
NK033(gi)008:2905: la je ring du khrid cing /
NK033(gi)008:2906: 'od snang gi nang du lu gu rgyud gnas pa la blta ba gnad dam pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:2907: zhes gsungs te shar lho spo ba'i tshul 'di gtso bor khra khang la brten dgos pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2908: gnyis pa mngon sum rang gnad du phab pa'i don ngo sprad pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:2909: yul rkyen dang pral ba nam mkha' stong pa /
NK033(gi)008:2910: dbang po rkyen dang bral ba rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma /
NK033(gi)008:2911: gnas rkyen dang bral ba d+r+wangs shing mtho la dben par /
NK033(gi)008:2912: sems dbang po'i yul gtad la re dogs kyis bcos
NK033(gi)008:2913: bslad mi bya bar rang babs su klod la bla
NK033(gi)008:2915: rang rang gi mdun gyi nam mkhar thig le 'od
NK033(gi)008:2916: lnga'i gur khyim 'ja' ris mu khyud can lnga tshom
NK033(gi)008:2917: du gnas pa'i dbus ma la bla ma kun bzang
NK033(gi)008:2918: yab yum rnam par snang mdzad kyi ngo bo /
NK033(gi)008:2919: phyogs bzhi'i thig ler rgyal ba rigs bzhi yab yum
NK033(gi)008:2920: kha sbyor gyi skur gsal bar mos la gdung shugs
NK033(gi)008:2921: drag pos gsol ba thob cig /
NK033(gi)008:2922: ces phur tshugs gsol 'debs gang 'os bya /
NK033(gi)008:2923: mthar de thams cad rang gi snying gar thim /
NK033(gi)008:2924: mi shigs dwangs ma chen po ngo bo rang bzhin
NK033(gi)008:2925: thugs rje gsum gyi bdag nyid rang rig 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:2926: ba dang dbyer med du bsres la mnyam par bzhag
NK033(gi)008:2927: pa'i ngang nas rdzogs chen yig drug ci nus su
NK033(gi)008:2928: brjod / de nas bzhugs stangs gzigs stangs gang rung
NK033(gi)008:2929: dang bstun snang ba'i 'char cha mtshon par byas la
NK033(gi)008:2930: brjod / / 'o mdo sngags kyi chos gzhan las
NK033(gi)008:2931: bde gshegs snying po dang rgyu'i rgyud sogs su bshad
NK033(gi)008:2932: cing yid byed kyi tshul du sgom pa de nyid
NK033(gi)008:2933: brjod / / / 'dir gzhi gnas kyi rig pa ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes gsum ldan /
NK033(gi)008:2934: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rjes gsum stong gsal mtha'
NK033(gi)008:2935: bral 'gag med tshig dang blo'i spyod yul las 'das
NK033(gi)008:2936: pa'i man ngag zab mos mngon sum du ngo sprod
NK033(gi)008:2937: pa'i tshul skal ldan dbang po yang rab las can
NK033(gi)008:2938: rnams la tshig gsum gyi sgo nas gdams pa ni
NK033(gi)008:2939: / gnas dben par song la lus gnad 'di ltar gyis /
NK033(gi)008:2943: de ltar nyams su blangs pa'i phyi'i dbyings nam mkha'
NK033(gi)008:2944: stong pa me long dang 'dra bas snang ba'i go
NK033(gi)008:2945: 'byed byas nas / nang gi dbyings rnam par dag
NK033(gi)008:2946: pa'i sgron ma zhes bya bdag po'i byad dang 'dra
NK033(gi)008:2947: 'byed byas nas / ba de nyid / thog mar
NK033(gi)008:2948: mthing kha khyab pa chen po'i 'od las rim gyis
NK033(gi)008:2949: mched nas nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon nam rma bya'i mdongs
NK033(gi)008:2952: kha dog gsal ba'i 'od lngar yang //
NK033(gi)008:2955: de'i dbus su thig le stong pa'i sgron ma zhes
NK033(gi)008:2956: bya ba ko mog gi chu la rdo bskyur ba'am
NK033(gi)008:2957: phub kyi sba sgor lta bu thog mar 'al 'ol
NK033(gi)008:2958: tsam dang / de nas dmar zlum gsal dwangs can 'char la /
NK033(gi)008:2959: de'i nang du rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyun bdag po'i sems dang 'dra ba nyid 'char te /
NK033(gi)008:2960: phra ba rta rnga la mdud pa byas pa lta bu dang /
NK033(gi)008:2961: gser skud dang mu tig gi phreng ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:2963: me tog gi chun po dang /
NK033(gi)008:2964: me tog gi d+r+wa ba rang sar gnas pa lta
NK033(gi)008:2965: bu thog mar 'al 'ol mi gsal ba 'gul 'phrigs
NK033(gi)008:2967: de nyid lta stangs kyis khrid nas dbyings kyi ra
NK033(gi)008:2968: bar bcug ste cher re gtad nas yin min gyi
NK033(gi)008:2969: rtog dpyod kyis ma bslad par lta mkhan gyi rig
NK033(gi)008:2970: pa de dang / rig pa rang gi ngo bo
NK033(gi)008:2971: la lta shes tsam las mi g.yo bar bsgoms pas
NK033(gi)008:2972: je brtan je gsal du 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)008:2974: rang gi rig pa lu gu rgyud //
NK033(gi)008:2977: de'ang blos byas kyis bcos bsgyur mi bya bar dbyings rig rang ngo la bltas pas /
NK033(gi)008:2978: phyi'i snang ba ma 'gags shing nang gi 'dzin pas ma bslad pa /
NK033(gi)008:2979: brjod med spros pa dang bral ba'i rang so bzung
NK033(gi)008:2980: bas yul dang yul can dbyer med 'dres nas 'od
NK033(gi)008:2981: gsal gyi snang ba smin mtshams nas bral te gsal
NK033(gi)008:2983: 'od gsal gyi snang ba de mi gsal ba'am g.yas
NK033(gi)008:2984: g.yon steng 'og tu yal yol byed na de'i steng
NK033(gi)008:2985: du mig dang sems car phog tu mi 'brang bar
NK033(gi)008:2986: lta stangs kyi khrid la sngar bzhin shar ba la
NK033(gi)008:2987: sems ha cang ma bsgrims par gtod cig /
NK033(gi)008:2988: de ltar nyams su blangs pas nyams myong rig thog
NK033(gi)008:2989: tu phebs te rig pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud
NK033(gi)008:2990: kyi rang zhal mngon sum du mjal bas kun tu
NK033(gi)008:2991: bzang po dang skal ba mnyam par gsungs pa yin
NK033(gi)008:2992: no // de ltar yang 'das rjes las /
NK033(gi)008:2993: mngon gsum gnad 'di sus mthong ba //
NK033(gi)008:2994: khams gsum ldog pa ma yin no //
NK033(gi)008:2997: dbyings dang rig pa'i lta stangs ni //
NK033(gi)008:2998: sgrib byed bral ba'i nam mkhar blta //
NK033(gi)008:2999: dbyings kyi nang du lu gu rgyud //
NK033(gi)008:3000: mnyam par bzhag cing 'bral mi bya //
NK033(gi)008:3001: de ltar su yis mthong ba'i mi //
NK033(gi)008:3002: thog ma'i kun tu bzang po dang //
NK033(gi)008:3003: skal ba dag ni mnyam pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3004: zhes gsungs pa'i don lags pas nges shes skyed cing
NK033(gi)008:3005: nyams len la brtson pas snang ba bzhi gong du
NK033(gi)008:3009: de ltar nyams su blang bar bstan nas /
NK033(gi)008:3010: de'i don la yid ches par bya ba'i phyir rig
NK033(gi)008:3011: pa'i rgyab rten gyi man ngag gis gtan la phab
NK033(gi)008:3012: nas / zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar zangs yig can
NK033(gi)008:3013: rang gi rig pa'i rgyab brten nas bshad pa dang
NK033(gi)008:3014: nas / / gzhan yang dung yig can sogs nas ji skad gsungs pa ltar /
NK033(gi)008:3017: de nyams len du 'gro ba'i rgyu mtshan /
NK033(gi)008:3018: 'bras bu sku gsum gyi rnam bzhag bstan pa rnams
NK033(gi)008:3019: kyis dbyings rig ji ltar mthong ba de'i rgyu mtshan
NK033(gi)008:3020: go don rnams legs par bshad de nges shes bskyed
NK033(gi)008:3021: par bya'o // 'dir spro zhing nus na yang tig
NK033(gi)008:3022: gi dpe don gsal byed sgron me'i ngo sprod kyi
NK033(gi)008:3024: gsum pa snang ba bzhi'i 'char tshul bstan pa la bzhi /
NK033(gi)008:3025: dang po chos nyid mngon sum gyi snang ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:3026: de ltar bya ba btang nas rtse gcig tu nyams su blangs te /
NK033(gi)008:3027: thog mar rdo rje lu gu rgyud la mi 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:3028: bar bltas pas dbyings snang rnam dag gi sgron ma
NK033(gi)008:3029: 'ja' 'od kyi nang du thig le stong sgron mu
NK033(gi)008:3030: khyud can gyi thig le dmar ser mtheb long tsam
NK033(gi)008:3031: pa sogs nyis sbrel sum sbrel gyi bar tshun chad
NK033(gi)008:3032: mthong ba ste / de yang res snang res mi snang ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3033: 'dir rdo rje lu gu rgyud 'phar g.yo byed pa'i
NK033(gi)008:3034: rnam pa de nyid ar la gtad pa'am btson du
NK033(gi)008:3037: smin mtshams dbyings rnam dag gi sgron ma yi ge na ro 'dra ba /
NK033(gi)008:3038: kha dog 'ja' tshon lta bu la rig pa ma
NK033(gi)008:3039: yengs par de la bcug ste lta ba ni 'dzin
NK033(gi)008:3040: par byed pa'i lcags kyu zhes bya ba mchog tu
NK033(gi)008:3041: zab pa'i man ngag yin gsungs so //
NK033(gi)008:3042: gnyis pa nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba ni //
NK033(gi)008:3043: 'od lnga thig le dang bcas pa rtag tu snang
NK033(gi)008:3044: zhing 'od lnga'i snang ba za 'og gi gur khyim
NK033(gi)008:3045: lta bu dang rtsibs shar gyen 'greng sogs smin mtshams
NK033(gi)008:3046: kyi sor bzhi las bral te nam mkhar 'thon nas
NK033(gi)008:3047: mthong ba'i yul tsam du dbyings snang zlum khrigs kyi
NK033(gi)008:3048: nang du pad 'dab bzhi bzhis bskor ba lta bu'i
NK033(gi)008:3049: tshom bu 'char ba tshun chad do //
NK033(gi)008:3050: gsum pa rig pa tshad phebs ni /
NK033(gi)008:3051: 'od lnga'i snang bas khengs pa'i dbus na mu khyud
NK033(gi)008:3052: lnga ldan gyi thig le'i nang du dang por lha'i
NK033(gi)008:3053: gtsug tor sogs nas rim par phyed sku dang /
NK033(gi)008:3054: sku rkyang sku lnga tshom sogs grangs med zhing khams thams cad gang ba'i bar 'char ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3055: bzhi pa chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:3059: nyams snang gi 'phel ba dang bcas pa thams cad zad pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:3062: gzung 'dzin gyi blo chos skur grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3063: 'di dag gi don rgyas pa ni chos rje kun
NK033(gi)008:3064: mkhyen chen po'i gsung rab rnams las shes par bya'o
NK033(gi)008:3065: // bzhi pa mtha' brten gyi man ngag bshad pa la bzhi /
NK033(gi)008:3066: mi 'gal ba gsum la gzhi bca' ba /
NK033(gi)008:3067: sdod pa gsum gyis tshad gzung ba /
NK033(gi)008:3068: thob pa gsum gyis gzer gdab pa /
NK033(gi)008:3069: gdeng bzhis grol tshad bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3070: dang po ni nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)008:3071: lus mi 'gul ba bzhugs stangs gsum las mi 'da' bar byas pas /
NK033(gi)008:3072: rtsa rlung thad sor gnas pas rtog pa rang 'gags pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3073: mig mi 'gul bar gzigs stangs gsum dang mi 'bral bar byas pas /
NK033(gi)008:3074: mngon sum yul la gsal bas yid dpyod tshig gi sgro 'dogs dang bral ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3075: rlung rig mi 'gul ba dal bar brten pas chos
NK033(gi)008:3076: nyid rang ngor gnas te ma bu dbyer med du
NK033(gi)008:3077: 'dres nas / gdod ma'i dbyings su gnas pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK033(gi)008:3078: de'i tshe sgron ma bzhi'i don la spyod pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:3079: snying dbus 'od rtsa'i nang na ye shes chen po gnas pa yang /
NK033(gi)008:3080: ngo bo stong pa dang thugs rje rigs pa gnyis
NK033(gi)008:3081: su med pa ni shes rab rang byung gi sgron
NK033(gi)008:3082: ma yin la / rang bzhin gsal ba 'ja' 'od kyi khang pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:3083: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma dang /
NK033(gi)008:3084: de'i dbus na lnga ldan 'od kyi tshom bu rigs
NK033(gi)008:3085: lnga sku'i cha can ni thig le stong pa'i sgron
NK033(gi)008:3086: ma ste / rma bya'i mdongs lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)008:3087: nang gi gdangs phyir shar dus mig rgyang zhags chu'i
NK033(gi)008:3088: sgron ma'i a 'bras kyi 'od gdangs dmar ser phyir
NK033(gi)008:3089: snang ba la thig le stong pa'i sgron mar btags
NK033(gi)008:3090: pa ni gdangs kyi thig le stong sgron yin la
NK033(gi)008:3091: / nam mkhar snang ba'i 'od snang la dbyings rnam
NK033(gi)008:3092: dag gi sgron mar btags pa yang gdangs kyi dbyings
NK033(gi)008:3094: de bzhin du rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK033(gi)008:3095: ces btags kyang rig pa'i gdangs rdo rje lu gu
NK033(gi)008:3096: rgyud do // de ltar 'od nang du lu gu
NK033(gi)008:3097: rgyud gnas pa la gtad nas ma yengs par phyir
NK033(gi)008:3098: rgyud do // bsgoms pas / nang du stong gsal
NK033(gi)008:3099: spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes shar ba ni
NK033(gi)008:3100: rgyud do // bsgoms pas / / shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:3102: gnad des ye thog tu dus der phebs pa la
NK033(gi)008:3103: btags kyis sngar med gsar byung gi shes rab rang
NK033(gi)008:3104: byung gi sgron ma ni ma yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3105: gnyis pa sdod pa gsum ni /
NK033(gi)008:3107: phyi snang ba sdod pas rkyen ngan grogs su 'char /
NK033(gi)008:3108: nang sgyu lus sdod pas 'khrul ba'i bya ba dang bral /
NK033(gi)008:3109: gsang ba rlung sems sdod pas rnam rtog skye mi srid pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3110: 'di'i skabs su tshad rmi lam gyis gzung ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3111: rtags lus ngag la 'char ba gnyis las /
NK033(gi)008:3113: brtson 'grus rab rmi lam gtan nas 'gags /
NK033(gi)008:3114: 'bring gis rmi lam la rmi lam du shes /
NK033(gi)008:3115: tha mas rmi lam ngan pa med par bzang po sha stag tu 'gyur ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3117: chos nyid mngon sum gyi dus na /
NK033(gi)008:3118: lus rus sbal 'khar gzhong du bcug pa ltar 'dug stangs las 'bral mi phod pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3119: ngag lkugs pa ltar brjod du med pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3120: sems mkha' 'gro rnyi la zin pa ltar rnam rtog
NK033(gi)008:3121: 'phro ba ltar snang yang gzhi las ma g.yos pa'o
NK033(gi)008:3123: lus skyes bu nad kyis gdungs pa ltar rgyan dang byi dor med pa /
NK033(gi)008:3124: ngag smyon pa ltar zang thal rjes med pa /
NK033(gi)008:3125: sems dug nad kyis zin pa ltar rtog pa'i 'phro 'du chad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3126: rig pa tshad phebs kyi dus na /
NK033(gi)008:3127: lus glang po che 'dam du bying ba ltar skad
NK033(gi)008:3128: cig gis ri brag la thogs med du 'gro ba
NK033(gi)008:3129: / ngag grul bum gyi phru gu ltar snyan zhing yid du 'ong ba /
NK033(gi)008:3130: sems snying la mdas zin pa ltar dran bsam gyi 'phro 'du chad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3131: chos nyid zad pa'i dus na /
NK033(gi)008:3132: lus dur khrod kyi ro ltar dgag sgrub kyi 'khrul pa med pa /
NK033(gi)008:3133: ngag brag cha ltar gzhan gyi rjes su zlos pa /
NK033(gi)008:3134: sems rims nad byang pa'i skyes bu ltar dran bsam
NK033(gi)008:3135: dbyings su dag nas rig pa rang gsal du gnas
NK033(gi)008:3136: pa'o // gsum pa thob pa gsum ni /
NK033(gi)008:3137: phyi snang ba la dbang thob pas snang rkyen zhing khams su grol /
NK033(gi)008:3138: nang phung po la dbang thob pas sgyu lus 'od gsal du grol /
NK033(gi)008:3139: gsang ba dbyings rig la dbang thob pas 'khrul rtog rang 'gags pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3141: yar sangs rgyas la thob tu re ba med pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3142: ma thob kyis dogs pa med /
NK033(gi)008:3143: mar 'khor bar mi skye ba'i re ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3144: skyes kyis dogs pa med pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3145: de dag gis rig pa gtan la dbab pa la
NK033(gi)008:3146: mthod rgal snying po'i don mngon sum lam du byed
NK033(gi)008:3148: gsum pa rjes gnad bzhi chos nyid kyi 'khor los
NK033(gi)008:3149: chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor du bya ba'i tshul
NK033(gi)008:3153: nyin mo snang ba rgyas gdab pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3154: mtshan mo ye shes gnad du bsnun pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3156: yang zab ye shes 'khor lo ltar gzhi lam 'bras
NK033(gi)008:3157: bu gsum la dam tshig chen po bcu gsum gyis
NK033(gi)008:3158: bsrung ba'i tshul nyid 'dir len dgos la /
NK033(gi)008:3162: mdor na snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK033(gi)008:3163: gang la'ang 'dzin zhen gyi blo'i dri mas ma bslad
NK033(gi)008:3164: / nyams kyi zhen pas ma bcings par gang ltar
NK033(gi)008:3165: snang yang rmi lam sgyu ma'i rol pa lta bu'i
NK033(gi)008:3167: rmi lam sgyu ma lta bur shar ba'i stong cha'i blo de yang yod med /
NK033(gi)008:3171: blang dor las 'das pa'i spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la bsal bzhag med par 'jog go //
NK033(gi)008:3172: rjes thob kyi gnas skabs rnams su'ang shes pa rgya
NK033(gi)008:3173: yan du ma shor bar dran 'dzin gyis 'di ltar
NK033(gi)008:3174: snang ba'i chos thams cad sgyu ma /
NK033(gi)008:3178: dri za'i grong khyer tsam du nges par 'dug ang /
NK033(gi)008:3179: skad cig kyang bden par grub pa rdul tsam yang med snyam du rtsal sbyang /
NK033(gi)008:3180: de bzhin du chags sdang dgag sgrub /
NK033(gi)008:3181: re dogs sogs gnyis 'dzin thams cad gnyis med ye
NK033(gi)008:3182: grol gyi dgongs pa zang thal rjen par skyong ba
NK033(gi)008:3185: srod la dbang po gnas su bsdu ba /
NK033(gi)008:3186: nam gung shes pa bum par 'jug pa /
NK033(gi)008:3187: tho rangs rig pa rang gsal gtod pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3189: mi tshe'i phyed gnyid log pa yin pas gnyid dge
NK033(gi)008:3190: bar bsgyur ba'i phyir 'di ltar nyams su blang bar
NK033(gi)008:3191: bya ste / sprul sku drang srong tsog pu'i lus gnad bcas la /
NK033(gi)008:3192: rang gi lus kyi dbus su rtsa dbu ma phyi dkar la nang dmar ba'am /
NK033(gi)008:3193: yang na kha dog dmar skya dwangs gsal sbubs stong
NK033(gi)008:3194: mda' smyug tsam spyi bo nas gsang gnas kyi bar
NK033(gi)008:3195: drang thal ler gnas pa'i lte bar pad+ma dmar po
NK033(gi)008:3196: 'dab ma bzhi pa'i dbus su a thung dmar po
NK033(gi)008:3197: reg bya tsha ba sol me ngar ma la phul
NK033(gi)008:3199: dbu ma'i yas snar ham dkar po mgo thur du
NK033(gi)008:3200: blta ba snum la 'dril ba bde ba'i rang bzhin
NK033(gi)008:3202: bde drod kyi gzhi bca' ba'i dmigs pa la sems dum gcig gzung ngo //
NK033(gi)008:3203: de nas rlung ro lan gsum sang gis bsal /
NK033(gi)008:3205: 'og rlung gyen du 'then pas lte ba'i a las me dmar khyug ge 'bar /
NK033(gi)008:3207: ham las byang sems bde ba'i rgyun nar babs pas me'i gsos byas /
NK033(gi)008:3208: me cher 'bar bas las dang bag chags bsregs /
NK033(gi)008:3209: zla ba bdud rtsir zhu ba'i dwangs mas dbu ma dang lus kyi rtsa khams thams cad gang /
NK033(gi)008:3210: bde drod kyi ye shes khyad par ba skyes pa la sems bzung ste bum can ci nus bzung /
NK033(gi)008:3211: bum can gyis ngal na sngar gyi dmigs pa de
NK033(gi)008:3212: rlung rang babs kyi ngang nas ci nus su bsgom
NK033(gi)008:3214: longs sku'i 'dug stangs sam gzhogs g.yas phab par gsungs kyang /
NK033(gi)008:3216: drang srong tsog pu'i stabs kyis nyal bar bzhed la /
NK033(gi)008:3217: gang ltar lus kyi dbus su dbu ma sngar ltar gsal btab /
NK033(gi)008:3218: khyad par du snying gar pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK033(gi)008:3219: bzhi pa kha cung zad bye ba'i dbus su a
NK033(gi)008:3220: yig dkar po 'od 'bar ba zhig bsgoms la sems
NK033(gi)008:3221: dar gcig bzung rjes spyi bor yang a dkar po
NK033(gi)008:3222: zhig bsgom / de nas a gnyis kyi bar du
NK033(gi)008:3223: a dkar po shin tu phra ba nyer gcig phreng
NK033(gi)008:3224: ba brgyus pa lta bur gnas par bsams la rlung
NK033(gi)008:3225: byang bar yod na bum can kha sbyor du bzung
NK033(gi)008:3226: zhig bsgom / zhing / de ltar min na 'jam
NK033(gi)008:3227: rlung rang babs kyi ngang nas gsal stong gi ye
NK033(gi)008:3228: shes sa le ba'i ngang du ci nus bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:3229: gnyid du 'gro khar a rnams rim gyis snying ga'i a la thim /
NK033(gi)008:3230: de nas spyi bo'i a de yang snying ga'i a la sib kyis thim /
NK033(gi)008:3231: snying pad+ma kha zum pa'i nang du a de bum nang gi mar me ltar gnas par bsams la /
NK033(gi)008:3232: rmi lam 'dzin pa'i 'dun pa bcas te sems ha
NK033(gi)008:3233: cang ma grims ha kyang ma glod pa'i ngang nas
NK033(gi)008:3235: gal te gnyid ma byung na sngar gyi dmigs pa de ga yang yang bskyar /
NK033(gi)008:3236: rmi lam dang gnyid kyi bar rnam rtog gzhan gyis ma chod par slob pa gal che /
NK033(gi)008:3237: rnam rtog shar yang spang blang bsu skyel dgag sgrub
NK033(gi)008:3238: mi bya bar a yig gi steng du sems bslan
NK033(gi)008:3239: te bzhag / gnyid mthug po min pa'i gnyid dang
NK033(gi)008:3240: rmi lam gyi bar der mi dang khang khyim sogs
NK033(gi)008:3241: rnam rtog gi snang ba ra ri zhig 'byung ba
NK033(gi)008:3242: de rmi lam gyi rgyu yin pas na mig mi
NK033(gi)008:3243: 'byed par de rmi lam yin snyam pa'i 'dun pa
NK033(gi)008:3244: btang ba la a de'i steng du sems bzung la
NK033(gi)008:3245: bzhag cing ngos zin par byas pas dpe khab mig
NK033(gi)008:3246: tu skud pa tshud pa ltar mu 'byor zhing zin
NK033(gi)008:3247: te bzhag / sla ba yin / de las ji
NK033(gi)008:3248: zhig na gnyid mthug pa'i skabs kyi stong pa'i ye
NK033(gi)008:3249: shes rmi lam med par gsal stong nam mkha' lta
NK033(gi)008:3250: bu lhag ger 'char na de'i nyams ma shor ba'i
NK033(gi)008:3251: ngang las lha sku sgyu ma lta bu'i skur langs
NK033(gi)008:3252: shing 'dzin med spros bral gyi ngang du 'jog go
NK033(gi)008:3253: te bzhag / sla ba yin / // rmis na
NK033(gi)008:3254: rmi lam dang rnam rtog thams cad snying nang gi
NK033(gi)008:3255: a la bsdus shing gong ltar bsgoms pas 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:3256: rang byung gi ye shes 'char ro //
NK033(gi)008:3257: nyin mo'ang rmi lam gyi 'dun shugs dang snang ba
NK033(gi)008:3258: zhi khro so so'i sku spel bsgyur byed pa dang
NK033(gi)008:3259: / res 'khor ba'i las sna tshogs la spel bsgyur bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3261: ma dag pa'i zhing khams rnams su 'gro zhing gnas lugs brtag pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3263: gcan gzan sogs kyis mtshon 'jigs skrag gi snang ba
NK033(gi)008:3264: dang sbyar te 'dun shugs drag pos thog bardzisa kyi
NK033(gi)008:3265: rtsal sbyangs pas / rmi lam gyi rten des nyin
NK033(gi)008:3266: mo ji ltar sbyangs pa'i don rnams mtshan mo gang
NK033(gi)008:3267: 'dod kyi sprul sgyur byed nus shing /
NK033(gi)008:3268: de yang thog mar 'ol spyi tsam dang /
NK033(gi)008:3269: de nas je brtan je gsal du 'gyur ba yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:3270: de yang gnyid du song la nye 'khor gyi gzugs mthong /
NK033(gi)008:3275: gtam gyi don rig la rtog pa mi skye /
NK033(gi)008:3276: gnyid du ma song ba yang ma yin te /
NK033(gi)008:3277: de las sad rgyu 'byung ba yin /
NK033(gi)008:3278: de ltar brtson pa chen pos yang yang bzung kyang
NK033(gi)008:3279: ma zin na 'byams pa yin pas 'byams pa bzhi'i
NK033(gi)008:3281: srab mthug 'od gsal gyi dbye sgo sogs khrid rim spyi dang mtshungs pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3283: tho rangs kyi thun la babs pa na /
NK033(gi)008:3285: snying nang gi a der gsal snang 'don bskyor zhig bya /
NK033(gi)008:3286: mig bar snang la gtad de ha zhes gsum bus
NK033(gi)008:3287: pas snying ga'i pad+ma kha bye ba'i nang nas a
NK033(gi)008:3288: de tshangs bug tu rgyangs kyis thon /
NK033(gi)008:3289: gzhu gang tsam gyi nam mkha' la ling nge 'dug
NK033(gi)008:3290: pa la sems gtad la rlung cung zhig phyir 'dzin
NK033(gi)008:3292: gang la yang mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzang po skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)008:3293: shes pa yer zhing rgod na a de je dmar gyur te /
NK033(gi)008:3294: snying nang du 'dug pa la sems gtad /
NK033(gi)008:3295: mig phyed btsum gyi cung zad dma' bar lta zhing bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:3296: yang bying na sngar ltar bsgoms pas bying rgod dang
NK033(gi)008:3297: bral ba'i ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa chu
NK033(gi)008:3298: bo'i rgyun bzhin 'char ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3299: de ltar mtshan mo thun gsum gyi rim pas nyams
NK033(gi)008:3300: su blangs pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ting nge
NK033(gi)008:3301: 'dzin bzang po skye zhing mngon par shes pa la
NK033(gi)008:3303: bya rtsol bral ba kun bzang gi klong der myur du grol bar 'gyur ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3304: 'di kun mkhyen chos rje'i zhal nas /
NK033(gi)008:3305: de ltar nyin mtshan du sgom pa thams cad kyi skabs su'ang /
NK033(gi)008:3306: dal 'byor rnyed par dka' bas dal ba chud mi gson par brtson pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3307: tshe mi rtag par shes pas sgrub pa la long yod mi byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3308: 'khor ba sdug bsngal du shes pas srin pa la mngon par skyo ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3309: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pas gang la'ang bden zhen med pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3310: mya ngan las 'das pa mchog tu bde bas zhi ba'i byang chub bsgrub pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3311: gsang sngags thabs kyis grub pas sna tshogs lam la bslab pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3312: theg chen snying rje la rags las pas gzhan don sems bskyed dang ldan pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3313: byin rlabs mos gus la rags las pas bla ma sangs rgyas dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3314: thams cad rang sems la thug pas dag snang phyogs med la sbyang ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3315: 'khor ba 'khrul rtog las byung bas gzung 'dzin gyi rtsa ba gcod pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3316: bde sdug sngon las las byung bas dge sdig blang dor du bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3317: 'khor 'das rig pa las shar bas rig pa rang gnad du ngo shes par bya ba ste /
NK033(gi)008:3318: gnad rnam pa bcu gnyis kyis rang gi rgyud 'dul
NK033(gi)008:3319: ba ni yang gnad gal po che'i gdams pa yin
NK033(gi)008:3320: pas snying nas bsam par bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:3323: gong gsal dmigs pa de dang sgom pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK033(gi)008:3325: lus nyams shes nyams la sogs pa'i rtags tshad dang gegs sel bog 'don /
NK033(gi)008:3326: nyams myong skyes rim nas ngo sprod thabs rnams zangs yig can sogs rtsa ba'i man ngag dang /
NK033(gi)008:3327: de dag gi dgongs 'grel yang tig yid bzhin nor
NK033(gi)008:3328: bu'i glegs bam nyid 'bral spang gi tshul du 'chang
NK033(gi)008:3329: nas rtogs par bya dgos shing /
NK033(gi)008:3330: khyad par lus nyams len gyi rten yin pas nad gdon gyi gegs sel bdud rtsi'i ljon shing /
NK033(gi)008:3331: mngon sum gyi gnad mig yin pas de la gegs sel sgron ma snang byed /
NK033(gi)008:3332: rig pa sems nyams len gyi rtsa ba yin pas
NK033(gi)008:3333: de'i gegs sel ye shes dri med rnams tshig tsam
NK033(gi)008:3334: du ma lus par brten par bya /
NK033(gi)008:3335: bogs 'don khregs thod gnyis ka la gal che ba nam mkha' sum phrugs kyi gdams pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:3336: phyi'i nam mkha' sprin med sngo dwangs ni 'dus ma byas rdul bral gyi nam mkha' /
NK033(gi)008:3337: nang gi nam mkha' gsang ba'i rtsa dbu ma ste
NK033(gi)008:3338: rgya mtsho gser gyi nyi ma las byung ba'i ka
NK033(gi)008:3339: ti shes sbug rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma dang 'brel
NK033(gi)008:3340: ba / de gnyis ka la khyab byed gsang ba'i nam mkha' snying ga'i mi shigs pa'i thig le /
NK033(gi)008:3341: de'ang ma dag pa gsum 'dus pa'i cha can ma
NK033(gi)008:3342: yin par dag pa'i mi shigs pa 'od gsal ba'i
NK033(gi)008:3343: rang bzhin ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi
NK033(gi)008:3344: bdag nyid rnam pa thams cad pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:3345: de yang nam mkha' dang po'i dpe rdul bral gyi me long /
NK033(gi)008:3346: gnyis pa'i dpe mda' srong gi mig /
NK033(gi)008:3347: gsum pa'i dpe nor bu ke ta ka lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)008:3348: de yang spyir rtsa dbu ma zhes bya ba dngos
NK033(gi)008:3349: su mig shes kyis bzung rung dbu ma'i tha snyad
NK033(gi)008:3350: 'dogs pa de ni da lta lus la gnas tshul
NK033(gi)008:3351: sgal tshigs dang nye ba'i rgyab ngos su yod pa
NK033(gi)008:3352: srog rtsa zhes grags pa ste gzung 'dzin 'khor ba
NK033(gi)008:3353: skyed byed yin / 'dir nang gi nam mkhar bzhag
NK033(gi)008:3354: rgyu'i dbus ni mig shes kyi spyod yul las 'das
NK033(gi)008:3355: pa dwangs ma lnga ldan gyi rtsa lus can rnams
NK033(gi)008:3356: kyi snying ga'i dbus su yod pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3357: de las gyes pa'i yal ga mig la zug pa
NK033(gi)008:3358: gnyis te snga ma'i ming la rgya mtsho gser gyi
NK033(gi)008:3360: phyi ma la rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma zhes bya /
NK033(gi)008:3361: de dag ni rten khyab bya'i nam mkha' 'am dbu ma yin /
NK033(gi)008:3362: de'i rang bzhin shin tu rnam dag dwangs ma chen
NK033(gi)008:3363: po'i dbu ma de gnyis kyi rang bzhin du bzhugs
NK033(gi)008:3364: pa yang / de dag gi khongs su bsdu zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3365: ming gi brda chad kyang mnyam por 'jug /
NK033(gi)008:3366: gnyis ka yang nang gi nam mkha' yin /
NK033(gi)008:3367: gsang ba'i nam mkha' dwangs ma lnga ldan gyi thig le /
NK033(gi)008:3368: de'i chos nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ngo
NK033(gi)008:3369: bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi bdag nyid rnam
NK033(gi)008:3370: pa thams cad pa de ni brten pa'am khyab byed
NK033(gi)008:3371: do // de ltar shes par byas nas phyi'i nam
NK033(gi)008:3372: mkha' shin tu dwangs pa la bzhugs stangs gang rung
NK033(gi)008:3373: dang 'brel bas nang gi nam mkha' gtad /
NK033(gi)008:3374: de la gsang ba'i nam mkha' gtad pas mi rtog
NK033(gi)008:3375: pa'i ye shes rgyud la tshegs med du 'char bar
NK033(gi)008:3376: 'gyur ro // mun khang brten pa'i lag len sogs
NK033(gi)008:3377: ni 'od gsal ye shes 'khor lo las shes par
NK033(gi)008:3378: 'gyur ro // bya'o // gegs sel bogs 'don nyams
NK033(gi)008:3379: len gyi rjes spyod mdor bsdus pa kun mkhyen chos
NK033(gi)008:3380: 'gyur ro // bya'o // rje'i zhal nas / gang
NK033(gi)008:3381: snang sgyu ma'i dpe brgyan du shes pas chags sdang
NK033(gi)008:3382: dang nyon mongs las grol bar bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3383: dgag sgrub sems kyi rol par shar tshad gzhi med
NK033(gi)008:3384: rtsa ba dang bral bar thag bcad la 'dzin zhen
NK033(gi)008:3386: ji srid bdag 'dzin dbyings su ma nub kyi bar
NK033(gi)008:3387: du zab mo'i gdams pa bsgom zhing rgyu 'bras kyi
NK033(gi)008:3388: las la 'dzem / dag snang dang mos gus bya zhing rang sems la skyon med par /
NK033(gi)008:3389: dam tshig dang sdom pa bsrung zhing gcig pur dben par 'dug /
NK033(gi)008:3390: rnam g.yeng dang 'du 'dzi spangs shing dgos med rgyud la brten /
NK033(gi)008:3391: chags med zhen med bya zhing 'dzin med lam du slong /
NK033(gi)008:3392: rtag tu 'chi ba bsam zhing brtson 'grus med bzhin sbar /
NK033(gi)008:3393: nyin mtshan dge bas 'da' zhing tshe'i 'di'i bya ba btang /
NK033(gi)008:3394: rtag tu bla ma bsten cing mos gus gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)008:3395: gtad med lam du khyer zhing byar med ngang la bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:3396: bdag gzhan gnyis 'dzin spangs shing re dogs rtsa ba gcad /
NK033(gi)008:3397: rkyen ngan lam du slong zhing cir snang bla mar blta /
NK033(gi)008:3398: thams cad rang snang shes pas bdag 'dzin zhen pa dor /
NK033(gi)008:3399: gang yang snying po med pas bden med yo lang bskyang /
NK033(gi)008:3400: ye stong bab stong shes pas rang snang zhar la 'char /
NK033(gi)008:3401: de lta bu'i thabs dang spyod pas gnas shin nyin mtshan 'da' bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:3402: blo rkyen khar 'chor ring la rig pa'i rtsal sbyong dben par nyams len la 'bungs /
NK033(gi)008:3403: dgag sgrub zhen 'dzin yod ring la dge sdig blang dor bya zhing gnyis med don la sbyang /
NK033(gi)008:3404: gang yang grogs su ma shar ba'i ring la gdams
NK033(gi)008:3405: pa'i sna kha bsgyur zhing rig pa'i don la blta
NK033(gi)008:3406: / skye shi'i 'jigs dngangs skyes ring la skye med
NK033(gi)008:3407: don la sbyangs pas phyi nang thams cad chos nyid
NK033(gi)008:3408: du 'char ba'i dus na sgom med chu bo rgyun
NK033(gi)008:3409: gyi rnal 'byor la gnas pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3410: zhes gdams par mdzad pa nyid snying gi bdud rtsir bzung bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)008:3411: gzhan yang khrid tshul 'diir shin tu gal che ba
NK033(gi)008:3412: sems dang rig pa 'byed pa'i man ngag kyang khregs
NK033(gi)008:3413: chod kyi rgyab yig nam mkha' dri med sogs las
NK033(gi)008:3414: rtogs par bya ba kho na'o //
NK033(gi)008:3415: don gnyis pa dbang po 'bring bar dor grol ba'i khrid la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:3420: gzhi ka dag las gzhan du snang ba thams cad bar do'i gnas skabs yin te /
NK033(gi)008:3421: gzhi snang ye shes su 'char ba'i snang cha ni dag pa chos nyid kyi bar do dang /
NK033(gi)008:3422: 'khrul snang 'gro drug gis bsdus pa'i chos so cog
NK033(gi)008:3423: ni ma dag pa 'khrul ba'i bar do yin la
NK033(gi)008:3424: / de yang dbyings ka dag las shar zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3425: 'char gzhi dbyings su ma rdzogs kyi bar gyi sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa ni bar do'o //
NK033(gi)008:3427: skye shi'am rang bzhin gyi bar do //
NK033(gi)008:3432: ma'i mngal du skye ba grub nas 'chi nad kyis btab pa tshun chad do //
NK033(gi)008:3434: 'chi ba la phyogs pa nas nang dbugs chad pa tshun chad do //
NK033(gi)008:3436: nang dbugs chad nas 'od gsal gyi snang ba shar te /
NK033(gi)008:3437: lhun grub kyi snang ba thim par tshun chad do //
NK033(gi)008:3439: lhun grub kyi snang ba thim nas phyi ma'i skye srid grub pa tshun chad do //
NK033(gi)008:3441: bar do bzhi la dpe don gnyis gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK033(gi)008:3442: dang po skye gnas kyi bar do la sgro 'dogs
NK033(gi)008:3443: chod pa thi bya tshang du 'jug pa lta bu
NK033(gi)008:3444: ni / don bla ma dam pa la brten nas /
NK033(gi)008:3445: des bstan pa'i gdams ngag la thos bsam gyis sgro
NK033(gi)008:3446: 'dogs bcad de bsgoms pas gnas lugs kyi don phyin
NK033(gi)008:3447: ci ma log par nyams myong rig thog tu sgro
NK033(gi)008:3448: 'dogs chod de slob pa'i lam bzhi dang sa bcu'i
NK033(gi)008:3449: yon tan rnams rdzogs nas mi slob pa'i 'bras bu
NK033(gi)008:3451: gnyis pa 'chi ka'i bar do la gsal gdab pa
NK033(gi)008:3452: sgeg mo me long la blta ba lta bu ni
NK033(gi)008:3453: / sngar bsgoms pa'i gdams pa rnams skabs 'dir blo la gsal 'debs pa yin te /
NK033(gi)008:3454: ji ltar 'debs na 'chi ba 'od gsal dang rjes
NK033(gi)008:3455: mthun gyi thim rim rnams la gdams pa'i gnad blo
NK033(gi)008:3456: ngor gsal bzhin du mig 'od snang la blta zhing
NK033(gi)008:3457: rig pa stong gsal du bzhag pas da lta'i 'od
NK033(gi)008:3458: gsal skyel ma lta bu dang bar do'i 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:3459: sun ma lta bu gnyis tshes bco lnga'i nyi ma
NK033(gi)008:3460: nub pa dang zla ba shar ba dus mnyam pa
NK033(gi)008:3462: de yang nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NK033(gi)008:3463: sa ni sa la thim pa na //
NK033(gi)008:3464: lus ni lci zhing zas mi len //
NK033(gi)008:3465: langs dang 'gro ba'i stobs kun zad //
NK033(gi)008:3466: chu ni chu la thim pa'i tshe //
NK033(gi)008:3467: kha chu sna chu 'dzag par byed //
NK033(gi)008:3468: de bzhin me la me thim pas //
NK033(gi)008:3469: kha sna dag ni rab tu skam //
NK033(gi)008:3470: lus kyi drod rnams mtha' nas 'chor //
NK033(gi)008:3471: de bzhin rlung la rlung thim pas //
NK033(gi)008:3472: dbugs ni ngar ngar yan lag g.yob //
NK033(gi)008:3473: mig kyang gyen la bzlog pa 'byung //
NK033(gi)008:3474: rtags ni su la byung ba de //
NK033(gi)008:3475: nges par pha rol 'gro bas na //
NK033(gi)008:3476: de tshe bla ma'i gdams ngag rnams //
NK033(gi)008:3477: rang gi rgyud la 'dril bar bya //
NK033(gi)008:3479: gdams pa'i don rnams la skabs 'dir rig pa drung
NK033(gi)008:3480: bton te skad cig kyang ma yengs par gsal btab
NK033(gi)008:3481: pas / rlung rnam shes la thim pa'i dus der
NK033(gi)008:3482: snga phyi'i 'od gsal gnyis ma bu 'phrod nas gdod
NK033(gi)008:3484: gsum pa chos nyid kyi bar dor rang snang la
NK033(gi)008:3485: yid ches pa ma pang du bu 'jug pa lta
NK033(gi)008:3486: bu ni / gdams ngag gi don nyams 'og tu
NK033(gi)008:3487: chud pas chos nyid kyi snang cha ji ltar shar
NK033(gi)008:3488: yang 'jigs pa med par rang snang ye shes kyi
NK033(gi)008:3489: rol par shar ba rnams thim tshul lnga'i sgo nas
NK033(gi)008:3491: dang po rnam shes nam mkhar thim pa'i tshe rig
NK033(gi)008:3492: pa'i 'od rtsal zhugs nas mig tu gnas skabs skad
NK033(gi)008:3493: cig dang po la ka dag gi snang ba ston
NK033(gi)008:3494: ka'i nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba lta bu'i 'od
NK033(gi)008:3496: de nas nam mkha' 'od gsal la thim pa'i tshe
NK033(gi)008:3497: dus ma 'gyur bar snang ba 'gyur nas 'od lnga'i
NK033(gi)008:3498: snang ba dang sgra 'od zer gsum gyi snang ba
NK033(gi)008:3500: de nas 'od gsal zung 'jug la thim pas rigs
NK033(gi)008:3501: lnga'i tshom bu rnams bsam gtan gyi zhag lngar rim
NK033(gi)008:3502: gyis 'char / de nas zung 'jug ye shes la
NK033(gi)008:3503: thim pas ye shes bzhi sbyor gyi snam bu dang
NK033(gi)008:3505: de nas ye shes lhun grub la thim pa'i dus su yar ka dag chos sku dang /
NK033(gi)008:3506: thad kar longs sku rigs lnga /
NK033(gi)008:3507: mar 'gro 'dul sprul sku la sogs pa'i zhing khams rnams 'char zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3508: de'i tshe chos nyid kyi snang cha ji ltar shar
NK033(gi)008:3509: yang 'jigs pa med pa sngar 'dris kyi mi dang
NK033(gi)008:3510: 'phrad pa ltar rang snang ye shes kyi rol par
NK033(gi)008:3511: thag bcad do // de'ang thim lugs lnga po mthar chags su bgrod pa'i nges pa med de /
NK033(gi)008:3512: gang zag gi dbang po'i rim pas /
NK033(gi)008:3513: rab nyi zla kha sbyor ltar lus bor ba dang 'od gsal 'char ba dus mnyam du grol /
NK033(gi)008:3514: 'bring zung 'jug dang ye shes kyi snang ba gang rung du grol /
NK033(gi)008:3515: tha ma lhun grub kyi snang bar grol zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3516: snang ba'i 'char tshul kyang gang du grol ba yan chad du 'char zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3517: de man chad dbyings su thim pas mi 'char la /
NK033(gi)008:3518: de dag gang dang gang du grol kyang skad cig dang por rang snang du ngo shes /
NK033(gi)008:3519: gnyis par shes thog tu gnas /
NK033(gi)008:3520: gsum par gnas thog tu grol /
NK033(gi)008:3521: bzhi par grol thog nas sems can gyi khams rnams su sprul pa bkye /
NK033(gi)008:3522: lnga par nang gsal bum skur bzhugs shing skad cig
NK033(gi)008:3523: de dag kyang phal cher bya rdzogs kyi skad cig
NK033(gi)008:3524: yin kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK033(gi)008:3525: bsam gtan gyi zhag ni sngon ting nge 'dzin la
NK033(gi)008:3526: mnyam par bzhag nas phyi ma'i kun rtog ma skyes
NK033(gi)008:3527: pa'i bar gyi goms cha yin la /
NK033(gi)008:3528: de rnams kyang 'dir ni rags bsdus tsam du bstan pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3529: gzhan yang chos nyid bar do'i snang ba la 'jug pa shes pa'i gnad /
NK033(gi)008:3531: mthar phyin pa ngo shes pa'i gnad gsum gyi don
NK033(gi)008:3532: sogs nyams len gnad kyi sgron me las shes par
NK033(gi)008:3533: bya'o // bzhi pa srid pa bar do la las
NK033(gi)008:3534: kyi 'phro mthud pas yur ba rkang chad la wa
NK033(gi)008:3536: 'khrul snang 'jigs skrag ji ltar shar yang sngar goms
NK033(gi)008:3537: pa'i gdams pa'i gnad kyis dag pa'i skyed srid kyi
NK033(gi)008:3539: de yang dbang po'i rim pas ngo sprod kyi gnad
NK033(gi)008:3540: thob kyang bsgom pa 'phro can du lus te skye
NK033(gi)008:3541: ba brgyud nas grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3542: goms kyang lhun grub kyi snang ba shar tshe ting
NK033(gi)008:3543: nge 'dzin gyi rtsal zhan stobs kyis snga phyi'i 'od
NK033(gi)008:3544: gsal gnyis shar nub dus mnyam pas rang snang ngos
NK033(gi)008:3545: ma zin par snang ba rang yal la song ste
NK033(gi)008:3546: rnam shes lus rgya dang bral stobs kyis 'byung bzhi
NK033(gi)008:3547: phra ba'i las rlung lugs ldog tu langs te /
NK033(gi)008:3548: bar do'i yid lus grub nas snang ba thams cad ban bum /
NK033(gi)008:3550: bya spu rlung gis bskyod pa ltar sna tshogs 'char zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3551: 'byung bzhi'i dngos po gang la'ang thogs med du 'jug
NK033(gi)008:3552: nus shing las kyi rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu dang ldan
NK033(gi)008:3553: pa / sngar med kyi mngon shes phra mo 'char zhing dbang po rno la dran pa gsal ba /
NK033(gi)008:3554: rigs mthun gyi 'gro ba gzhan lha mig dag pas mthong ba /
NK033(gi)008:3555: sngar goms bag chags kyis nye du 'brel yod sogs
NK033(gi)008:3556: kyi phyogs su phyin te gtam smras kyang de rnams
NK033(gi)008:3557: kyis ma mthong zhing ma thos pas lan med pa
NK033(gi)008:3558: na rang nyid shi bar shes te /
NK033(gi)008:3559: sngar gyi gdams pa rnams dran pas bar do'i 'khrul
NK033(gi)008:3560: snang dang 'jigs skrag thams cad rang ngo shes nas
NK033(gi)008:3561: / de yang dbang po'i rim pas blo rab rnams bla ma'i mos gus kyi lam khyer dang /
NK033(gi)008:3562: gzung 'dzin gnyis bsdus kyi snang ba thams cad bden
NK033(gi)008:3563: med sgyu ma lta bur rtogs pas grol ba dang
NK033(gi)008:3564: / blo 'bring rnams yid dam gyi bskyed rdzogs zung
NK033(gi)008:3565: 'jug gi nyams len la brten nas grol ba dang
NK033(gi)008:3566: / / tha mas dag pa'i zhing yid la bsams
NK033(gi)008:3567: nas mdun mkhar chos 'byung dmar po gdeng ka gyen
NK033(gi)008:3568: bstan gyi dbus su rang sems a yig dkar po'i
NK033(gi)008:3569: rnam par gsal btab cing smon lam gyis mtshams sbyar
NK033(gi)008:3570: te chos 'byung nam mkha' skar mda' 'phangs pa ltar
NK033(gi)008:3571: dag zhing du song bar bsams te sems spros bral
NK033(gi)008:3572: gyi ngang du bzhag pas grol lo //
NK033(gi)008:3573: der ma grol na phyi ma'i mngal sgo ngan pa spangs te bzang po'i 'phro mthud pa ni /
NK033(gi)008:3574: gang du skye 'gyur gyi pha ma dang yi dam
NK033(gi)008:3575: dbyer med yab yum gyi rnam par bsgoms pa'i mngal
NK033(gi)008:3576: du pad nyi zla steng h'u yig dkar po zhig
NK033(gi)008:3577: bsams la der rnam shes 'jug dus skye ba blang
NK033(gi)008:3578: ba'i rten 'di la bstan pa dang sems can gyi
NK033(gi)008:3579: don rlabs po che byed nus par shog cig snyam
NK033(gi)008:3580: pa'i 'dun pa rtse gcig pas rang nyid rdo rje
NK033(gi)008:3581: sems dpar bsgoms te de nyid ma'i mngal gyi h'u
NK033(gi)008:3583: spros bral stong nyid kyi ngang du bzhag pas pha
NK033(gi)008:3584: ma dad pa can gyis bur skyes te chung ngu
NK033(gi)008:3585: nas chos dang 'phrad cing shes rab dang brtson 'grus
NK033(gi)008:3586: ldan pa / sbyangs pa'i las 'phro sad pas snying
NK033(gi)008:3587: po'i bstan pa dang mjal nas lam gyi 'phro mthud
NK033(gi)008:3588: pas tshe de nyid dam bar dor nges par 'tshang
NK033(gi)008:3590: don gsum pa dbang po tha ma rang bzhin sprul
NK033(gi)008:3591: sku'i zhing du 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams pa la gsum
NK033(gi)008:3592: / rang bzhin gnas pa'i dus su sbyong ba /
NK033(gi)008:3594: sprul sku'i zhing du grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3596: mngon sum gyi snang ba la nyin mtshan goms par
NK033(gi)008:3597: byas pas rmi lam ngan pa nub nas bzang po
NK033(gi)008:3599: sems la bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK033(gi)008:3600: la yun ring du gnas pa des skabs su nyin
NK033(gi)008:3601: dus rang bzhin sprul pa sku'i zhing bsam la rig
NK033(gi)008:3602: pa 'od kyi gong bu mig nas 'thon te /
NK033(gi)008:3603: gtso bo'i thugs kar 'phangs par bya zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3604: mtshan dus nyal tshe'ang tho skor thams cad rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing dang /
NK033(gi)008:3606: snying pad+ma dang nyi zla'i dbus na /
NK033(gi)008:3607: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas bzhugs pa la sems gtad nas ma yengs par gnyid du nyal bas /
NK033(gi)008:3608: dag pa'i zhing khams rmi lam du 'byongs par 'ong nges so //
NK033(gi)008:3609: gnad 'di ni nyi zla kha sbyor gyi 'grel par gsungs pas rab tu zab bo //
NK033(gi)008:3612: le lo can btsan thabs 'pho ba'i man ngag la brten nas mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3614: rang snang bar do'i 'od gsal nub dus rang nyid kyis bar dor ngo shes pa 'byung bas /
NK033(gi)008:3615: de'i tshe sngar gyi dmigs pa des 'phos pas skye ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3616: de'ang chos nyid bden pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK033(gi)008:3617: rig 'dzin gyi bla ma rnams kyi thugs rje las de ltar 'gyur ba yin la /
NK033(gi)008:3618: bar du'ang gang du bsam sar phyin nus pa'i rdzu 'phrul yod pa'i gnad kyis so //
NK033(gi)008:3619: kha cig bems rig bral ma thag skye bar gsungs la /
NK033(gi)008:3620: kha cig 'od gsal nub pa dang dus mnyam du skye bar gsungs /
NK033(gi)008:3621: kha cig srid pa'i bar do la lam 'thon nas
NK033(gi)008:3622: rmi lam ltar yad yud zhag bdun la sogs par
NK033(gi)008:3623: gnas pa las / rmi lam sad pa'i tshul gyis
NK033(gi)008:3624: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba la sogs par rdzus
NK033(gi)008:3626: de dag ni goms shugs rab 'bring tha ma'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3628: gser phreng gi dgongs pa 'pho ba 'od gsal snying po nyams su len par bya ste /
NK033(gi)008:3629: de'ang rtsa khrid dang sprel na zur du mi dgos kyang /
NK033(gi)008:3630: mi sbrel bar dmigs su bsgom pa sogs la skyabs sems bla ma'i rnal 'byor rnam sngon du btang /
NK033(gi)008:3631: gang ltar bde ba'i stan la lus gnad dang ldan pas 'khod de /
NK033(gi)008:3633: dmigs skor dang po stong ra sbyang ba /
NK033(gi)008:3634: gnyis pa rtsa gsal gdab pa /
NK033(gi)008:3635: gsum pa rlung sems bsdu ba /
NK033(gi)008:3636: bzhi pa bsu skyel la slob pa /
NK033(gi)008:3638: drug pa las la sbyar ba'o //
NK033(gi)008:3640: rang lus phyi lpags pa'i skya ri la nang stong chen sgrib thogs dang bral bar bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)008:3642: lus kyis dbus su dbu ma dwangs gsal mda' smyug tsam pa /
NK033(gi)008:3643: spyi bo nas gsang gnas kyi bar drang tha ler gnas par bsgom /
NK033(gi)008:3645: snying gar 'od lnga'i gong bu'i dbus su rang gi
NK033(gi)008:3646: rlung sems mi 'gyur ba'i dwangs ma a dkar po
NK033(gi)008:3647: sran chung tsam dkar zhing 'tsher ba zhig bsgoms pas
NK033(gi)008:3648: / tha mal gyi rtog pa 'gags nas a la
NK033(gi)008:3649: sems rtse gcig tu zin pa ni goms pa'i tshad
NK033(gi)008:3650: / do / 'di ni longs sku'i 'char gzhi kun bzang yab yum gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3652: rang gi spyi bo'i nam mkhar 'og min lhun grub
NK033(gi)008:3653: rin po che'i zhing khams 'ja' tshon 'od lnga 'khyil
NK033(gi)008:3654: ba'i dbus na pad+ma dang nyi zla'i ste nga du
NK033(gi)008:3655: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang dbyer med pa'i rnam par
NK033(gi)008:3656: snang mdzad yab yum longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i cha
NK033(gi)008:3657: byad can gyi mtha' bskor du mi bskyod pa sogs
NK033(gi)008:3659: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i 'khor gyis bskor ba gsal btab cir mos gus drag tu bya /
NK033(gi)008:3660: de nas ngag tu a +aa zhes brgya rtsa brgyad
NK033(gi)008:3661: dbyangs bcas brjod pas a de je mtho je mthor
NK033(gi)008:3662: gyur te rnam snang gi thugs kar sib kyis thim
NK033(gi)008:3663: par bsams la mnyam par bzhag /
NK033(gi)008:3664: yang a de rnam snang gi thugs ka nas rang gi snying gar bde phril te babs par bsam /
NK033(gi)008:3665: gegs chung khyad skabs su tshangs bug tu ham dkar
NK033(gi)008:3666: po zhig gsal btab pa de las bdud rtsi'i rgyun
NK033(gi)008:3667: rnam shes kyi thig le la sib sib bstims /
NK033(gi)008:3668: de ltar na'ang mthar ham dang ro gcig tu gyur pa rnam snang gi thugs kar bstim zhing /
NK033(gi)008:3669: de nas rigs lnga'i tshom bu je mtho je phrar
NK033(gi)008:3670: gyur te nam mkha' la 'ja' ltar yal bar bsams
NK033(gi)008:3671: la a grangs ji ltar rigs pa brjod cing gsal
NK033(gi)008:3672: stong spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du 'jog go
NK033(gi)008:3673: // sngar nas 'pho ba 'byongs zin pa yin na nam dgos dus las la sbyar bas chog go //
NK033(gi)008:3674: de ltar min na zhag bdun la sogs pa'i bar rtags thon thon du bsgom dgos so //
NK033(gi)008:3676: mjug tu gegs sel rlung 'jug gnas ldang gsum dang
NK033(gi)008:3677: sbyar ba'i rdor bzlas ci nus bya zhing mthar dge
NK033(gi)008:3679: bzlog tu med pa'i 'chi ltas shar ba na 'pho bar bya ste /
NK033(gi)008:3680: de'ang spyi bo'i tshangs bug ha re yod par bsams la /
NK033(gi)008:3681: snying ga'i thig le rnam snang gi thugs kar bstim
NK033(gi)008:3682: pa' bar sngar ltar las thig le mi 'bebs shing
NK033(gi)008:3683: / lan gcig gsum sogs ci rigs kyi mthar sngar
NK033(gi)008:3684: ltar rigs lnga'i tshom bu je mthor gshegs rjes 'pho
NK033(gi)008:3685: bya 'pho byed dang bral ba'i ngang du rang sems
NK033(gi)008:3686: bde sing nger bsgyur la 'jog go //
NK033(gi)008:3687: des ni bar do'i 'od gsal ngos zin cing srid pa bar do'i g.yang sa mi mthong /
NK033(gi)008:3688: gzhon nu bum sku'i zhing khams kun tu bzang po'i
NK033(gi)008:3689: sa la sangs rgyas nas don gnyis lhun gyis grub
NK033(gi)008:3690: pa'i phrin las la dbang 'byor ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3692: mngon sum gyi don mthong yang brtan pa ma thob par sgom pa 'phro can du lus pa'am /
NK033(gi)008:3693: bsgoms kyang ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal zhan pas bar
NK033(gi)008:3694: do'i grol tshad dang mi ldan pa rnams chos nyid
NK033(gi)008:3695: kyi bar do shar yang ngos ma zin par srid
NK033(gi)008:3696: pa'i bar do rmi lam gyi 'khrul ngo tsam du
NK033(gi)008:3697: shar ba las / chos 'di'i sgo mthong ba'i byin
NK033(gi)008:3698: rlabs kyis rmi lam sad pa'i cha tsam la mngon
NK033(gi)008:3699: par dga' ba la sogs pa dag pa'i zhing du
NK033(gi)008:3700: skye ba blangs nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK033(gi)008:3701: shar ba las / zhal mthong / gsung thos /
NK033(gi)008:3706: gzengs bstod rnams thob nas nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba
NK033(gi)008:3707: las grol nas gdod ma'i zhing du skad cig gis
NK033(gi)008:3709: spyi don bzhi pa bsgoms pa las byung ba'i 'bras bu bstan pa la gsum /
NK033(gi)008:3712: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus bshad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3714: 'di nyid du grol lugs gsum bshad pa de la'ang
NK033(gi)008:3715: lhag med dang lhag bcas su sangs rgyas pas sku
NK033(gi)008:3717: rang bzhin mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'od lnga 'du 'bral med /
NK033(gi)008:3718: thugs rje mdzad pa'i phrin las su rgyas pas thugs rje la rgyun chad med pas /
NK033(gi)008:3719: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ba ste /
NK033(gi)008:3720: de'ang tshe 'di'i rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du sangs rgyas pa la bzhed do //
NK033(gi)008:3721: gnyis pa lhag bcas myang 'das ni //
NK033(gi)008:3722: ka dag lhun grub kyi nyams len la brten pa lam gyi yon tan 'bras bu'i thob tshul lo //
NK033(gi)008:3723: zhes pa ltar sa lam gyi yon tan rim gyis
NK033(gi)008:3724: bgrod de gdos bcas kyi phung po lhag bcas su
NK033(gi)008:3729: gdung sogs phyi nang gi rtags snang dang bcas bar dor 'tshang rgya ba ni /
NK033(gi)008:3730: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba zhes bzhed pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3732: grol lugs gsum po gang du sangs rgyas kyang thugs rje mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK033(gi)008:3733: rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i gzugs sku gnyis kyi mthu las rgyal sras sar gnas rnams dang /
NK033(gi)008:3734: thun mong gi gdul bya la rnam snang longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3735: gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul pa'i rnam rol so so'i mos ngor mtha' yas par ston pa ste /
NK033(gi)008:3736: de'ang nang gsal sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med
NK033(gi)008:3737: pa'i dgongs pa dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dbyings
NK033(gi)008:3738: las ma g.yos bzhin du phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rnams
NK033(gi)008:3739: su longs spyod rdzogs sku dang sprul skus don mdzad
NK033(gi)008:3740: pa ni mkha' dbyings kyi zla ba dwangs pa'i chu
NK033(gi)008:3741: snod du mar 'char ba lta bu dang /
NK033(gi)008:3742: 'khor ba ji srid bar du don mdzad pa ni
NK033(gi)008:3743: yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang dpag bsam gyi shing
NK033(gi)008:3744: ltar 'bad med lhun grub tu 'byung zhing rgyun mi
NK033(gi)008:3748: yang gsang snying thig mngon sum man ngag 'dir //
NK033(gi)008:3749: gang gis reg pas myang 'das dngos la sbyor //
NK033(gi)008:3750: zhes gsungs pa ltar gsang ba bla na med pa'i
NK033(gi)008:3751: gdams pa 'di rtse gcig tu nyams su blangs na
NK033(gi)008:3752: dbang po yang rab rnams tshe gcig lus gcig gis
NK033(gi)008:3753: grol ba dang / yang na rab lo gsum /
NK033(gi)008:3755: tha mas mi lo bdun tshun la grol ba rgyud
NK033(gi)008:3756: dang rig 'dzin grub pa'i tshogs kyis mgrin gcig tu
NK033(gi)008:3757: gsungs so // lnga pa zhar byung lag len gyi gnad bstan pa la gnyis /
NK033(gi)008:3758: gdams ngag spyi'i rnam par bzhag pa /
NK033(gi)008:3759: lag len gyi dbye bsdu bshad pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3761: rdzogs pa chen po 'di'i lugs kyi gdams ngag gi 'debs lugs gsum du bzhed de /
NK033(gi)008:3762: khrid kyi lugs su gdab pa /
NK033(gi)008:3763: ngo sprod kyi lugs su gdab ba /
NK033(gi)008:3764: mgron po la rgal la tshang sprugs su gdab pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3766: sngon 'gro gsum gang rung sngon du song nas dngos
NK033(gi)008:3767: gzhi ngo sprod de rjes rgyab chos kyis yid ches
NK033(gi)008:3768: par byed pa'o // de'ang skyes bu spros pa can
NK033(gi)008:3769: thun mong gi drod rtags la dga' bas sku gsum
NK033(gi)008:3770: gyi sna khrid pa 'byung gzhi'i sgra don la sngon
NK033(gi)008:3771: du sbyangs nas dngos gzhi ngo sprod pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3772: brtson 'grus can brtul zhugs la dga' bas rig pa'i
NK033(gi)008:3773: sna khrid pa 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod
NK033(gi)008:3774: pa la sngon du sbyangs nas dngos gzhi ngo sprod
NK033(gi)008:3775: pa'o // le lo can rtog dpyod la dga' bas
NK033(gi)008:3776: sems kyi sna khrid pa lus ngag sems kyi sngon
NK033(gi)008:3777: 'gro sngon du sbyangs nas dngos gzhi ngo sprod pa
NK033(gi)008:3778: pa'o // yin no // ngo sprod kyi lugs su
NK033(gi)008:3779: gdab pa ni las 'phro sad pa kha cig la
NK033(gi)008:3780: snye ma mgul pa nas 'chang ba ltar dbang gi
NK033(gi)008:3781: rjes la ngo sprad nas nyams su len pa ste
NK033(gi)008:3782: pa'o // yin no // / de'ang khregs chod dang
NK033(gi)008:3783: thod rgal don kho na ston par bya ba dang
NK033(gi)008:3784: pa'o // yin no // / / de'i rjes 'brel du dbyings mtshon byed me long //
NK033(gi)008:3785: ye shes mtshon byed rma bya'i mdongs /
NK033(gi)008:3786: zung 'jug mtshon byed man shel sogs la brten nas ngo sprod nyer gcig dang /
NK033(gi)008:3787: lnga tshan lnga'i sgo nas gdab pa'o //
NK033(gi)008:3789: de'ang dus mtha'i tshe 'chi kha'i mi de mgron po lam zhugs lta bu /
NK033(gi)008:3790: 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal la chen po lta bu /
NK033(gi)008:3791: de'i las snang snang ba'i 'char tshul sna tshogs snang
NK033(gi)008:3792: ba ngo ma shes na dgrar ldang ba'i tshang yod
NK033(gi)008:3793: cing / ngo shes na grogs su 'char ba'i tshang yod pas /
NK033(gi)008:3794: 'chi kha'i dus der ngo sprod tshang sprugs su 'debs par gsungs so //
NK033(gi)008:3795: de'ang phyi ma gnyis sa bcad dang por 'du ba yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3796: gnyis pa lag len gyi dbye bsdu ni /
NK033(gi)008:3797: rdzogs rim yongs rdzogs smin slob tu khrid par 'dod na //
NK033(gi)008:3798: thun gyi sngon 'gro nas brtsams te sngon 'gro sems sbyang bdun dang /
NK033(gi)008:3799: thun mong dang khyad par gyi tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK033(gi)008:3800: de nas chags bral rlung dang chags can thig le'i rnal 'byor /
NK033(gi)008:3802: ka dag gi khrid dmigs rnams dang /
NK033(gi)008:3803: 'khor 'das ru shan dbye ba nas bzung thod rgal gyi man ngag /
NK033(gi)008:3804: sku gsum gyi 'dug stangs la slob tshul /
NK033(gi)008:3805: mtshan mo'i thun gsum la ye shes gnad du bsnun pa'i man ngag /
NK033(gi)008:3806: rmi lam bzung sbyang spel bsgyur la 'bad pa'i rim
NK033(gi)008:3807: pa rnams re re nas rgyud la myong bas skyes
NK033(gi)008:3808: kyi bar du bsgom pa la slob cing skabs su
NK033(gi)008:3809: bab pa'i spyod pa la gnas pas gdod ma'i grol
NK033(gi)008:3810: sar rnyogs pa gdon mi za'o //
NK033(gi)008:3811: yang rdzogs rim gzhan gyis rgyud sbyangs zin pa'i gang
NK033(gi)008:3812: zag lam 'di'i dngos gzhi la zhugs par spro na
NK033(gi)008:3813: / sems sbyong bdun po ji ltar 'os pa nas
NK033(gi)008:3814: thun mong ma yin pa'i sngon 'gro dran pa rgyun
NK033(gi)008:3816: sgo gsum gyi sngon 'gro nas brtsams khregs thod dngos la 'jug pas chog cing /
NK033(gi)008:3817: lo rgan pa sogs rtsa rlung mi 'chun pa'am //
NK033(gi)008:3818: de'i 'bras bu mi 'byin pa'i rigs la rlung thig
NK033(gi)008:3819: gi rnal 'byor bzhag kyang chad skyon du mi 'gyur
NK033(gi)008:3820: ba dang / dbang po'i sgo mi gsal ba lta
NK033(gi)008:3821: bu thod rgal gyis nod du mi rung ba la
NK033(gi)008:3822: khregs chod kho na ni shin tu ston rung la
NK033(gi)008:3823: ba dang / / khregs chod legs par sngon du
NK033(gi)008:3824: ma song ba la thod rgal rkyang pa nam yang
NK033(gi)008:3825: ba dang / / ston mi rung / spyir khregs
NK033(gi)008:3826: chod ni lam 'bad med du rang grol ba 'od
NK033(gi)008:3827: gsal gyi snang ba la ma ltos par rig pa
NK033(gi)008:3828: rjen pa nyams su len pa le lo can ma
NK033(gi)008:3829: bsgoms par 'tshang rgya ba dang dbang po rnon po'i
NK033(gi)008:3830: ba dang / / ston mi rung / gnad yin
NK033(gi)008:3831: la / thod rgal ni 'bad bcas su grol ba
NK033(gi)008:3832: 'od gsal gyi snang ba la ltos nas brtson 'grus
NK033(gi)008:3833: can tshe 'di nyid du gdos bcas 'od lus su
NK033(gi)008:3834: dag nas 'tshang rgya bar byed pa yin no //
NK033(gi)008:3835: khrid tshul rgyas bsdus gang la'ang lugs 'di'i dbang bskur
NK033(gi)008:3836: rnams ni cis kyang sngon du 'gro dgos la bsags
NK033(gi)008:3837: sbyong gzhan nyams su len ma nus kyang bla ma'i
NK033(gi)008:3838: rim pa dngos grub rgya mtsho tsam ni shin tu
NK033(gi)008:3840: 'di nyid ched du nyams su len pa po la gnad che ba /
NK033(gi)008:3841: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i sgrub thabs yid bzhin nor bu skor gsum gyi bsgom bzlas dang /
NK033(gi)008:3842: bogs 'don spyod pa'i gnad yig bdud rtsi'i rgyal po sogs kyang grogs su bsten /
NK033(gi)008:3846: tha ma rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du mi grol
NK033(gi)008:3847: mi srid pa'i zab chos gdod ma'i mgon po'i thugs
NK033(gi)008:3848: tig 'di lta bu dang mjal ba'i tshe snyoms las
NK033(gi)008:3849: su mi bzhag par ci nus kyis nyams su blang
NK033(gi)008:3850: ba la rtse gcig tu brtson par byas pas don
NK033(gi)008:3851: gnyis lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur ba gdon mi za'o
NK033(gi)008:3852: // bla med 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i lam //
NK033(gi)008:3853: grol ba bzhi ldan theg dgu'i mthar thug pa //
NK033(gi)008:3854: gang de'i yang snying zhing khams rgya mtsho ru //
NK033(gi)008:3855: mtshan tsam dkon pa'i snying tig yid bzhin nor //
NK033(gi)008:3856: lugs srol bzhi yi mchog gyur bi ma la'i //
NK033(gi)008:3857: snying tig ma bu bka' srol chu bo gsum //
NK033(gi)008:3858: gcig 'dus mkhas grub kun gyi mnog chos te //
NK033(gi)008:3859: de yi khrid tshul kun gyi yang bcud bsdus //
NK033(gi)008:3860: zab barlingasa rdo rje'i gnas ni rtogs par dka' //
NK033(gi)008:3861: chos srung mel tshe nam yang mi g.yel bas //
NK033(gi)008:3862: bdag lta rmongs pa'i lam su babs min kyang //
NK033(gi)008:3863: khyab bdag bla mas rjes su gnang phyir bris //
NK033(gi)008:3864: gong ma'i gsung bzang dpang por bkod na yang //
NK033(gi)008:3865: shes rab rtsal chung sgom pa'i stobs dman pas //
NK033(gi)008:3866: nongs par gang gyur rtsa gsum chos srung gis //
NK033(gi)008:3867: 'phral yun sgrib par mi 'gyur dag tshangs stsol //
NK033(gi)008:3868: dri med bshes gnyen mkhas pa'i gtsug rgyan dngos //
NK033(gi)008:3869: klong chen gnyis pa rdo rje gzi brjid kyi //
NK033(gi)008:3870: zhal lung bdud rtsi dam sel rnyogs pa yis //
NK033(gi)008:3871: bslad min skal ldan gsos su bsten par 'os //
NK033(gi)008:3872: rab dge dri ma med las 'od gsal gyi //
NK033(gi)008:3873: snang ba'i sbubs su 'khrul pa kun sangs te //
NK033(gi)008:3874: nam mkha' khyab pa'i lus can ji snyed pa //
NK033(gi)008:3875: gdod ma'i grol sar mngon byang chub par shog /
NK033(gi)008:3876: chos tshul 'di yang nyi zla ltar khyab cing //
NK033(gi)008:3877: nor bu bzhin du skye dgu'i 'dod pa 'jo //
NK033(gi)008:3878: chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam yang chad med pas //
NK033(gi)008:3879: thog ma'i mgon po'i mdzad pa sgrub gyur cig //
NK033(gi)008:3880: de ltar snying thig ma bu'i khrid srol chu bo gcig 'dus kyi yig cha 'adi'ang /
NK033(gi)008:3881: kun mkhyen gdod ma'i mgon po rdo rje gzi brjid
NK033(gi)008:3882: rtsal gyi zhal snga nas smin grol bka' drin du
NK033(gi)008:3883: stsal ba'i tshe / 'di ltar bgyi bar 'os zhes bka' yis rjes su gnang ba dang /
NK033(gi)008:3884: slad char sgrub sde 'di nyid du nyams len mkhan
NK033(gi)008:3885: rnams la nye bar mkho bas mtshams sbyar te rje
NK033(gi)008:3886: bla ma nyid la gsol ba btab kyang /
NK033(gi)008:3887: slar rjes su gnang ba dmigs bsal du stsal ba las /
NK033(gi)008:3888: byams mgon t+aa'i si tu'i 'bangs tha pad+ma gar dbang
NK033(gi)008:3889: phrin las 'gro 'dul rtsal gyis smin gling rje btsun
NK033(gi)008:3890: rin po che'i khrid yig rtsa bar bzung /
NK033(gi)008:3891: snying tig ma bu dngos kyi rdo rje'i gsung stabs bde ba rnams nye bar bsdebs /
NK033(gi)008:3892: rdo rje tshe dbang nor bu'i zhal lung dang /
NK033(gi)008:3893: karma snying tig gi gnad 'ga' zhig gis kyang zur brgyan te /
NK033(gi)008:3894: dpal spungs yang khrod kun bzang bde chen 'od gsal
NK033(gi)008:3895: gling du rgyal bas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK033(gi)008:3896: dus tshes dge bar bris pa bstan 'gro la phan
NK033(gi)008:3897: pa rgya chen po 'byung bar gyur cig //
